1150void
1151printacl(const char *s, ACL *aclp, FILE *f)
1152{
1153 if (f == NULL)
1154 f = stderr;
1155 acl_array_num = 0;
1156 fprintf(f, "%s-line %d: ", s, gbl.lineno);
1157 _printacl(1, aclp, f);
1158 fprintf(f, "\n");
1159}
1160
1161static void
1162_dumpacl(int nest, ACL *aclp, FILE *f)
1163{
1164 /* dump a list of aclps */
1165 for (; aclp != NULL; aclp = aclp->next) {
1166 int sptr, dtype, ast, astinit, astlimit, aststep, astcount;
1167 SST *stkp;
1168 DOINFO *doinfo;
1169
1170 fprintf(f, "\n%*.*s", 2 * nest, 2 * nest, " ");
1171 switch (aclp->id) {
1172 case AC_AST:
1173 dtype = A_DTYPEG(aclp->u1.ast);
1174 ast = aclp->u1.ast;
1175 fprintf(f, "dtype %d, ast(%d) ", dtype, ast);
1176 if (ast) {
1177 printast(ast);
1178 if (A_ALIASG(ast)) {
1179 fprintf(f, " [alias");
1180 if (A_ALIASG(ast) != ast) {
1181 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
1182 fprintf(f, "(%d) ", ast);
1183 printast(ast);
1184 }
1185 fprintf(f, "]");
1186 }
1187 }
1188 break;
1189 case AC_EXPR:
1190 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
1191 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1192 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
1193 switch (SST_IDG(stkp)) {
1194 case S_ACONST:
1195 fprintf(f, "expr aconst, dtype %d", dtype);
1196 ast = 0;
1197 break;
1198 case S_CONST:
1199 fprintf(f, "expr const, dtype %d", dtype);
1200 break;
1201 case S_SCONST:
1202 fprintf(f, "expr sconst, dtype %d", dtype);
1203 break;
1204 case S_EXPR:
1205 fprintf(f, "expr expr, dtype %d", dtype);
1206 break;
1207 case S_IDENT:
1208 sptr = SST_SYMG(stkp);
1209 fprintf(f, "expr ident %d=%s, dtype %d", sptr,
1210 (sptr > 0 && sptr < stb.stg_avail) ? SYMNAME(sptr) : "", dtype);
1211 break;
1212 default:
1213 fprintf(f, "expr unknown, dtype %d", dtype);
1214 break;
1215 }
1216 if (ast) {
1217 fprintf(f, ", ast(%d) ", ast);
1218 printast(ast);
1219 if (A_ALIASG(ast)) {
1220 fprintf(f, " [alias");
1221 if (A_ALIASG(ast) != ast) {
1222 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
1223 fprintf(f, "(%d) ", ast);
1224 printast(ast);
1225 }
1226 fprintf(f, "]");
1227 }
1228 }
1229 break;
1230 case AC_CONST:
1231 fprintf(f, "const dtype %d conval %d", aclp->dtype, aclp->conval);
1232 break;
1233 case AC_ACONST:
1234 dtype = aclp->dtype;
1235 fprintf(f, "array, dtype %d", dtype);
1236 _dumpacl(nest + 1, aclp->subc, f);
1237 break;
1238 case AC_SCONST:
1239 dtype = aclp->dtype;
1240 sptr = DTY(dtype + 3); /* tag sptr */
1241 fprintf(f, "structure %s dtype %d", SYMNAME(sptr), dtype);
1242 _dumpacl(nest + 1, aclp->subc, f);
1243 break;
1244 case AC_IDO:
1245 doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
1246 sptr = doinfo->index_var;
1247 astinit = doinfo->init_expr;
1248 astlimit = doinfo->limit_expr;
1249 aststep = doinfo->step_expr;
1250 astcount = doinfo->count;
1251 fprintf(f, "DO [ast(%d)] %s = ast(%d), ast(%d), ast(%d) = [", astcount,
1252 SYMNAME(sptr), astinit, astlimit, aststep);
1253 if (astcount)
1254 printast(astcount);
1255 fprintf(f, "] ");
1256 if (astinit)
1257 printast(astinit);
1258 fprintf(f, ", ");
1259 if (astlimit)
1260 printast(astlimit);
1261 fprintf(f, ", ");
1262 if (aststep)
1263 printast(aststep);
1264 _dumpacl(nest + 1, aclp->subc, f);
1265 break;
1266 case AC_REPEAT:
1267 fprintf(f, "REPEAT*%d", aclp->u1.count);
1268 _dumpacl(nest + 1, aclp->subc, f);
1269 break;
1270 case AC_IEXPR:
1271 dtype = aclp->dtype;
1272 fprintf(f, "AC_IEXPR dtype %d, op %s", dtype,
1273 iexpr_op(aclp->u1.expr->op));
1274 break;
1275 case AC_CONVAL:
1276 dtype = aclp->dtype;
1277 fprintf(f, "AC_CONVAL dtype %d, conval %d", dtype, aclp->conval);
1278 break;
1279 default:
1280 fprintf(f, "unknown aclp->id %d", aclp->id);
1281 break;
1282 }
1283 }
1284}
1285
1286void
1287dumpacl(const char *s, ACL *aclp, FILE *f)
1288{
1289 if (f == NULL)
1290 f = stderr;
1291 acl_array_num = 0;
1292 fprintf(f, "ACL(%s):", s);
1293 _dumpacl(1, aclp, f);
1294 fprintf(f, "\n");
1295}
1296#endif
1297
1298static int
1299compute_width_dtype(DTYPE in_dtype)
1300{
1301 int sum;
1302 int member_dtype;
1303 int sptr;
1304 int stag;
1305 DTYPE dtype = DDTG(in_dtype);
1306
1307 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_DERIVED)
1308 return 1;
1309 stag = DTY(dtype + 3);
1310 if (VISITG(stag))
1311 return 1;
1312 VISITP(stag, 1);
1313 sum = 0;
1314 /* for each member */
1315 sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
1316 for (; sptr != NOSYM; sptr = SYMLKG(sptr)) {
1317 member_dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
1318 if (DTYG(member_dtype) == TY_DERIVED)
1319 sum += compute_width_dtype(member_dtype);
1320 else
1321 sum++;
1322 }
1323 VISITP(stag, 0);
1324 return sum;
1325}
1326
1327/* This code computes the number of arrays that are going to be
1328 created to store the aclp (== 1, unless this is an array of
1329 derived types.
1330 */
1331static int cw_array_num = 0;
1332static int max_cw_array_num = 0;
1333
1334static void
1335_compute_width(int in_array, ACL *aclp)
1336{
1337 int save_cw_array_num;
1338 DTYPE dtype;
1339
1340 /* if we are !in_array then we are in a structure, and
1341 the following element (or array) will represent a new
1342 mangled component, so increment cw_array_num */
1343
1344 for (; aclp != NULL; aclp = aclp->next) {
1345 switch (aclp->id) {
1346 case AC_AST:
1347 case AC_CONST:
1348 dtype = A_DTYPEG(aclp->u1.ast);
1349 goto have_dtype;
1350 case AC_EXPR:
1351 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(aclp->u1.stkp);
1352 have_dtype:
1353 aclp->u2.array_i = cw_array_num; /* save index */
1354 if (!in_array)
1355 cw_array_num += compute_width_dtype(dtype);
1356 if ((cw_array_num - 1) > max_cw_array_num)
1357 max_cw_array_num = (cw_array_num - 1);
1358 break;
1359 case AC_ACONST:
1360 _compute_width(1, aclp->subc); /* element list */
1361 dtype = aclp->dtype;
1362 if (!in_array)
1363 cw_array_num += compute_width_dtype(dtype);
1364 if ((cw_array_num - 1) > max_cw_array_num)
1365 max_cw_array_num = (cw_array_num - 1);
1366 break;
1367 case AC_SCONST:
1368 save_cw_array_num = cw_array_num;
1369
1370 _compute_width(0, aclp->subc); /* member list */
1371
1372 if (in_array)
1373 cw_array_num = save_cw_array_num;
1374 break;
1375 case AC_IDO:
1376 _compute_width(in_array, aclp->subc); /* IDO ac list */
1377 break;
1378 case AC_REPEAT:
1379 _compute_width(in_array, aclp->subc); /* item repeated */
1380 break;
1381 case AC_IEXPR:
1382 _compute_width(in_array, aclp->subc);
1383 break;
1384 default:
1385 interr("compute width aclp->id", aclp->id, 3);
1386 break;
1387 }
1388 }
1389}
1390
1391/** \brief Check if array has zero size.
1392
1393 It expects lowerbound and upper bound to be constant asts.
1394 Don't use NUM_ELEM because it could return 1 as number of element,
1395 If dtype is zero, it loosely check aggregate size which must be done
1396 after chk_constructor/(2).
1397 */
1398ISZ_T
1399size_of_array(DTYPE dtype)
1400{
1401 int i;
1402 ADSC *ad;
1403 int numdim;
1404 ISZ_T dim_size;
1405 ISZ_T size = 1;
1406 ISZ_T d;
1407
1408 if (dtype) {
1409#define DEFAULT_DIM_SIZE 127
1410
1411#if DEBUG
1412 assert(DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY, "extent_of, expected TY_ARRAY", dtype, 3);
1413#endif
1414 if ((d = DTY(dtype + 2)) <= 0) {
1415 interr("extent_of: no array descriptor", (int)d, 3);
1416 return 0;
1417 }
1418
1419 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
1420 case TY_ARRAY:
1421 if (DTY(dtype + 2) != 0) {
1422 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
1423 numdim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
1424 if (numdim < 1 || numdim > 7) {
1425 interr("extent_of: bad numdim", 0, 1);
1426 numdim = 0;
1427 }
1428 for (i = 0; i < numdim; i++) {
1429 if (A_TYPEG(AD_LWAST(ad, i)) != A_CNST &&
1430 A_TYPEG(AD_UPAST(ad, i)) != A_CNST) {
1431 dim_size = DEFAULT_DIM_SIZE;
1432 } else {
1433 dim_size = ad_val_of(sym_of_ast(AD_UPAST(ad, i))) -
1434 ad_val_of(sym_of_ast(AD_LWAST(ad, i))) + 1;
1435 }
1436 size *= dim_size;
1437 }
1438 }
1439 break;
1440
1441 default:
1442 return size;
1443 }
1444 } else if (acs.aggr_cnt == astb.bnd.zero && acs.scalar_cnt == 0) {
1445 return 0;
1446 }
1447 return size;
1448}
1449
1450static int
1451compute_width(ACL *aclp)
1452{
1453 cw_array_num = 0;
1454 max_cw_array_num = 0;
1455 _compute_width(1, aclp);
1456 return (max_cw_array_num + 1);
1457}
1458
1459/** \brief Check the array constructor and decide the dtype.
1460
1461 It is called when we first recognize an array constructor.
1462 */
1463DTYPE
1464chk_constructor(ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
1465{
1466 SEM_DIM_SPECS dim_specs_tmp;
1467#if DEBUG
1468 if (DBGBIT(3, 64))
1469 printacl("chk_constructor", aclp, gbl.dbgfil);
1470 assert(aclp->id == AC_ACONST, "chk_constructor aclp->id:", aclp->id, 3);
1471#endif
1472
1473 save_dim_specs(&dim_specs_tmp);
1474 BZERO(&acs, _ACS, 1);
1475 acs.aggr_cnt = astb.bnd.zero;
1476 acs.is_const = TRUE;
1477
1478 sem.top = &sem.dostack[0];
1479 compute_size(true, aclp->subc, dtype);
1480 if (dtype) {
1481 acs.eltype = dtype;
1482 }
1483
1484 switch (DTY(acs.eltype)) {
1485 case TY_CHAR:
1486 case TY_NCHAR:
1487 if (!A_ALIASG(DTY(acs.eltype + 1))) {
1488 } else if (acs.zln) {
1489 /* should be an error */
1490 acs.eltype = get_type(2, DTY(acs.eltype), astb.i1);
1491 }
1492 break;
1493 }
1494
1495 sem.arrdim.ndim = 1;
1496
1497 sem.bounds[0].lowtype = S_CONST;
1498 sem.bounds[0].lowb = 1;
1499 sem.bounds[0].lwast = 0;
1500
1501 if (acs.aggr_cnt == astb.bnd.zero) {
1502 sem.bounds[0].uptype = S_CONST;
1503 sem.bounds[0].upb = acs.scalar_cnt;
1504 sem.bounds[0].upast = mk_isz_cval((INT)acs.scalar_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype);
1505 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 0;
1506 } else {
1507 sem.bounds[0].uptype = S_EXPR;
1508 sem.bounds[0].upb = 0;
1509 sem.bounds[0].upast = mk_binop(
1510 OP_ADD, acs.aggr_cnt, mk_isz_cval((INT)acs.scalar_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype),
1511 astb.bnd.dtype);
1512 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 1;
1513 acs.is_const = FALSE;
1514 }
1515 if (sem.gcvlen && is_deferlenchar_dtype(acs.eltype)) {
1516 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 1;
1517 }
1518 aclp->size = sem.bounds[0].upast;
1519
1520 acs.arrtype = mk_arrdsc();
1521 DTY(acs.arrtype + 1) = acs.eltype;
1522 restore_dim_specs(&dim_specs_tmp);
1523
1524 aclp->is_const = acs.is_const; /* store in acl */
1525 aclp->dtype = acs.arrtype; /* store in acl and also return*/
1526 return acs.arrtype;
1527}
1528
1529/** \brief Initialize a named array constant (array PARAMETER), ensuring that
1530 it's only being done within the context of its host subprogram.
1531 */
1532void
1533init_named_array_constant(int arr, int host)
1534{
1535 if (ENCLFUNCG(arr) == 0 || ENCLFUNCG(arr) == host)
1536 /* emit the data inits for the named array constant */
1537 init_sptr_w_acl((int)CONVAL1G(arr), (ACL *)get_getitem_p(CONVAL2G(arr)));
1538}
1539
1540static int ALLOCATE_ARRAYS = TRUE;
1541
1542SPTR
1543get_param_alias_var(SPTR param_sptr, DTYPE dtype)
1544{
1545 char *np = mangle_name(SYMNAME(param_sptr), "ac");
1546 SPTR alias_sptr = getsymbol(np);
1547
1548 STYPEP(alias_sptr, ST_VAR);
1549 DTYPEP(alias_sptr, dtype);
1550 DCLDP(alias_sptr, 1);
1551 SCP(alias_sptr, SC_STATIC);
1552 SCOPEP(alias_sptr, stb.curr_scope);
1553 CONVAL1P(param_sptr, alias_sptr);
1554 PARAMP(alias_sptr, PARAMG(param_sptr));
1555 PARAMVALP(alias_sptr, PARAMVALG(param_sptr));
1556 DINITP(alias_sptr, 1);
1557 HCCSYMP(alias_sptr, 1);
1558 NMCNSTP(alias_sptr, param_sptr);
1559 sym_is_refd(alias_sptr);
1560 REFP(alias_sptr, 1);
1561 return alias_sptr;
1562}
1563
1564static int
1565convert_ctmp_array_to_param(int cctmpsptr, ACL *aclp)
1566{
1567 /* A temp has been generated to hold the value of an array
1568 * constructor and this temp is used in an expression. Convert
1569 * the temp to a named constant so that the initialization
1570 * values are available (in the associated A_INIT list) for use
1571 * in expression evaluation (esp. named constant initialization
1572 * expressions) */
1573
1574 SST tmp_sst;
1575 SST init;
1576 DTYPE dtype = DTYPEG(cctmpsptr);
1577 int aliassptr;
1578
1579 PARAMP(cctmpsptr, 1);
1580 STYPEP(cctmpsptr, ST_ARRAY);
1581 SCP(cctmpsptr, SC_NONE);
1582
1583 BZERO(&tmp_sst, SST, 1);
1584 SST_IDP(&tmp_sst, S_IDENT);
1585 SST_SYMP(&tmp_sst, cctmpsptr);
1586 dinit_struct_param(cctmpsptr, aclp, aclp->dtype);
1587
1588 STYPEP(cctmpsptr, ST_PARAM);
1589 SCOPEP(cctmpsptr, stb.curr_scope);
1590
1591 aliassptr = get_param_alias_var(cctmpsptr, dtype);
1592 STYPEP(aliassptr, ST_ARRAY);
1593
1594 BZERO(&init, SST, 1);
1595 SST_IDP(&init, S_ACONST);
1596 SST_DTYPEP(&init, aclp->dtype);
1597 SST_ACLP(&init, aclp);
1598
1599 construct_acl_for_sst(&init, DTYPEG(cctmpsptr));
1600
1601 if (sem.interface == 0) {
1602 CONVAL2P(cctmpsptr, put_getitem_p(aclp));
1603 } else {
1604 IGNOREP(cctmpsptr, 0);
1605 }
1606
1607 return aliassptr;
1608}
1609
1610/** \brief Assign \a aclp values to \a in_sptr.
1611
1612 If \a in_sptr is 0, it assigns values to temporaries. init_sptr_w_acl() is
1613 called at the point we are trying to use (a possibly array/struct nested)
1614 constructor; eg. in mkexpr1(). If acl is constant, dinit_constructor()
1615 uses data initialization to assign the values; otherwise, _construct is
1616 called to generate runtime code to assign values. (is_const means: is
1617 constant, we can do it, and we're in the right context to do it.)
1618 */
1619int
1620init_sptr_w_acl(int in_sptr, ACL *aclp)
1621{
1622 int sptr_supplied;
1623 int sptr;
1624 int ast;
1625 SST tmp_sst;
1626 VAR *ivl;
1627 SEM_DIM_SPECS dim_specs_tmp;
1628
1629#if DEBUG
1630 if (DBGBIT(3, 64))
1631 printacl("init_sptr_w_acl", aclp, gbl.dbgfil);
1632#endif
1633
1634 if (in_sptr && DINITG(in_sptr))
1635 return in_sptr;
1636
1637 if (in_sptr && ENCLFUNCG(in_sptr) &&
1638 STYPEG(ENCLFUNCG(in_sptr)) == ST_MODULE) {
1639 /* the DINIT flag used to be enough. But now interf.c sets DINIT to
1640 zero. So for MODULE var$ac referenced outside the module, we can
1641 assume the initialization has already been done. */
1642 return in_sptr;
1643 }
1644
1645 if (aclp->id != AC_ACONST) {
1646 interr("init_sptr_w_acl aclp->id:", aclp->id, 3);
1647 return 0;
1648 }
1649
1650 save_dim_specs(&dim_specs_tmp);
1651 BZERO(&acs, _ACS, 1);
1652
1653 sptr_supplied = (in_sptr != 0);
1654 sptr = in_sptr;
1655
1656 /* chk_constructor() was called earlier and set up this information */
1657 acs.is_const = aclp->is_const;
1658 acs.arrtype = aclp->dtype;
1659 sem.arrdim.ndefer = AD_DEFER(AD_DPTR(acs.arrtype));
1660
1661 if (sem.dinit_data) {
1662 if (sptr_supplied) {
1663 acs.tmp = 0;
1664 } else {
1665 acs.tmp = get_arr_const(acs.arrtype);
1666 }
1667
1668 sptr = acs.tmp;
1669 /* converts to AC_AST ACL */
1670 aclp->subc = rewrite_acl(aclp->subc, aclp->dtype, aclp->id);
1671
1672 if (!sptr_supplied) {
1673 acs.tmp = sptr = convert_ctmp_array_to_param(sptr, aclp);
1674 }
1675
1676 ast = mk_id(sptr);
1677 SST_IDP(&tmp_sst, S_IDENT);
1678 SST_ASTP(&tmp_sst, ast);
1679 SST_DTYPEP(&tmp_sst, DTYPEG(sptr));
1680 SST_SHAPEP(&tmp_sst, A_SHAPEG(ast));
1681 ivl = dinit_varref(&tmp_sst);
1682 dinit(ivl, aclp);
1683 } else if (acs.is_const) {
1684 if (sptr_supplied) {
1685 acs.tmp = 0;
1686 } else {
1687 acs.tmp = get_arr_const(acs.arrtype);
1688 }
1689
1690 /* converts AC_AST to AC_IEXPR. */
1691 aclp->subc = rewrite_acl(aclp->subc, aclp->dtype, aclp->id);
1692 } else {
1693 int std;
1694 if (sem.arrdim.ndefer) {
1695 ALLOCATE_ARRAYS = 0; /* allocate for these array temps is done here */
1696 }
1697
1698 if (sem.arrdim.ndefer && sem.arrfn.sptr > NOSYM &&
1699 sem.arrfn.return_value &&
1700 ADD_DEFER(A_DTYPEG(sem.arrfn.return_value)) &&
1701 aclp->id == AC_ACONST && aclp->subc->id == AC_IDO) {
1702 /* The ACL is an array constructor that contains implied-do loop, and
1703 * there is a function call that returns a deferred-length array.
1704 * Create an allocatable array temp in case of that the function call
1705 * appears in the loop body and causes the size of the resulting array to
1706 * be determined at runtime.
1707 */
1708 sptr = acs.tmp = get_adjlr_arr_temp(acs.arrtype);
1709 get_static_descriptor(acs.tmp);
1710 get_all_descriptors(acs.tmp);
1711 } else
1712 sptr = acs.tmp = get_arr_temp(acs.arrtype, FALSE, FALSE, FALSE);
1713 ALLOCATE_ARRAYS = 1;
1714 if (sem.arrdim.ndefer) {
1715 sem.bounds[0].lwast = astb.bnd.one;
1716 sem.bounds[0].upast = aclp->size;
1717 /* assign values to the bounds temporaries and allocate the
1718 * array.
1719 */
1720 std = STD_PREV(0);
1721 gen_allocate_array(acs.tmp);
1722 std = STD_NEXT(std);
1723 }
1724
1725 acs.func_in_do = FALSE;
1726 /* generate code to assign aclp values to the temporary */
1727 constructf90(acs.tmp, aclp);
1728
1729 /* If the function call returns a deferred-length array or adjustable
1730 * array, and it appears in the loop body, the bounds of the function
1731 * return array is uninitialized when used in the allocation of array temp.
1732 * Here we set the function return array to be zero-sized before the
1733 * allocation.
1734 */
1735 if (acs.func_in_do && sem.arrdim.ndefer && sem.arrfn.return_value) {
1736 int ret_sptr, dtype, ndim, i;
1737
1738 ret_sptr = A_SPTRG(sem.arrfn.return_value);
1739 dtype = DTYPEG(ret_sptr);
1740 ndim = ADD_NUMDIM(dtype);
1741 if (ADJARRG(ret_sptr)) {
1742 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
1743 int lb = ADD_LWBD(dtype, i);
1744 int ub = ADD_UPBD(dtype, i);
1745 assert(A_TYPEG(lb) == A_ID, "init_sptr_w_acl: lb not id", lb,
1746 ERR_Fatal);
1747 assert(A_TYPEG(ub) == A_ID, "init_sptr_w_acl: ub not id", ub,
1748 ERR_Fatal);
1749 (void)add_stmt_before(
1750 mk_assn_stmt(lb, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype), std);
1751 (void)add_stmt_before(
1752 mk_assn_stmt(ub, astb.bnd.zero, astb.bnd.dtype), std);
1753 }
1754 } else if (SDSCG(ret_sptr)) {
1755 int sdsc = SDSCG(ret_sptr);
1756 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
1757 int lb = lbound_of(dtype, i);
1758 int extnt = ADD_EXTNTAST(dtype, i);
1759 assert(A_TYPEG(lb) == A_SUBSCR, "init_sptr_w_acl: lb not subs", lb,
1760 ERR_Fatal);
1761 assert(memsym_of_ast(lb) == sdsc, "init_sptr_w_acl: lb not sdsc", lb,
1762 ERR_Fatal);
1763 assert(A_TYPEG(extnt) == A_SUBSCR, "init_sptr_w_acl: extnt not subs",
1764 extnt, ERR_Fatal);
1765 assert(memsym_of_ast(extnt) == sdsc,
1766 "init_sptr_w_acl: extnt not sdsc", extnt, ERR_Fatal);
1767 (void)add_stmt_before(
1768 mk_assn_stmt(lb, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype), std);
1769 (void)add_stmt_before(
1770 mk_assn_stmt(extnt, astb.bnd.zero, astb.bnd.dtype), std);
1771 }
1772 }
1773 }
1774 acs.tmp = sptr; /* if we recursed, asc.tmp may have changed */
1775 }
1776
1777 /* if the user didn't supply an sptr, use the temporary
1778 created above. */
1779 if (!sptr_supplied) {
1780 sptr = acs.tmp;
1781 }
1782
1783 if (acs.is_const) {
1784 if (!sem.dinit_data) {
1785 dinit_constructor(sptr, aclp);
1786 } else if (sptr_supplied) {
1787 interr("acl not resolved as constant", sptr, 2);
1788 }
1789 }
1790 restore_dim_specs(&dim_specs_tmp);
1791 return sptr;
1792}
1793
1794/* add_flag gets set to false, when we see a SCONST. We want to
1795 recurse on structure constructor to set acs.is_const, but we
1796 don't want to add to the counts for any components of the
1797 structure constructor.
1798 Convert the dtype to the dtype passed as argument.
1799 */
1800static void
1801compute_size(bool add_flag, ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
1802{
1803 for (; aclp != NULL; aclp = aclp->next) {
1804 switch (aclp->id) {
1805 case AC_AST:
1806 compute_size_ast(add_flag, aclp, dtype);
1807 break;
1808 case AC_EXPR:
1809 dtype = compute_size_expr(add_flag, aclp, dtype);
1810 break;
1811 case AC_ACONST:
1812 compute_size(add_flag, aclp->subc, dtype);
1813 break;
1814 case AC_SCONST:
1815 compute_size_sconst(add_flag, aclp, dtype);
1816 break;
1817 case AC_IDO: {
1818 int save_start, save_end, save_level;
1819 DOINFO *save_doinfo = NULL;
1820 LOGICAL saved = FALSE;
1821 IDO_INFO *ido = (IDO_INFO *)getitem(0, sizeof(IDO_INFO));
1822 ido->doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
1823 ido->next = acs.ido_list;
1824 /* start processing of implied-do */
1825 acs.ido_list = ido;
1826 acs.ido_level++;
1827 if (acs.loop_stmts.level != 0 &&
1828 acs.ido_level == acs.loop_stmts.level) {
1829 /* save information before computing size of implied-do */
1830 save_start = acs.loop_stmts.start;
1831 save_end = acs.loop_stmts.end;
1832 save_level = acs.loop_stmts.level;
1833 save_doinfo = acs.loop_stmts.doinfo;
1834 saved = TRUE;
1835 acs.loop_stmts.start = 0;
1836 acs.loop_stmts.end = 0;
1837 acs.loop_stmts.level = 0;
1838 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo = NULL;
1839 }
1840 compute_size_ido(add_flag, aclp, dtype);
1841 if (saved) {
1842 if (acs.loop_stmts.level == 0) {
1843 /* restore information after computing size of implied-do */
1844 acs.loop_stmts.start = save_start;
1845 acs.loop_stmts.end = save_end;
1846 acs.loop_stmts.level = save_level;
1847 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo = save_doinfo;
1848 } else {
1849 move_range_before(save_start, save_end, acs.loop_stmts.start);
1850 acs.loop_stmts.start = save_start;
1851 /* update acs.loop_stmts.doinfo */
1852 for (IDO_INFO *iter = acs.ido_list; iter; iter = iter->next) {
1853 if (iter->doinfo == save_doinfo) {
1854 break;
1855 }
1856 if (iter->doinfo == acs.loop_stmts.doinfo) {
1857 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo = save_doinfo;
1858 break;
1859 }
1860 }
1861 }
1862 }
1863 /* finish processing of implied-do */
1864 acs.ido_level--;
1865 acs.ido_list = acs.ido_list->next;
1866 if (sem.dinit_error) {
1867 return;
1868 }
1869 break;
1870 }
1871 default:
1872 interr("compute_size,ill.id", aclp->id, 3);
1873 }
1874 }
1875}
1876
1877static void
1878compute_size_ast(bool add_flag, ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
1879{
1880 if (acs.eltype == 0 || acs.zln) {
1881 if (acs.eltype != 0) {
1882 acs.zln = 0;
1883 }
1884 if (dtype == 0) {
1885 dtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(aclp->u1.ast));
1886 }
1887 if (A_TYPEG(aclp->u1.ast) == A_ID) {
1888 dtype = fix_dtype(A_SPTRG(aclp->u1.ast), dtype);
1889 }
1890 acs.eltype = dtype;
1891 switch (DTY(acs.eltype)) {
1892 case TY_CHAR:
1893 case TY_NCHAR:
1894 if (A_ALIASG(DTY(acs.eltype + 1)) &&
1895 get_isz_cval(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(DTY(acs.eltype + 1)))) == 0) {
1896 acs.zln = 1;
1897 }
1898 }
1899 }
1900 if (add_flag)
1901 acs.scalar_cnt++;
1902}
1903
1904static DTYPE
1905compute_size_expr(bool add_flag, ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
1906{
1907 DTYPE dt2, dtype2;
1908 SST *stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
1909 LOGICAL specified_dtype = dtype != 0;
1910 DTYPE dt = DDTG(dtype);
1911 dtype2 = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1912 dt2 = DDTG(SST_DTYPEG(stkp));
1913 if (!specified_dtype) {
1914 dtype = dtype2;
1915 dt = dt2;
1916 }
1917
1918 if (acs.eltype == 0 || acs.zln) {
1919 int id = SST_IDG(stkp);
1920 if (acs.eltype != 0) {
1921 acs.zln = 0;
1922 }
1923 if (id == S_IDENT) {
1924 dt = fix_dtype(SST_SYMG(stkp), dt);
1925 } else if (id == S_EXPR || id == S_LVALUE) {
1926 if (dtype == DT_ASSCHAR || dtype == DT_DEFERCHAR
1927 || dtype == DT_ASSNCHAR || dtype == DT_DEFERNCHAR
1928 ) {
1929 dt = adjust_ch_length(dt, SST_ASTG(stkp));
1930 } else if (dt == DT_ASSCHAR || dt == DT_DEFERCHAR
1931 || dt == DT_ASSNCHAR || dt == DT_DEFERNCHAR
1932 ) {
1933 dt = fix_dtype(SST_SYMG(stkp), dt);
1934 }
1935 }
1936 /* need to change the type for the first element too */
1937 if (specified_dtype && acs.eltype == 0 &&
1938 add_flag) { /* if we're in a struct, don't do */
1939 if (DTY(dt) == TY_CHAR && DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR) {
1940 if (dtype2 != DT_DEFERCHAR && dtype2 != DT_DEFERNCHAR)
1941 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1942 } else if (DTY(dt) == TY_NCHAR && DTY(dtype) == TY_NCHAR) {
1943 if (dtype2 != DT_DEFERCHAR && dtype2 != DT_DEFERNCHAR)
1944 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1945 } else if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
1946 if (DDTG(dtype) != dt) {
1947 errsev(95);
1948 }
1949 } else {
1950 cngtyp(stkp, acs.eltype);
1951 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1952 }
1953 }
1954 acs.eltype = dt;
1955 switch (DTY(acs.eltype)) {
1956 case TY_CHAR:
1957 case TY_NCHAR:
1958 if (A_ALIASG(DTY(acs.eltype + 1)) &&
1959 get_isz_cval(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(DTY(acs.eltype + 1)))) == 0) {
1960 acs.zln = 1;
1961 }
1962 }
1963 } else {
1964 /* don't use chktyp here; chktyp evals semantic stack entry
1965 * causes S_CONST to become S_EXPR.
1966 */
1967 if (add_flag) { /* if we're in a struct, don't do */
1968 if (DTY(dt) == TY_CHAR && DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR) {
1969 if (dtype2 != DT_DEFERCHAR && dtype2 != DT_DEFERNCHAR)
1970 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1971 } else if (DTY(dt) == TY_NCHAR && DTY(dtype) == TY_NCHAR) {
1972 if (dtype2 != DT_DEFERCHAR && dtype2 != DT_DEFERNCHAR)
1973 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1974 } else if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
1975 if (is_dtype_runtime_length_char(dtype) &&
1976 is_dtype_runtime_length_char(acs.eltype)) {
1977 // AC element could have adjusted length. The length mismatch should
1978 // be checked in runtime when -fcheck=bounds is enabled.
1979 } else if (!eq_dtype(DDTG(dtype), acs.eltype)) {
1980 errsev(95);
1981 }
1982 } else {
1983 cngtyp(stkp, acs.eltype);
1984 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
1985 }
1986 }
1987 }
1988 switch (SST_IDG(stkp)) {
1989 case S_ACONST:
1990 interr("compute_size, AC_ACONST in AC_EXPR", 0, 3);
1991 if (add_flag)
1992 acs.scalar_cnt += CONVAL2G(sym_of_ast(AD_NUMELM(AD_DPTR(dtype))));
1993 break;
1994 case S_CONST:
1995 mkexpr(stkp);
1996 if (add_flag)
1997 acs.scalar_cnt++;
1998 break;
1999 default:
2000 mkexpr(stkp);
2001 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY) {
2002 int ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
2003 if (add_flag)
2004 acs.scalar_cnt++;
2005 if (!ast) {
2006 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2007 } else if (A_ALIASG(ast) || (acs.level && _can_fold(ast))) {
2008 /* do nothing */
2009 } else if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID) {
2010 int sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
2011 if (STYPEG(sptr) != ST_VAR || !PARAMVALG(sptr)) {
2012 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2013 }
2014 } else {
2015 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2016 }
2017 } else {
2018 int ast;
2019 if (add_flag) {
2020 int sz = size_of_ast((int)SST_ASTG(stkp));
2021 if (A_ALIASG(sz))
2022 acs.scalar_cnt += ad_val_of(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(sz)));
2023 else
2024 acs.aggr_cnt = mk_binop(OP_ADD, acs.aggr_cnt, sz, astb.bnd.dtype);
2025 }
2026 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
2027 if (!ast) {
2028 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2029 } else if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID) {
2030 int sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
2031 if (STYPEG(sptr) != ST_ARRAY || !PARAMVALG(sptr)) {
2032 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2033 }
2034 } else if (!_can_fold(ast)) {
2035 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2036 }
2037 }
2038 }
2039 return specified_dtype ? dtype : DT_NONE;
2040}
2041
2042/* Check dependencies and find the outermost implied-do loop
2043 * on which the array size depends.
2044 */
2045static void
2046check_dependence_ido(ACL *aclp)
2047{
2048 DOINFO *cur_ido = aclp->u1.doinfo;
2049 STD_RANGE *range = aclp->u2.std_range;
2050 int level = acs.ido_level - 1;
2051
2052 for (IDO_INFO *ido = acs.ido_list->next; ido; ido = ido->next) {
2053 int dovar_id = mk_id(ido->doinfo->index_var);
2054 LOGICAL depend = FALSE;
2055 if (contains_ast(acs.aggr_cnt, dovar_id) ||
2056 contains_ast(cur_ido->init_expr, dovar_id) ||
2057 contains_ast(cur_ido->limit_expr, dovar_id) ||
2058 contains_ast(cur_ido->step_expr, dovar_id)) {
2059 /* direct dependence */
2060 depend = TRUE;
2061 }
2062
2063 if (!depend && range != NULL && range->mid != range->end) {
2064 for (int std = STD_NEXT(range->mid); std; std = STD_NEXT(std)) {
2065 if (contains_ast(STD_AST(std), dovar_id)) {
2066 /* indirect dependence */
2067 depend = TRUE;
2068 break;
2069 }
2070 if (std == range->end)
2071 break;
2072 }
2073 }
2074 /* update information about the loop on which current implied-do depends */
2075 if (depend && (acs.loop_stmts.level == 0 ||
2076 acs.loop_stmts.level > level)) {
2077 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo = ido->doinfo;
2078 }
2079 level--;
2080 }
2081}
2082
2083/* When computing the size of AC_IDO, clone the stmts on which the bounds of
2084 * the current implied-do loop depend, and generate loop to compute size.
2085 */
2086static void
2087handle_dependence_ido(ACL *aclp)
2088{
2089 int sumid;
2090 int prev_std;
2091 STD_RANGE *range = aclp->u2.std_range;
2092 DOINFO *doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
2093
2094 if (acs.loop_stmts.start == 0 && acs.loop_stmts.end == 0) {
2095 prev_std = STD_LAST;
2096 } else {
2097 prev_std = STD_PREV(acs.loop_stmts.start);
2098 }
2099
2100 /* create temp for size at the beginning and initialize it with zero */
2101 if (acs.loop_stmts.sumid == 0) {
2102 acs.loop_stmts.sumid = mk_id(get_temp(astb.bnd.dtype));
2103 }
2104 sumid = acs.loop_stmts.sumid;
2105 if (acs.loop_stmts.doinfo == doinfo) {
2106 (void)add_stmt(mk_assn_stmt(sumid, astb.bnd.zero, astb.bnd.dtype));
2107 }
2108
2109 /* clone stmts on which the bounds of current implied-do depend */
2110 if (range != NULL && range->mid != range->end) {
2111 for (int std = STD_NEXT(range->mid); std; std = STD_NEXT(std)) {
2112 (void)add_stmt(STD_AST(std));
2113 if (std == range->end)
2114 break;
2115 }
2116 }
2117
2118 if (acs.loop_stmts.level == 0) {
2119 /* current implied-do is the outermost one */
2120 int st, ast;
2121 st = doinfo->step_expr == 0 ? astb.bnd.one : doinfo->step_expr;
2122 ast = mk_binop(OP_SUB, doinfo->limit_expr, doinfo->init_expr,
2123 astb.bnd.dtype);
2124 ast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, ast, st, astb.bnd.dtype);
2125 ast = mk_binop(OP_DIV, ast, st, astb.bnd.dtype);
2126 ast = mk_binop(OP_MUL, ast, acs.aggr_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype);
2127 ast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2128 (void)add_stmt(mk_assn_stmt(sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype));
2129 } else {
2130 /* generate loop to compute size */
2131 SPTR dovar, odovar;
2132 int newid, ast;
2133 int do_beg_std;
2134
2135 odovar = doinfo->index_var;
2136 dovar = get_temp(DTYPEG(odovar));
2137 HIDDENP(dovar, 1);
2138 newid = mk_id(dovar);
2139 ast = mk_stmt(A_DO, 0);
2140 A_DOVARP(ast, newid);
2141 A_M1P(ast, doinfo->init_expr);
2142 A_M2P(ast, doinfo->limit_expr);
2143 A_M3P(ast, doinfo->step_expr);
2144 A_M4P(ast, 0);
2145 do_beg_std = add_stmt(ast);
2146
2147 ast_visit(1, 1);
2148 ast_replace(mk_id(odovar), newid);
2149 move_range_after(acs.loop_stmts.start, acs.loop_stmts.end, do_beg_std);
2150 for (int std = STD_NEXT(do_beg_std); std; std = STD_NEXT(std)) {
2151 STD_AST(std) = ast_rewrite(STD_AST(std));
2152 }
2153
2154 /* add size */
2155 if (acs.aggr_cnt != astb.bnd.zero) {
2156 ast = ast_rewrite(acs.aggr_cnt);
2157 ast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2158 (void)add_stmt(mk_assn_stmt(sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype));
2159 }
2160 ast_unvisit();
2161 (void)add_stmt(mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0));
2162 }
2163
2164 if (acs.loop_stmts.doinfo == aclp->u1.doinfo) {
2165 /* remove information about dependence of implied-do */
2166 acs.aggr_cnt = sumid;
2167 acs.loop_stmts.start = 0;
2168 acs.loop_stmts.end = 0;
2169 acs.loop_stmts.level = 0;
2170 acs.loop_stmts.sumid = 0;
2171 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo = NULL;
2172 } else {
2173 acs.aggr_cnt = astb.bnd.zero;
2174 acs.loop_stmts.start = STD_NEXT(prev_std);
2175 acs.loop_stmts.end = STD_LAST;
2176 acs.loop_stmts.level = acs.ido_level;
2177 }
2178}
2179
2180static void
2181compute_size_ido(bool add_flag, ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
2182{
2183 DOINFO *doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
2184 INT initval, limitval, stepval;
2185 int save_scalar_cnt, save_aggr_cnt;
2186 int id;
2187 if (sem.dinit_data) {
2188 /* set up for the possibility that a nested implied
2189 * do will require counting the number of elements
2190 */
2191 sem.top->sptr = aclp->u1.doinfo->index_var;
2192 sem.top->currval = initval = dinit_eval(doinfo->init_expr);
2193 if (sem.dinit_error) {
2194 return;
2195 }
2196 sem.top->upbd = limitval = dinit_eval(doinfo->limit_expr);
2197 if (sem.dinit_error) {
2198 return;
2199 }
2200 sem.top->step = stepval = dinit_eval(doinfo->step_expr);
2201 if (sem.dinit_error) {
2202 return;
2203 }
2204 sem.top++;
2205
2206 if (A_ALIASG(doinfo->count)) {
2207 acs.level++;
2208 DOVARP(doinfo->index_var, 1);
2209 }
2210 }
2211 if (add_flag) {
2212 save_scalar_cnt = acs.scalar_cnt;
2213 save_aggr_cnt = acs.aggr_cnt;
2214 /*
2215 * scalar_cnt & aggr_cnt will reflect the number of items
2216 * immediately contained by this implied do.
2217 */
2218 acs.scalar_cnt = 0;
2219 acs.aggr_cnt = astb.bnd.zero;
2220 }
2221 compute_size(add_flag, aclp->subc, dtype);
2222 /*
2223 * size is the 'cnt*scalar_cnt + cnt*aggr_cnt'
2224 */
2225 id = mk_id(doinfo->index_var);
2226 check_dependence_ido(aclp);
2227 if (add_flag && (contains_ast(acs.aggr_cnt, id) ||
2228 acs.loop_stmts.doinfo != NULL)) {
2229 /* The size expression depends on the loop index variable.
2230 * This is tricky because we need the size to allocate
2231 * the temporary before we generate the loop. First,
2232 * if there is a scalar_cnt, convert it to an expression
2233 * to be added later (size can't be a constant now).
2234 */
2235 if (acs.scalar_cnt != 0) {
2236 acs.aggr_cnt =
2237 mk_binop(OP_ADD, acs.aggr_cnt,
2238 mk_isz_cval(acs.scalar_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype), astb.bnd.dtype);
2239 acs.scalar_cnt = 0;
2240 }
2241 /* Now we need to evaluate the size expression for each
2242 * value of the loop index variable and add the results.
2243 * There are two cases:
2244 */
2245 if (A_ALIASG(doinfo->init_expr) && A_ALIASG(doinfo->limit_expr) &&
2246 A_ALIASG(doinfo->step_expr) && acs.loop_stmts.doinfo == NULL) {
2247 int i;
2248 int ast;
2249
2250 /* In the easy case, the loop control expressions are
2251 * constants, so we can iterate at compile time,
2252 * substituting each value of the loop variable and
2253 * adding the sizes.
2254 */
2255 initval = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(doinfo->init_expr)));
2256 limitval = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(doinfo->limit_expr)));
2257 stepval = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(doinfo->step_expr)));
2258 ast = astb.bnd.zero;
2259 if (stepval >= 0) {
2260 for (i = initval; i <= limitval; i += stepval) {
2261 ast_visit(1, 1);
2262 ast_replace(id, mk_cval(i, astb.bnd.dtype));
2263 ast =
2264 mk_binop(OP_ADD, ast, ast_rewrite(acs.aggr_cnt), astb.bnd.dtype);
2265 ast_unvisit();
2266 }
2267 } else {
2268 for (i = initval; i >= limitval; i += stepval) {
2269 ast_visit(1, 1);
2270 ast_replace(id, mk_cval(i, astb.bnd.dtype));
2271 ast =
2272 mk_binop(OP_ADD, ast, ast_rewrite(acs.aggr_cnt), astb.bnd.dtype);
2273 ast_unvisit();
2274 }
2275 }
2276 acs.aggr_cnt = ast;
2277 } else if (acs.loop_stmts.doinfo != NULL) {
2278 handle_dependence_ido(aclp);
2279 } else {
2280 /* Non-constant loop control expression(s).
2281 * Must generate a run-time loop to add sizes.
2282 */
2283 int odovar, dovar, sum, sumid, newid, doif;
2284 DOINFO newdoinfo;
2285 int ast;
2286
2287 /* Duplicate loop info, but substitute a new index var. */
2288 newdoinfo = *doinfo;
2289 odovar = doinfo->index_var;
2290 dovar = get_temp(DDTG(DTYPEG(odovar)));
2291 STYPEP(dovar, STYPEG(odovar));
2292 DTYPEP(dovar, DTYPEG(odovar));
2293 if (SCG(odovar) == SC_PRIVATE) {
2294 SCP(dovar, SC_PRIVATE);
2295 } else {
2296 SCP(dovar, SC_LOCAL);
2297 }
2298 HIDDENP(dovar, 1);
2299 newdoinfo.index_var = dovar;
2300 newid = mk_id(dovar);
2301
2302 /* Get a temp for the sum and initialize to zero. */
2303 sum = get_temp(astb.bnd.dtype);
2304 sumid = mk_id(sum);
2305 ast = mk_assn_stmt(sumid, astb.bnd.zero, astb.bnd.dtype);
2306 add_stmt(ast);
2307
2308 /* Rewrite the size expression to use the new index var. */
2309 ast_visit(1, 1);
2310 ast_replace(id, newid);
2311 ast = ast_rewrite(acs.aggr_cnt);
2312 ast_unvisit();
2313
2314 /* Generate the loop. */
2315 NEED_DOIF(doif, DI_DO);
2316 add_stmt(do_begin(&newdoinfo));
2317 ast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2318 ast = mk_assn_stmt(sumid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2319 add_stmt(ast);
2320 do_end(&newdoinfo);
2321
2322 /* Size is now in our sum temporary. */
2323 acs.aggr_cnt = sumid;
2324 }
2325 } else if (A_ALIASG(doinfo->count)) {
2326 if (add_flag) {
2327 int v = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(doinfo->count)));
2328 acs.scalar_cnt *= v;
2329 acs.aggr_cnt = mk_binop(OP_MUL, acs.aggr_cnt, mk_cval(v, astb.bnd.dtype),
2330 astb.bnd.dtype);
2331 }
2332 if (sem.dinit_data) {
2333 acs.level--;
2334 DOVARP(doinfo->index_var, 0);
2335 } else
2336 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2337 } else if (sem.dinit_data) {
2338 /* TODO: why is this not a simple division?? */
2339 /* must count them */
2340 int i, v = 0;
2341 for (i = initval; i <= limitval; i += stepval, v++)
2342 ;
2343
2344 acs.scalar_cnt *= v;
2345 if (v) {
2346 acs.aggr_cnt = mk_binop(OP_MUL, acs.aggr_cnt, mk_cval(v, astb.bnd.dtype),
2347 astb.bnd.dtype);
2348 acs.level--;
2349 DOVARP(doinfo->index_var, 0);
2350 }
2351 } else {
2352 if (add_flag) {
2353 if (acs.scalar_cnt != 0) {
2354 acs.aggr_cnt = mk_binop(OP_ADD, acs.aggr_cnt,
2355 mk_isz_cval(acs.scalar_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype),
2356 astb.bnd.dtype);
2357 acs.scalar_cnt = 0;
2358 }
2359 acs.aggr_cnt =
2360 mk_binop(OP_MUL, doinfo->count, acs.aggr_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype);
2361 }
2362 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2363 }
2364 if (add_flag) {
2365 /*
2366 * fold counts due to the implied do into the totals
2367 */
2368 acs.scalar_cnt += save_scalar_cnt;
2369 acs.aggr_cnt =
2370 mk_binop(OP_ADD, acs.aggr_cnt, save_aggr_cnt, astb.bnd.dtype);
2371 }
2372 if (sem.dinit_data) {
2373 sem.top--;
2374 }
2375}
2376
2377static void
2378compute_size_sconst(bool add_flag, ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype)
2379{
2380 if (add_flag) {
2381 acs.scalar_cnt++;
2382 }
2383 if (acs.eltype == 0) {
2384 acs.eltype = dtype != 0 ? dtype : aclp->dtype;
2385 }
2386 compute_size(false, aclp->subc, dtype);
2387 if (ALLOCFLDG(DTY(aclp->dtype + 3))) {
2388 acs.is_const = FALSE;
2389 }
2390}
2391
2392static LOGICAL
2393_can_fold(int ast)
2394{
2395 int sptr, asd, ndim, i, b;
2396
2397 if (ast == 0)
2398 return FALSE;
2399 if (A_ALIASG(ast))
2400 return TRUE;
2401 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
2402 case A_ID:
2403 /* see if this ident is an active do index variable: */
2404 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
2405 if (DOVARG(sptr))
2406 return TRUE;
2407
2408 /* if the ID has PARAMVAL, subscripts are foldable */
2409 if (PARAMVALG(sptr))
2410 return TRUE;
2411 break;
2412
2413 case A_MEM:
2414 return _can_fold(A_PARENTG(ast));
2415
2416 case A_SUBSCR:
2417 if (!_can_fold(A_LOPG(ast)))
2418 return FALSE;
2419 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
2420 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
2421 for (i = 0; i < ndim; ++i) {
2422 int ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
2423 if (!_can_fold(ss))
2424 return FALSE;
2425 }
2426 return TRUE;
2427 break;
2428
2429 case A_TRIPLE:
2430 b = A_LBDG(ast);
2431 if (b == 0 || !_can_fold(b))
2432 return FALSE;
2433 b = A_UPBDG(ast);
2434 if (b == 0 || !_can_fold(b))
2435 return FALSE;
2436 b = A_STRIDEG(ast);
2437 if (b != 0 && !_can_fold(b))
2438 return FALSE;
2439 return TRUE;
2440 break;
2441
2442 case A_CNST:
2443 return TRUE;
2444
2445 case A_UNOP:
2446 if (!DT_ISINT(A_DTYPEG(ast)))
2447 return FALSE;
2448 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == OP_SUB)
2449 return _can_fold((int)A_LOPG(ast));
2450 break;
2451
2452 case A_BINOP:
2453 if (!DT_ISINT(A_DTYPEG(ast)))
2454 return FALSE;
2455 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
2456 case OP_ADD:
2457 case OP_SUB:
2458 case OP_MUL:
2459 case OP_DIV:
2460 if (!_can_fold((int)A_LOPG(ast)))
2461 return FALSE;
2462 return _can_fold((int)A_ROPG(ast));
2463 }
2464 break;
2465
2466 case A_CONV:
2467 case A_PAREN:
2468 return _can_fold((int)A_LOPG(ast));
2469
2470 default:
2471 break;
2472 }
2473 return FALSE;
2474}
2475
2476/* ------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
2477/* small routines used by constructf90(). generate subscripts as they are
2478 * needed. */
2479
2480static int sub_i = 7;
2481static int tmpids[MAXDIMS];
2482
2483static void
2484init_constructf90()
2485{
2486 int i;
2487
2488 for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {
2489 acs.element_cnt[i] = 0; /* # of individual constructor items */
2490 acs.indx[i] = astb.bnd.one; /* subscript of first element */
2491 acs.indx_tmpid[i] = 0; /* no subscripting temporary yet */
2492 acs.subs[i] = astb.bnd.one;
2493 tmpids[i] = 0;
2494 }
2495 sub_i = 7;
2496}
2497
2498static int
2499add_subscript(int base_id, int indexast, DTYPE dtype)
2500{
2501 int dest;
2502
2503 acs.subs[sub_i] = indexast;
2504 /* generate subscripts as they are seen */
2505 dest = mk_subscr(base_id, &acs.subs[sub_i], 1, dtype);
2506 return dest;
2507}
2508
2509static int
2510apply_shape_subscripts(int base_id, int shp, DTYPE dtype)
2511{
2512 int dest;
2513 int i, ndim;
2514 int ast;
2515 int subs[MAXDIMS];
2516
2517 ndim = SHD_NDIM(shp);
2518 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
2519 ast = mk_triple(SHD_LWB(shp, i), SHD_UPB(shp, i), SHD_STRIDE(shp, i));
2520 subs[i] = ast;
2521 }
2522 dest = mk_subscr(base_id, subs, ndim, dtype);
2523 return dest;
2524}
2525
2526static void
2527push_subscript()
2528{
2529 sub_i--;
2530}
2531
2532static void
2533pop_subscript()
2534{
2535 sub_i++;
2536}
2537
2538static void
2539clear_element_cnt()
2540{
2541 acs.element_cnt[sub_i] = 0;
2542}
2543
2544static void
2545incr_element_cnt()
2546{
2547 acs.element_cnt[sub_i]++;
2548}
2549
2550static INT
2551get_element_cnt()
2552{
2553 return acs.element_cnt[sub_i];
2554}
2555
2556static int
2557get_subscripting_tmp(int indexast)
2558{
2559 int ast;
2560
2561 if (!tmpids[sub_i])
2562 tmpids[sub_i] = mk_id(get_temp(astb.bnd.dtype));
2563 if (indexast != tmpids[sub_i]) {
2564 ast = mk_assn_stmt(tmpids[sub_i], indexast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2565 add_stmt(ast);
2566 }
2567 return (tmpids[sub_i]);
2568}
2569
2570static void
2571incr_tmp(int tmpid)
2572{
2573 int ast;
2574
2575 ast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, tmpid, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
2576 ast = mk_assn_stmt(tmpid, ast, astb.bnd.dtype);
2577 add_stmt(ast);
2578}
2579
2580#define THRESHHOLD 20
2581
2582static int
2583size_of_shape_dim(int shape, int i)
2584{
2585 int sz;
2586 if (SHD_LWB(shape, i) == SHD_STRIDE(shape, i)) {
2587 sz = SHD_UPB(shape, i);
2588 } else {
2589 sz = mk_binop(OP_SUB, SHD_UPB(shape, i), SHD_LWB(shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
2590 sz = mk_binop(OP_ADD, sz, SHD_STRIDE(shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
2591 }
2592 if (SHD_STRIDE(shape, i) != astb.bnd.one) {
2593 sz = mk_binop(OP_DIV, sz, SHD_STRIDE(shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
2594 }
2595 return sz;
2596} /* size_of_shape_dim */
2597
2598static int
2599get_shape_arraydtype(int shape, int eltype)
2600{
2601 int arrtype, i, n;
2602 int sz;
2603 LOGICAL need_alloc = FALSE;
2604
2605 n = sem.arrdim.ndim = SHD_NDIM(shape);
2606 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 0;
2607
2608 for (i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
2609 sem.bounds[i].lowtype = S_CONST;
2610 sem.bounds[i].lowb = 1;
2611 sem.bounds[i].lwast = 0;
2612
2613 sz = size_of_shape_dim(shape, i);
2614 if (A_ALIASG(sz) && (ad_val_of(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(sz))) < THRESHHOLD)) {
2615 /* small constant size */
2616 sem.bounds[i].uptype = S_CONST;
2617 sem.bounds[i].upb = ad_val_of(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(sz)));
2618 sem.bounds[i].upast = sz;
2619 } else {
2620 sem.bounds[i].uptype = S_EXPR;
2621 sem.bounds[i].upb = 0;
2622 sem.bounds[i].upast = sz;
2623 need_alloc = TRUE;
2624 }
2625 }
2626
2627 if (is_deferlenchar_dtype(acs.arrtype))
2628 need_alloc = TRUE;
2629
2630 if (need_alloc)
2631 sem.arrdim.ndefer = n;
2632 arrtype = mk_arrdsc();
2633 DTY(arrtype + 1) = eltype;
2634 return arrtype;
2635} /* get_shape_arraydtype */
2636
2637static void
2638mkexpr_assign_temp(SST *stkptr)
2639{
2640 int ast, a, simple;
2641 DTYPE dtype;
2642 int dest;
2643 int id;
2644
2645 mkexpr(stkptr);
2646 /* may have to change to create temp based on shape if we are in
2647 structure and doing array assignment of a multiple dimension array. */
2648
2649 simple = 1;
2650 ast = SST_ASTG(stkptr);
2651 for (a = ast; a > 0;) {
2652 switch (A_TYPEG(a)) {
2653 case A_ID:
2654 a = 0;
2655 break;
2656 case A_MEM:
2657 a = A_PARENTG(a);
2658 break;
2659 default:
2660 simple = 0;
2661 a = 0;
2662 break;
2663 }
2664 }
2665 /* if we have an array expression, we need to assign it to
2666 a temporary so that we can subscript it. */
2667 if (DTY(dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkptr)) == TY_ARRAY && !simple) {
2668 if (is_deferlenchar_ast(ast)) {
2669 dtype = get_shape_arraydtype(A_SHAPEG(ast), DTY(acs.arrtype + 1));
2670 } else {
2671 dtype = get_shape_arraydtype(A_SHAPEG(ast), DTY(dtype + 1));
2672 }
2673 id = get_arr_temp(dtype, FALSE, FALSE, FALSE);
2674 if (sem.arrdim.ndefer)
2675 gen_allocate_array(id);
2676 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
2677 dest = mk_id(id);
2678 ast = mk_assn_stmt(dest, ast, dtype);
2679 add_stmt(ast);
2680 SST_ASTP(stkptr, dest);
2681 }
2682}
2683
2684/* if we have a%b, a and b are arrays, subscripts i,j,
2685 * turn this into a(i)%b(j); this is overkill, since F90
2686 * only allows one vector subscript in a member tree */
2687static int
2688add_dt_subscr(int ast, int *subs, int numdim)
2689{
2690 int lop, dtype;
2691 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
2692 case A_SUBSCR:
2693 /* already have the subscripts */
2694 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
2695 if (A_TYPEG(lop) == A_ID) {
2696 assert(numdim == 0, "add_dt_subscr: too many subscripts", numdim, 3);
2697 } else if (A_TYPEG(lop) == A_MEM) {
2698 int parent, mem, asd, ndim, i, oldsubs[MAXDIMS];
2699 parent = add_dt_subscr(A_PARENTG(lop), subs, numdim);
2700 mem = A_MEMG(lop);
2701 dtype = DTYPEG(A_SPTRG(mem));
2702 mem = mk_member(parent, mem, dtype);
2703 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
2704 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
2705 for (i = 0; i < ndim; ++i) {
2706 oldsubs[i] = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
2707 }
2708 ast = mk_subscr(mem, oldsubs, ndim, DTY(dtype + 1));
2709 } else {
2710 interr("add_dt_subscr: unexpected subscript parent", A_TYPEG(lop), 3);
2711 }
2712 break;
2713
2714 case A_MEM:
2715 dtype = DTYPEG(A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(ast)));
2716 /* apply subscripts? */
2717 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY) {
2718 int parent;
2719 parent = add_dt_subscr(A_PARENTG(ast), subs, numdim);
2720 ast = mk_member(parent, A_MEMG(ast), dtype);
2721 } else {
2722 int parent, ndim, odim;
2723 /* take some subscripts here */
2724 ndim = ADD_NUMDIM(dtype);
2725 odim = numdim - ndim;
2726 assert(odim >= 0, "add_dt_subscr: not enough subscripts", numdim - ndim,
2727 3);
2728 parent = add_dt_subscr(A_PARENTG(ast), subs, odim);
2729 ast = mk_member(parent, A_MEMG(ast), dtype);
2730 ast = mk_subscr(ast, subs + odim, ndim, DTY(dtype + 1));
2731 }
2732 break;
2733 case A_ID:
2734 dtype = DTYPEG(A_SPTRG(ast));
2735 /* apply subscripts? */
2736 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY) {
2737 assert(numdim == 0, "add_dt_subscr: too many subscripts", numdim, 3);
2738 } else {
2739 int ndim;
2740 /* take rest of subscripts here */
2741 ndim = ADD_NUMDIM(dtype);
2742 assert(ndim == numdim, "add_dt_subscr: wrong number of subscripts",
2743 numdim - ndim, 3);
2744 ast = mk_subscr(ast, subs, ndim, DTY(dtype + 1));
2745 }
2746 break;
2747 }
2748 return ast;
2749} /* add_dt_subscr */
2750
2751static int oldindex[MAXDIMS], newindex[MAXDIMS], numindex;
2752
2753static void
2754ast_replace_index(int old, int new)
2755{
2756 oldindex[numindex] = old;
2757 newindex[numindex] = new;
2758 ++numindex;
2759} /* ast_replace_index */
2760
2761static int
2762ast_rewrite_indices(int ast)
2763{
2764 int i, newast;
2765 ast_visit(1, 1);
2766 for (i = 0; i < numindex; ++i) {
2767 ast_replace(oldindex[i], newindex[i]);
2768 }
2769 newast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2770 ast_unvisit();
2771 return newast;
2772} /* ast_rewrite_indices */
2773
2774static ACL *
2775acl_rewrite_asts(ACL *aclp)
2776{
2777 int ast, initast, limitast, countast, stepast;
2778 SST *stkp, *sst;
2779 DOINFO *doinfo;
2780 ACL *newaclp, *subc, *next;
2781
2782 newaclp = 0;
2783 if (aclp->next) {
2784 next = acl_rewrite_asts(aclp->next);
2785 if (next != aclp->next) {
2786 newaclp = GET_ACL(15);
2787 *newaclp = *aclp;
2788 newaclp->next = next;
2789 }
2790 }
2791 switch (aclp->id) {
2792 case AC_AST:
2793 ast = ast_rewrite(aclp->u1.ast);
2794 if (ast != aclp->u1.ast) {
2795 if (newaclp == 0) {
2796 newaclp = GET_ACL(15);
2797 *newaclp = *aclp;
2798 }
2799 newaclp->u1.ast = ast;
2800 }
2801 break;
2802 case AC_EXPR:
2803 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
2804 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
2805 switch (SST_IDG(stkp)) {
2806 case S_ACONST:
2807 break;
2808 case S_CONST:
2809 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2810 break;
2811 case S_SCONST:
2812 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2813 break;
2814 case S_EXPR:
2815 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2816 break;
2817 case S_LVALUE:
2818 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2819 break;
2820 case S_IDENT:
2821 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
2822 break;
2823 default:
2824 interr("acl_rewrite_asts: unknown expr type", SST_IDG(stkp), 3);
2825 break;
2826 }
2827 if (ast != SST_ASTG(stkp)) {
2828 NEW(sst, SST, SST_SIZE);
2829 if (sst == NULL)
2830 error(7, 4, 0, CNULL, CNULL);
2831 *sst = *stkp;
2832 SST_ASTP(sst, ast);
2833 if (newaclp == 0) {
2834 newaclp = GET_ACL(15);
2835 *newaclp = *aclp;
2836 }
2837 newaclp->u1.stkp = sst;
2838 }
2839 break;
2840 case AC_ACONST:
2841 case AC_SCONST:
2842 case AC_REPEAT:
2843 subc = acl_rewrite_asts(aclp->subc);
2844 if (subc != aclp->subc) {
2845 if (newaclp == 0) {
2846 newaclp = GET_ACL(15);
2847 *newaclp = *aclp;
2848 }
2849 newaclp->subc = subc;
2850 }
2851 break;
2852 case AC_IDO:
2853 doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
2854 initast = ast_rewrite(doinfo->init_expr);
2855 limitast = ast_rewrite(doinfo->limit_expr);
2856 stepast = ast_rewrite(doinfo->step_expr);
2857 countast = ast_rewrite(doinfo->count);
2858 if (initast != doinfo->init_expr || limitast != doinfo->limit_expr ||
2859 stepast != doinfo->step_expr || countast != doinfo->count) {
2860 doinfo = get_doinfo(15);
2861 *doinfo = *(aclp->u1.doinfo);
2862 doinfo->init_expr = initast;
2863 doinfo->limit_expr = limitast;
2864 doinfo->step_expr = stepast;
2865 doinfo->count = countast;
2866 }
2867 subc = acl_rewrite_asts(aclp->subc);
2868 if (doinfo != aclp->u1.doinfo || subc != aclp->subc) {
2869 if (newaclp == 0) {
2870 newaclp = GET_ACL(15);
2871 *newaclp = *aclp;
2872 }
2873 newaclp->subc = subc;
2874 newaclp->u1.doinfo = doinfo;
2875 }
2876 break;
2877 default:
2878 interr("acl_rewrite_asts: unknown ACL id", aclp->id, 3);
2879 break;
2880 }
2881 return newaclp ? newaclp : aclp;
2882} /* acl_rewrite_asts */
2883
2884static int
2885gen_null_intrin()
2886{
2887 int func_ast, ast;
2888 func_ast = mk_id(intast_sym[I_NULL]);
2889 ast = mk_func_node(A_INTR, func_ast, 0, 0);
2890 A_DTYPEP(ast, DT_WORD);
2891 EXPSTP(intast_sym[I_NULL], 1);
2892 A_OPTYPEP(ast, I_NULL);
2893 return ast;
2894}
2895
2896static int
2897_constructf90(int base_id, int in_indexast, bool in_array, ACL *aclp)
2898{
2899 int i;
2900 SST *stkp;
2901 DOINFO *doinfo;
2902 int ast;
2903 DTYPE dtype;
2904 int odovar, dovar;
2905 int dest;
2906 int src_subs[MAXDIMS];
2907 int src;
2908 int tmpsptr;
2909 int mem_sptr, mem_sptr_id, cmem_sptr;
2910 ACL *mem_aclp;
2911 ACL *tmp;
2912 int tmpid;
2913 int indexast;
2914 INT cnt;
2915 LOGICAL sdscismbr;
2916 int argt = 0;
2917 int argt_count = 0;
2918
2919 indexast = in_indexast;
2920
2921#if DEBUG
2922 if (DBGBIT(3, 64))
2923 printacl("_constructf90", aclp, gbl.dbgfil);
2924#endif
2925
2926 for (; aclp != NULL; aclp = aclp->next) {
2927 switch (aclp->id) {
2928 case AC_ACONST:
2929 if (in_array) {
2930 indexast = _constructf90(base_id, indexast, true, aclp->subc);
2931 } else {
2932 push_subscript();
2933 indexast = _constructf90(base_id, SHD_LWB(A_SHAPEG(base_id), 0), true,
2934 aclp->subc);
2935 pop_subscript();
2936 }
2937 break;
2938 case AC_SCONST:
2939 mem_aclp = aclp->subc;
2940 dtype = aclp->dtype;
2941 if (in_array)
2942 dest = add_subscript(base_id, indexast, dtype);
2943 else
2944 dest = base_id;
2945 dtype = DDTG(dtype);
2946
2947 mem_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
2948 for (; mem_sptr != NOSYM; mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr)) {
2949 if (!is_unl_poly(mem_sptr) && no_data_components(DTYPEG(mem_sptr)))
2950 continue;
2951 /* skip $td */
2952 if (CLASSG(mem_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(mem_sptr))
2953 continue;
2954 if (XBIT(58, 0x10000) && POINTERG(mem_sptr) && !F90POINTERG(mem_sptr)) {
2955 SST *astkp;
2956 int aast;
2957 int stmtast, asptr;
2958 if (!mem_aclp) {
2959 /* Check to see if there's a default
2960 * initialization for this missing element in the
2961 * structure constructor. If not, then issue an
2962 * error message.
2963 */
2964 mem_aclp = get_struct_default_init(mem_sptr);
2965 if (!mem_aclp) {
2966 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, "No default initialization for",
2967 SYMNAME(mem_sptr));
2968 mem_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
2969 mem_aclp->id = AC_AST;
2970 mem_aclp->dtype = DT_PTR;
2971 mem_aclp->u1.ast = astb.i0;
2972 }
2973 }
2974 if (mem_aclp->id == AC_AST &&
2975 (mem_aclp->dtype == DT_PTR || POINTERG(mem_sptr)) &&
2976 mem_aclp->u1.ast == astb.i0) {
2977 /* Convert this to NULL then assign ptr */
2978 aast = gen_null_intrin();
2979 } else if (DTY(DTYPEG(mem_sptr)) == TY_PTR &&
2980 DTY(DTY(DTYPEG(mem_sptr) + 1)) == TY_PROC) {
2981 /* cannot call mkexpr which later call mkexpr1
2982 * for procedure(subroutine) assignment of
2983 * derived type in structure constructor.
2984 */
2985 mkexpr2(mem_aclp->u1.stkp);
2986 astkp = mem_aclp->u1.stkp;
2987 aast = SST_ASTG(astkp);
2988 } else {
2989 mkexpr(mem_aclp->u1.stkp);
2990 astkp = mem_aclp->u1.stkp;
2991 aast = SST_ASTG(astkp);
2992 }
2993 if ((A_TYPEG(aast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(aast) == I_NULL) ||
2994 (DTY(DTYPEG(mem_sptr)) == TY_PTR &&
2995 DTY(DTY(DTYPEG(mem_sptr) + 1)) == TY_PROC)) {
2996
2997 if (!(A_TYPEG(aast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(aast) == I_NULL))
2998 (void)chk_pointer_target(mem_sptr, aast);
2999
3000 stmtast = add_ptr_assign(mkmember(dtype, dest, NMPTRG(mem_sptr)),
3001 aast, 0);
3002 add_stmt(ast_rewrite_indices(stmtast));
3003 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3004 if (SDSCG(mem_sptr) && STYPEG(SDSCG(mem_sptr)) == ST_MEMBER) {
3005 cmem_sptr = mem_sptr;
3006 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == MIDNUMG(cmem_sptr)) {
3007 /* point to pointer */
3008 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3009 }
3010 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == PTROFFG(cmem_sptr)) {
3011 /* point to offset */
3012 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3013 }
3014 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == SDSCG(cmem_sptr)) {
3015 /* point to sdsc */
3016 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3017 }
3018 if (CLASSG(cmem_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(mem_sptr)) {
3019 /* points to $td */
3020 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3021 }
3022 } else if (MIDNUMG(mem_sptr)) {
3023 mem_sptr = MIDNUMG(mem_sptr); /* skip $o, $sd, $p */
3024 }
3025 } else if (SDSCG(mem_sptr)) {
3026 (void)chk_pointer_target(mem_sptr, aast);
3027 astkp = mem_aclp->u1.stkp;
3028 i = NMPTRG(mem_sptr);
3029 if (SST_IDG(astkp) == S_IDENT) {
3030 asptr = SST_SYMG(astkp);
3031 aast = mk_id(asptr);
3032 } else if (SST_IDG(astkp) == S_LVALUE) {
3033 aast = mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast;
3034 if (aast == 0) {
3035 asptr = SST_LSYMG(astkp);
3036 aast = mk_id(asptr);
3037 }
3038 } else {
3039 aast = mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast;
3040 }
3041 if (STYPEG(SDSCG(mem_sptr)) == ST_MEMBER) {
3042 /* do a 'pointer-assign' here. skip over
3043 * base pointer/offset/descriptor */
3044 stmtast = add_ptr_assign(mkmember(dtype, dest, i), aast, 0);
3045 (void)add_stmt(ast_rewrite_indices(stmtast));
3046 cmem_sptr = mem_sptr;
3047 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == MIDNUMG(cmem_sptr)) {
3048 /* point to pointer */
3049 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3050 }
3051 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3052 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == PTROFFG(cmem_sptr)) {
3053 /* point to offset */
3054 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3055 }
3056 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3057 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == SDSCG(cmem_sptr)) {
3058 /* point to sdsc */
3059 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3060 }
3061 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3062 if (CLASSG(cmem_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(mem_sptr)) {
3063 /* points to $td, no aclp, part of sdsc */
3064 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3065 }
3066 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next; /* past sdsc */
3067 } else {
3068 stmtast = add_ptr_assign(mkmember(dtype, dest, i), aast, 0);
3069 (void)add_stmt(ast_rewrite_indices(stmtast));
3070 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3071 mem_sptr = MIDNUMG(mem_sptr); /* skip $o, $sd, $p */
3072 }
3073 } else {
3074 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next; /* skip pointee */
3075 }
3076 continue;
3077 } else if (ALLOCATTRG(mem_sptr)) {
3078 int stmt, orig_mem_sptr;
3079 ast = mk_id(mem_sptr);
3080 orig_mem_sptr = mem_sptr;
3081 if (mem_aclp->id == AC_ACONST) {
3082 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, DTYPEG(mem_sptr));
3083 tmpsptr = getcctmp_sc('f', sem.dtemps++, ST_ARRAY, mem_aclp->dtype,
3084 SC_STATIC);
3085 NODESCP(tmpsptr, 0);
3086 tmp = clone_init_const(mem_aclp, FALSE);
3087 init_sptr_w_acl(tmpsptr, tmp);
3088 acs.is_const = 0;
3089 ast = mk_id(tmpsptr);
3090 ast = mk_assn_stmt(mem_sptr_id, ast, mem_aclp->dtype);
3091 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3092 /* need init $p $sd */
3093 (void)add_stmt_before(add_nullify_ast(mem_sptr_id), stmt);
3094 } else if (mem_aclp->id == AC_SCONST) {
3095 if (is_unl_poly(mem_sptr)) {
3096 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, mem_aclp->dtype);
3097 } else {
3098 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, DTYPEG(mem_sptr));
3099 }
3100 tmpsptr = getcctmp_sc('f', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR, mem_aclp->dtype,
3101 SC_STATIC);
3102 NODESCP(tmpsptr, 0);
3103 tmp = clone_init_const(mem_aclp, FALSE);
3104 init_derived_w_acl(tmpsptr, tmp);
3105 acs.is_const = 0;
3106 ast = mk_id(tmpsptr);
3107 ast = mk_assn_stmt(mem_sptr_id, ast, mem_aclp->dtype);
3108 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3109
3110 } else if (mem_aclp->id == AC_EXPR &&
3111 A_TYPEG(mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast) == A_INTR &&
3112 A_OPTYPEG(mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast) == I_NULL) {
3113 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, DTYPEG(mem_sptr));
3114 ast = add_nullify_ast(mem_sptr_id);
3115 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3116 } else if ((DTYPEG(mem_sptr)) == DT_DEFERCHAR ||
3117 (DTYPEG(mem_sptr)) == DT_DEFERNCHAR) {
3118
3119 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, DTYPEG(mem_sptr));
3120 if (mem_aclp->id == AC_AST && mem_aclp->u1.ast == astb.i0) {
3121 ast = add_nullify_ast(mem_sptr_id);
3122 } else {
3123 ast = add_nullify_ast(mem_sptr_id);
3124 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3125 mkexpr(mem_aclp->u1.stkp);
3126 ast = mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast;
3127 ast = mk_assn_stmt(mem_sptr_id, ast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
3128 }
3129
3130 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3131
3132 if (SDSCG(mem_sptr) && STYPEG(SDSCG(mem_sptr)) == ST_MEMBER) {
3133 cmem_sptr = mem_sptr;
3134 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == MIDNUMG(cmem_sptr)) {
3135 /* point to pointer */
3136 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3137 }
3138 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == PTROFFG(cmem_sptr)) {
3139 /* point to offset */
3140 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3141 }
3142 if (SYMLKG(mem_sptr) == SDSCG(cmem_sptr)) {
3143 /* point to sdsc */
3144 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3145 }
3146 if (CLASSG(cmem_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(mem_sptr)) {
3147 /* points to $td */
3148 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr);
3149 }
3150 } else {
3151 mem_sptr = MIDNUMG(mem_sptr); /* skip $o, $sd, $p */
3152 }
3153 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3154 continue;
3155
3156 } else {
3157 if (mem_aclp->id == AC_EXPR && is_unl_poly(mem_sptr)) {
3158 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, SST_DTYPEG(mem_aclp->u1.stkp));
3159 } else {
3160 mem_sptr_id = mk_member(dest, ast, DTYPEG(mem_sptr));
3161 }
3162 if (mem_aclp->id == AC_AST && mem_aclp->u1.ast == astb.i0) {
3163 ast = add_nullify_ast(mem_sptr_id);
3164 } else {
3165 mkexpr(mem_aclp->u1.stkp);
3166 ast = mem_aclp->u1.stkp->ast;
3167 ast = mk_assn_stmt(mem_sptr_id, ast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
3168 }
3169 stmt = add_stmt(ast);
3170 }
3171
3172 sdscismbr = (SDSCG(mem_sptr) && STYPEG(SDSCG(mem_sptr)) == ST_MEMBER);
3173 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr); /* point to pointer */
3174 mem_aclp = mem_aclp->next;
3175 if (sdscismbr) {
3176 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr); /* point to offset */
3177 if (DTY(DTYPEG(orig_mem_sptr)) == TY_ARRAY)
3178 mem_sptr = SYMLKG(mem_sptr); /* point to sdsc */
3179 }
3180 continue;
3181 }
3182 i = NMPTRG(mem_sptr);
3183 mem_sptr_id = mkmember(dtype, dest, i);
3184 if (mem_aclp == 0) {
3185 /* interr("ran out of aclp",sptr,2); */
3186 break;
3187 }
3188 tmp = mem_aclp->next;
3189 mem_aclp->next = 0; /* decouple aclp */
3190 i = _constructf90(mem_sptr_id, 0, false, mem_aclp);
3191 mem_aclp->next = tmp; /* relink behind us */
3192 mem_aclp = tmp;
3193 }
3194 if (in_array) {
3195 indexast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, indexast, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
3196 incr_element_cnt();
3197 }
3198 break;
3199 case AC_EXPR:
3200 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
3201 if (in_array)
3202 mkexpr_assign_temp(stkp);
3203 else
3204 mkexpr(stkp);
3205 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
3206 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
3207 /* constructor item is an array */
3208 int shp;
3209 int shpdest;
3210 int ndim;
3211 int iv;
3212 int alloc_obj = 0; /* used to dealloc array function return variable */
3213
3214 if (!in_array) {
3215 /* handle case where a (possibly multiple dimensioned
3216 array is assigned to a structure element. */
3217 src = SST_ASTG(stkp);
3218 shp = A_SHAPEG(src);
3219 dest = base_id;
3220 shpdest = A_SHAPEG(dest);
3221 ndim = SHD_NDIM(shp);
3222 add_shape_rank(ndim);
3223 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
3224 ast = extent_of_shape(shp, i);
3225 ast = mk_binop(
3226 OP_SUB,
3227 mk_binop(OP_ADD, SHD_LWB(shpdest, i), ast, astb.bnd.dtype),
3228 astb.i1, astb.bnd.dtype);
3229 add_shape_spec(SHD_LWB(shpdest, i), ast, astb.i1);
3230 }
3231 shpdest = mk_shape();
3232 dest = apply_shape_subscripts(base_id, shpdest, dtype);
3233 ast = mk_assn_stmt(dest, src, dtype);
3234 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3235 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3236 break;
3237 }
3238
3239 /* In the loop generated from implied-do loop, we encoutered the AST
3240 * used as the return value to replace the function call.
3241 */
3242 if (acs.level && sem.arrfn.sptr > NOSYM &&
3243 sem.arrfn.return_value == SST_ASTG(stkp)) {
3244 int ret_sptr = A_SPTRG(sem.arrfn.return_value);
3245 acs.func_in_do = TRUE;
3246 /* STDs generated in func_call2(semfunc.c) have been move in loop
3247 * when processing AC_IDO. We do not need move in sem.arrfn.alloc_std
3248 * and sem.arrfn.call_std again.
3249 */
3250 if (sem.arrfn.alloc_std) {
3251 /* remove return variable from sem.p_dealloc */
3252 ITEM *pre = NULL;
3253 for (ITEM *itemp = sem.p_dealloc; itemp; itemp = itemp->next) {
3254 if (A_SPTRG(itemp->ast) == ret_sptr) {
3255 if (pre != NULL)
3256 pre->next = itemp->next;
3257 else
3258 sem.p_dealloc = itemp->next;
3259 alloc_obj = itemp->ast;
3260 break;
3261 }
3262 pre = itemp;
3263 }
3264 }
3265 if (ADD_DEFER(SST_DTYPEG(stkp))) {
3266 /* If the function call returns deferred-length array or adjustable
3267 * array, we use the sum of the current length of the array temp
3268 * and the length of the array returned by the function as the
3269 * length of the array temp after reallocation.
3270 */
3271 int src_array = memsym_of_ast(base_id);
3272 if (!SDSCG(ret_sptr))
3273 get_static_descriptor(ret_sptr);
3274 argt_count = 3;
3275 argt = mk_argt(argt_count);
3276 ARGT_ARG(argt, 0) = mk_id(MIDNUMG(src_array));
3277 ARGT_ARG(argt, 1) = mk_id(SDSCG(src_array));
3278 ARGT_ARG(argt, 2) = mk_id(SDSCG(ret_sptr));
3279 DESCUSEDP(src_array, 1);
3280 DESCUSEDP(ret_sptr, 1);
3281 ast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, mk_id(sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(
3282 RTE_realloc_arr_in_impiled_do), DT_ADDR)), argt_count, argt);
3283 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3284 }
3285 }
3286
3287 tmpid = get_subscripting_tmp(indexast);
3288
3289 /* get do begins for src array objects */
3290 shp = A_SHAPEG(SST_ASTG(stkp));
3291 ndim = SHD_NDIM(shp);
3292 for (i = ndim - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
3293 iv = get_temp(astb.bnd.dtype);
3294 ast = mk_stmt(A_DO, 0);
3295 dovar = mk_id(iv);
3296 A_DOVARP(ast, dovar);
3297 A_M1P(ast, SHD_LWB(shp, i));
3298 A_M2P(ast, SHD_UPB(shp, i));
3299 A_M3P(ast, SHD_STRIDE(shp, i));
3300 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3301 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3302 src_subs[i] = A_DOVARG(ast);
3303 }
3304
3305 src = add_dt_subscr(SST_ASTG(stkp), src_subs, ndim);
3306
3307 dest = add_subscript(base_id, tmpid, DTY(dtype + 1));
3308
3309 ast = mk_assn_stmt(dest, src, DTY(dtype + 1));
3310 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3311 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3312
3313 /* increment the subscripting temporary */
3314 incr_tmp(tmpid);
3315
3316 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
3317 ast = mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0);
3318 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3319 }
3320
3321 /* dealloc array function return variable */
3322 if (alloc_obj)
3323 (void)gen_alloc_dealloc(TK_DEALLOCATE, alloc_obj, 0);
3324 clear_element_cnt();
3325 indexast = tmpid;
3326 } else {
3327 /* constructor item is a scalar */
3328 src = SST_ASTG(stkp);
3329 dest = base_id;
3330 dtype = A_DTYPEG(dest);
3331 if (in_array) {
3332 dtype = DDTG(dtype);
3333 dest = add_subscript(dest, indexast, dtype);
3334 }
3335 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY && ast_is_sym(src) &&
3336 has_layout_desc(memsym_of_ast(src))) {
3337 int argt, dest_td_sym, src_td_sym;
3338 dest_td_sym = getccsym('d', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR);
3339 DTYPEP(dest_td_sym, dtype);
3340 src_td_sym = getccsym('d', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR);
3341 DTYPEP(src_td_sym, A_DTYPEG(src));
3342 argt = mk_argt(5);
3343 ARGT_ARG(argt, 0) = dest;
3344 ARGT_ARG(argt, 1) = mk_id(get_static_type_descriptor(dest_td_sym));
3345 ARGT_ARG(argt, 2) = src;
3346 ARGT_ARG(argt, 3) = mk_id(get_static_type_descriptor(src_td_sym));
3347 ARGT_ARG(argt, 4) = mk_unop(OP_VAL, mk_cval1(1, DT_INT), DT_INT);
3348 ast = mk_id(sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_poly_asn), DT_NONE));
3349 ast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, ast, 5, argt);
3350 } else {
3351 ast = mk_assn_stmt(dest, src, dtype);
3352 }
3353 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3354 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3355 if (in_array) {
3356 indexast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, indexast, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
3357 incr_element_cnt();
3358 }
3359 }
3360 break;
3361 case AC_IDO:
3362 tmpid = get_subscripting_tmp(indexast);
3363
3364 acs.level++;
3365 clear_element_cnt();
3366 doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
3367 /* for array constructor, we must create a new symbol
3368 * for the implied 'do' loop */
3369 odovar = doinfo->index_var;
3370 /* insert a new one */
3371 dovar = get_temp(DDTG(DTYPEG(odovar)));
3372 STYPEP(dovar, STYPEG(odovar));
3373 DTYPEP(dovar, DTYPEG(odovar));
3374 if (SCG(odovar) == SC_PRIVATE) {
3375 SCP(dovar, SC_PRIVATE);
3376 } else {
3377 SCP(dovar, SC_LOCAL);
3378 }
3379 HIDDENP(dovar, 1);
3380 ast_replace_index(mk_id(odovar), mk_id(dovar));
3381 doinfo->index_var = dovar;
3382 ast = do_begin(doinfo);
3383 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3384
3385 /* Folling line of code is an extension, where we allow
3386 * a ac-do-variable to be referenced in limit expression.
3387 * Do not rewrite ast of limit_expr. For example,
3388 * do i = 1, n
3389 * x = (/i,i = 1,fox(i)/)
3390 * end do
3391 * i in fox(i) is from do i=1, not implied-do-variable i
3392 */
3393
3394 if (!XBIT(57, 0x4000))
3395 A_M2P(ast, doinfo->limit_expr);
3396
3397 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3398 /* Value-list must be rewritten too. */
3399 ast_visit(1, 1);
3400 ast_replace(mk_id(odovar), mk_id(dovar));
3401 if (aclp->u2.std_range != NULL && aclp->u2.std_range->start != 0) {
3402 /* move in stmts generated by loop body and replace dovar */
3403 int do_std = STD_LAST;
3404 move_range_after(aclp->u2.std_range->start, aclp->u2.std_range->mid,
3405 do_std);
3406 for (int std = STD_NEXT(do_std); std; std = STD_NEXT(std)) {
3407 STD_AST(std) = ast_rewrite(STD_AST(std));
3408 }
3409 }
3410 aclp->subc = acl_rewrite_asts(aclp->subc);
3411 ast_unvisit();
3412
3413 _constructf90(base_id, tmpid, in_array, aclp->subc);
3414
3415 if ((cnt = get_element_cnt())) {
3416 /* increment the subscripting temporary */
3417 i = mk_isz_cval(cnt, astb.bnd.dtype);
3418 i = mk_binop(OP_ADD, tmpid, i, astb.bnd.dtype);
3419 ast = mk_assn_stmt(tmpid, i, astb.bnd.dtype);
3420 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3421 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3422 }
3423
3424 NEED_DOIF(i, DI_DO); /* need a loop stack entry for do_end() */
3425 do_end(doinfo);
3426 --numindex; /* done with this loop */
3427 indexast = tmpid;
3428 clear_element_cnt();
3429 acs.level--;
3430 break;
3431 case AC_AST: /* default init */
3432 ast = aclp->u1.ast;
3433 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3434
3435 if (is_iso_cptr(dtype)) {
3436 mem_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
3437 ast = mkmember(dtype, ast, NMPTRG(mem_sptr));
3438 }
3439
3440 if (in_array) {
3441 dtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(base_id));
3442 dest = add_subscript(base_id, indexast, dtype);
3443 } else {
3444 dtype = A_DTYPEG(base_id);
3445 dest = base_id;
3446 }
3447
3448 ast = mk_assn_stmt(dest, ast, dtype);
3449
3450 ast = ast_rewrite_indices(ast);
3451 (void)add_stmt(ast);
3452 if (in_array) {
3453 indexast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, indexast, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
3454 incr_element_cnt();
3455 }
3456 break;
3457 case AC_IEXPR:
3458 break;
3459 default:
3460 interr("_construct,ill.id", aclp->id, 3);
3461 break;
3462 }
3463 }
3464
3465 return indexast;
3466}
3467
3468static void
3469constructf90(int arr, ACL *aclp)
3470{
3471 DTYPE dtype;
3472 int lower;
3473 bool inarray;
3474
3475 init_constructf90();
3476
3477 acs.level = 0;
3478 acs.width = compute_width(aclp);
3479
3480 dtype = DTYPEG(arr);
3481 inarray = DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY;
3482 if (inarray) {
3483 lower = ADD_LWAST(dtype, 0);
3484 if (lower == 0)
3485 lower = astb.bnd.one;
3486 push_subscript();
3487 } else {
3488 lower = astb.bnd.one;
3489 }
3490
3491 acs.tmpid = mk_id(arr);
3492
3493 numindex = 0;
3494 _constructf90(acs.tmpid, lower, inarray, aclp);
3495
3496 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
3497 pop_subscript();
3498 }
3499
3500 if (sub_i != 7)
3501 interr("sub_i in constructf90 is not back", sub_i, 2);
3502}
3503
3504ACL *
3505mk_init_intrinsic(AC_INTRINSIC init_intr)
3506{
3507 AEXPR *aexpr;
3508 ACL *expracl = GET_ACL(15);
3509
3510 expracl->id = AC_IEXPR;
3511 expracl->u1.expr = aexpr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
3512 BZERO(aexpr, AEXPR, 1);
3513 aexpr->op = AC_INTR_CALL;
3514 aexpr->lop = GET_ACL(15);
3515 aexpr->lop->id = AC_ICONST;
3516 aexpr->lop->u1.i = init_intr;
3517
3518 return expracl;
3519}
3520
3521static ACL *
3522mk_ulbound_intrin(AC_INTRINSIC intrin, int ast)
3523{
3524 ACL *argacl;
3525 ACL *dimval;
3526 ACL **r;
3527 AEXPR *aexpr;
3528 int ubound[MAXDIMS];
3529 int lbound[MAXDIMS];
3530 int i;
3531 LOGICAL must_convert;
3532 ACL *expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(intrin);
3533 int arg_count = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
3534 int argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3535 int argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3536 int shape = A_SHAPEG(argast);
3537 int rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
3538 int dtyper;
3539
3540 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3541 if (A_TYPEG(argast) == A_ID) {
3542 ubound[i] = ubound_of_shape(shape, i);
3543 lbound[i] = lbound_of_shape(shape, i);
3544 } else {
3545 ubound[i] = extent_of_shape(shape, i);
3546 lbound[i] = astb.i1;
3547 }
3548 }
3549
3550 aexpr = expracl->u1.expr;
3551
3552 argacl = aexpr->rop = GET_ACL(15);
3553 argacl->id = AC_ACONST;
3554 sem.arrdim.ndim = 1;
3555 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 0;
3556 sem.bounds[0].lowtype = S_CONST;
3557 sem.bounds[0].lowb = 1;
3558 sem.bounds[0].lwast = 0;
3559 sem.bounds[0].uptype = S_CONST;
3560 sem.bounds[0].upb = rank;
3561 sem.bounds[0].upast = mk_cval(rank, stb.user.dt_int);
3562 dtyper = mk_arrdsc();
3563 DTY(dtyper + 1) = stb.user.dt_int;
3564 argacl->dtype = dtyper;
3565
3566 must_convert = FALSE;
3567 if (arg_count == 2 && argacl->dtype != stb.user.dt_int)
3568 must_convert = TRUE;
3569
3570 r = &argacl->subc;
3571 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3572 *r = GET_ACL(15);
3573 (*r)->id = AC_AST;
3574 (*r)->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3575 (*r)->is_const = TRUE;
3576 if (intrin == AC_I_ubound) {
3577 (*r)->u1.ast = ubound[i];
3578 } else {
3579 (*r)->u1.ast = lbound[i];
3580 }
3581 if (must_convert) {
3582 (*r)->u1.ast = mk_convert((*r)->u1.ast, stb.user.dt_int);
3583 }
3584 r = &(*r)->next;
3585 }
3586
3587 if (arg_count == 2) {
3588 argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
3589 if (!_can_fold(argast)) {
3590 error(87, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3591 }
3592 argacl = construct_acl_from_ast(argast, stb.user.dt_int, 0);
3593 if (!argacl) {
3594 return 0;
3595 }
3596 aexpr->rop->next = argacl;
3597 expracl->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3598
3599 dimval = eval_init_expr_item(argacl);
3600 if (!dimval) {
3601 return 0;
3602 }
3603 i = dimval->conval;
3604 if (dimval->dtype == DT_INT8)
3605 i = get_int_cval(i);
3606 if ((intrin == AC_I_ubound && !_can_fold(ubound[i - 1])) ||
3607 (intrin == AC_I_lbound && !_can_fold(lbound[i - 1]))) {
3608 error(87, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3609 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3610 return 0;
3611 }
3612 } else {
3613 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3614 if ((intrin == AC_I_ubound && !_can_fold(ubound[i])) ||
3615 (intrin == AC_I_lbound && !_can_fold(lbound[i]))) {
3616 error(87, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3617 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3618 return 0;
3619 }
3620 }
3621 expracl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3622 ;
3623 }
3624
3625 return expracl;
3626}
