3628static ACL *
3629mk_transpose_intrin(int ast)
3630{
3631 ACL *expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(AC_I_transpose);
3632 expracl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3633
3634 AEXPR *aexpr;
3635 aexpr = expracl->u1.expr;
3636
3637 int argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3638 int srcast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3639 aexpr->rop = construct_acl_from_ast(srcast, A_DTYPEG(srcast), 0);
3640 if (!aexpr->rop) {
3641 return 0;
3642 }
3643
3644 return expracl;
3645}
3646
3647static ACL *
3648mk_reshape_intrin(int ast)
3649{
3650 ACL *expracl;
3651 int arg_count;
3652 int argt;
3653 AEXPR *aexpr;
3654 int srcast;
3655 int shapeast;
3656 int padast = 0;
3657 int orderast = 0;
3658 ACL *a;
3659 int new_sz, old_sz;
3660
3661 expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(AC_I_reshape);
3662 aexpr = expracl->u1.expr;
3663
3664 arg_count = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
3665 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3666
3667 /* Ignore arg2, the shape was built and plugged in ref_pd */
3668 shapeast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
3669 srcast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3670
3671 new_sz = get_int_cval(sym_of_ast(ADD_NUMELM(A_DTYPEG(ast))));
3672 old_sz = get_int_cval(sym_of_ast(ADD_NUMELM(A_DTYPEG(srcast))));
3673 if (arg_count > 2) {
3674 padast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2);
3675 if (arg_count > 3) {
3676 orderast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 3);
3677 }
3678 }
3679
3680 /* compute the number of elements in the source */
3681 if (new_sz > old_sz && !padast) {
3682 error(4, 3, gbl.lineno,
3683 "Source and shape argument size mismatch, too few source constants",
3684 NULL);
3685 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3686 return 0;
3687 }
3688
3689 expracl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3690
3691 aexpr->rop = construct_acl_from_ast(srcast, A_DTYPEG(srcast), 0);
3692 if (!aexpr->rop) {
3693 return 0;
3694 }
3695 aexpr->rop->next = construct_acl_from_ast(shapeast, A_DTYPEG(shapeast), 0);
3696 if (!aexpr->rop->next) {
3697 return 0;
3698 }
3699
3700 if (arg_count > 2) {
3701 if (padast) {
3702 aexpr->rop->next->next =
3703 construct_acl_from_ast(padast, A_DTYPEG(padast), 0);
3704 if (!aexpr->rop->next->next) {
3705 return 0;
3706 }
3707 } else {
3708 a = GET_ACL(15);
3709 a->id = AC_AST;
3710 a->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3711 a->u1.ast = astb.i0;
3712 aexpr->rop->next->next = a;
3713 }
3714
3715 if (arg_count > 3 && orderast) {
3716 aexpr->rop->next->next->next =
3717 construct_acl_from_ast(orderast, A_DTYPEG(orderast), 0);
3718 if (!aexpr->rop->next->next->next) {
3719 return 0;
3720 }
3721 }
3722 }
3723
3724 return expracl;
3725}
3726
3727static ACL *
3728mk_shape_intrin(int ast)
3729{
3730 ACL *expracl;
3731 ACL *argacl;
3732 int argast;
3733 ACL **r;
3734 AEXPR *aexpr;
3735 int rank;
3736 int shape;
3737 int argt;
3738 int ubound[MAXDIMS];
3739 int lbound[MAXDIMS];
3740 int i;
3741
3742 expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(AC_I_shape);
3743 expracl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3744
3745 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3746
3747 argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3748 shape = A_SHAPEG(argast);
3749 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
3750
3751 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3752 if (A_TYPEG(argast) == A_ID) {
3753 ubound[i] = ubound_of_shape(shape, i);
3754 lbound[i] = lbound_of_shape(shape, i);
3755 if (lbound[i] != astb.i1 || lbound[i] != astb.i0) {
3756 ubound[i] = extent_of_shape(shape, i);
3757 }
3758 } else {
3759 ubound[i] = extent_of_shape(shape, i);
3760 lbound[i] = astb.i1;
3761 }
3762 }
3763
3764 aexpr = expracl->u1.expr;
3765
3766 argacl = aexpr->rop = GET_ACL(15);
3767 argacl->id = AC_ACONST;
3768 argacl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(argast);
3769
3770 r = &argacl->subc;
3771 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3772 *r = GET_ACL(15);
3773 (*r)->id = AC_AST;
3774 (*r)->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3775 (*r)->is_const = TRUE;
3776 (*r)->u1.ast = ubound[i];
3777 r = &(*r)->next;
3778 }
3779
3780 return expracl;
3781}
3782
3783static ACL *
3784mk_size_intrin(int ast)
3785{
3786 ACL *expracl;
3787 ACL **csub_acl;
3788 ACL *c_acl;
3789 ACL *arg2acl;
3790 ACL *dimval;
3791 int arg1ast;
3792 int arg2ast;
3793 DTYPE dtype;
3794 int shape;
3795 int rank;
3796 int i;
3797 int argt;
3798 int arg_count;
3799
3800 /* Build a new arg list that contains:
3801 * 1) array size (possible astb.i0)
3802 * 2) array constructor containing the size of each dimension
3803 * 3) original DIM arg (optional)
3804 * (athough I'm not sure why, it would be much easier to just
3805 * plug the size value).
3806 */
3807
3808 expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(AC_I_size);
3809 expracl->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3810
3811 arg_count = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
3812 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3813
3814 arg1ast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3815 shape = A_SHAPEG(arg1ast);
3816 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
3817
3818 if (arg_count == 1) {
3819 if (A_TYPEG(arg1ast) == A_ID &&
3820 (ASUMSZG(A_SPTRG(arg1ast)) || ASSUMSHPG(A_SPTRG(arg1ast)))) {
3821 error(87, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3822 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3823 return 0;
3824 }
3825 } else {
3826 arg2ast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
3827 if (!_can_fold(arg2ast)) {
3828 error(422, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3829 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3830 return 0;
3831 }
3832 arg2acl = construct_acl_from_ast(arg2ast, A_DTYPEG(arg2ast), 0);
3833 if (!arg2acl) {
3834 return 0;
3835 }
3836 dimval = eval_init_expr_item(arg2acl);
3837 if (!dimval) {
3838 return 0;
3839 }
3840 i = dimval->conval;
3841 if (i > rank) {
3842 error(423, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3843 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3844 return 0;
3845 }
3846 }
3847
3848 expracl->u1.expr->rop = c_acl = GET_ACL(15);
3849 c_acl->id = AC_AST;
3850 c_acl->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3851 if (A_TYPEG(arg1ast) == A_ID &&
3852 (ASUMSZG(A_SPTRG(arg1ast)) || ASSUMSHPG(A_SPTRG(arg1ast)))) {
3853 c_acl->u1.ast = astb.i0;
3854 } else {
3855 c_acl->u1.ast = size_of_ast(arg1ast);
3856 }
3857 if (c_acl->dtype != A_DTYPEG(c_acl->u1.ast))
3858 c_acl->u1.ast = mk_convert(c_acl->u1.ast, c_acl->dtype);
3859
3860 /* shape/dtype for arg 2 */
3861 sem.arrdim.ndim = 1;
3862 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 0;
3863 sem.bounds[0].lowtype = S_CONST;
3864 sem.bounds[0].lowb = 1;
3865 sem.bounds[0].lwast = 0;
3866 sem.bounds[0].uptype = S_CONST;
3867 sem.bounds[0].upb = rank;
3868 sem.bounds[0].upast = mk_cval(rank, stb.user.dt_int);
3869 dtype = mk_arrdsc();
3870 DTY(dtype + 1) = stb.user.dt_int;
3871
3872 c_acl->next = GET_ACL(15);
3873 c_acl = c_acl->next;
3874 c_acl->id = AC_ACONST;
3875 c_acl->dtype = dtype;
3876 csub_acl = &c_acl->subc;
3877 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
3878 *csub_acl = c_acl = GET_ACL(15);
3879 c_acl->id = AC_AST;
3880 c_acl->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
3881
3882 if (_can_fold(SHD_LWB(shape, i)) && _can_fold(SHD_UPB(shape, i))) {
3883 c_acl->u1.ast = extent_of_shape(shape, i);
3884 } else if (arg_count == 1 || i == dimval->conval - 1) {
3885 error(87, 3, gbl.lineno, NULL, NULL);
3886 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3887 return 0;
3888 } else {
3889 c_acl->u1.ast = astb.i0;
3890 }
3891
3892 csub_acl = &(*csub_acl)->next;
3893 }
3894
3895 if (arg_count == 2) {
3896 expracl->u1.expr->rop->next->next = arg2acl;
3897 }
3898
3899 return expracl;
3900}
3901
3902static ACL *
3903mk_transfer_intrin(int ast)
3904{
3905 int argt;
3906 int argast;
3907 ACL *expracl;
3908 ACL *arglist;
3909
3910 expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(AC_I_transfer);
3911
3912 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3913 argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
3914 arglist = construct_acl_from_ast(argast, A_DTYPEG(argast), 0);
3915 if (arglist == 0) {
3916 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3917 return 0;
3918 }
3919
3920#ifdef try_without_this
3921 /* Maybe we don't need the 2nd and 3rd args.
3922 A_DTYPEG(ast) gives the type of the result.
3923 */
3924 /* Can't call construct_acl_from_ast() for the mold argument because
3925 * it need not be a constant. All we really need is the element type.
3926 */
3927 argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
3928 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
3929 aclp->id = AC_AST;
3930 aclp->dtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(argast));
3931 aclp->u1.ast = mk_cval(0, aclp->dtype);
3932 arglist->next = aclp;
3933
3934 /* size of result */
3935 argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2);
3936 aclp = construct_acl_from_ast(argast, A_DTYPEG(argast), 0);
3937 if (aclp == 0) {
3938 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3939 return 0;
3940 }
3941 arglist->next->next = aclp;
3942#endif
3943
3944 expracl->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3945 expracl->u1.expr->rop = arglist;
3946 return expracl;
3947}
3948
3949static ACL *
3950construct_arg_list(int ast)
3951{
3952 int argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3953 ACL *argroot = NULL;
3954 ACL **curarg = &argroot;
3955 int i;
3956
3957 for (i = 0; i < A_ARGCNTG(ast); i++) {
3958 int argast = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
3959 /* argast is 0 for optional args */
3960 if (argast) {
3961 *curarg = construct_acl_from_ast(argast, A_DTYPEG(argast), 0);
3962 if (!*curarg) {
3963 return 0;
3964 }
3965 curarg = &(*curarg)->next;
3966 }
3967 }
3968 return argroot;
3969}
3970
3971static ACL *
3972mk_nonelem_init_intrinsic(AC_INTRINSIC init_intr, int ast, DTYPE dtype)
3973{
3974 ACL *expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(init_intr);
3975 ACL *arglist = construct_arg_list(ast);
3976
3977 if (sem.dinit_error) {
3978 return 0;
3979 }
3980 expracl->dtype = dtype;
3981 expracl->u1.expr->rop = arglist;
3982 return expracl;
3983}
3984
3985static ACL *
3986mk_elem_init_intrinsic(AC_INTRINSIC init_intr, int ast, DTYPE dtype,
3987 int parent_acltype)
3988{
3989 ACL *arg1acl;
3990 ACL *a;
3991 DTYPE arg1dtype;
3992 DTYPE dtypebase = DDTG(dtype);
3993 ACL *expracl = mk_init_intrinsic(init_intr);
3994 ACL *arglist = construct_arg_list(ast);
3995
3996 if (!arglist) {
3997 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
3998 return 0;
3999 }
4000
4001 arg1acl = arglist;
4002 arg1dtype = arg1acl->dtype;
4003 expracl->dtype = dtypebase;
4004 expracl->u1.expr->rop = arglist;
4005
4006 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
4007 if (DTY(arg1dtype) != TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST)
4008 expracl->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(dtype);
4009 a = GET_ACL(15);
4010 a->id = AC_ACONST;
4011 a->dtype = dtype;
4012 a->subc = expracl;
4013 expracl = a;
4014 }
4015 return expracl;
4016}
4017
4018static AC_INTRINSIC
4019get_ac_intrinsic(int ast)
4020{
4021 SPTR sptr = A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast));
4022 switch (STYPEG(sptr)) {
4023 case ST_PD:
4024 return map_PD_to_AC(PDNUMG(sptr));
4025 case ST_INTRIN:
4026 case ST_GENERIC:
4027 return map_I_to_AC(INTASTG(sptr));
4028 case ST_PROC:
4029 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR) {
4030 return map_I_to_AC(A_OPTYPEG(ast));
4031 } else {
4032 return AC_I_NONE;
4033 }
4034 default:
4035 return AC_I_NONE;
4036 }
4037}

4268
4269static ACL *
4270construct_intrinsic_acl(int ast, DTYPE dtype, int parent_acltype)
4271{
4272 AC_INTRINSIC intrin = get_ac_intrinsic(ast);
4273 switch (intrin) {
4274 case AC_I_char:
4275 case AC_I_adjustl:
4276 case AC_I_adjustr:
4277 case AC_I_ichar:
4278 case AC_I_index:
4279 case AC_I_int:
4280 case AC_I_ishft:
4281 case AC_I_max:
4282 case AC_I_min:
4283 case AC_I_nint:
4284 case AC_I_len_trim:
4285 case AC_I_ishftc:
4286 case AC_I_fltconvert:
4287 case AC_I_scan:
4288 case AC_I_verify:
4289 case AC_I_floor:
4290 case AC_I_ceiling:
4291 case AC_I_mod:
4292 case AC_I_sqrt:
4293 case AC_I_exp:
4294 case AC_I_log:
4295 case AC_I_log10:
4296 case AC_I_sin:
4297 case AC_I_cos:
4298 case AC_I_tan:
4299 case AC_I_asin:
4300 case AC_I_acos:
4301 case AC_I_atan:
4302 case AC_I_atan2:
4303 case AC_I_abs:
4304 case AC_I_iand:
4305 case AC_I_ior:
4306 case AC_I_ieor:
4307 case AC_I_merge:
4308 case AC_I_scale:
4309 return mk_elem_init_intrinsic(intrin, ast, dtype, parent_acltype);
4310 case AC_I_maxloc:
4311 case AC_I_maxval:
4312 case AC_I_minloc:
4313 case AC_I_minval:
4314 return mk_elem_init_intrinsic(intrin, ast, dtype, parent_acltype);
4315 case AC_I_lshift:
4316 /* LSHIFT(i, shift) == ISHFT(i, shift) */
4317 return mk_elem_init_intrinsic(AC_I_ishft, ast, dtype, parent_acltype);
4318 case AC_I_rshift: {
4319 /* RSHIFT(i, shift) == ISHFT(-i, shift) */
4320 int argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
4321 int val = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
4322 int shift = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
4323 int new_shift = mk_unop(OP_SUB, shift, A_DTYPEG(shift));
4324 int new_ast = ast_intr(I_ISHFT, A_DTYPEG(ast), 2, val, new_shift);
4325 return mk_elem_init_intrinsic(AC_I_ishft, new_ast, dtype, parent_acltype);
4326 }
4327 case AC_I_len:
4328 case AC_I_lbound:
4329 case AC_I_ubound:
4330 return mk_ulbound_intrin(intrin, ast);
4331 case AC_I_null:
4332 case AC_I_repeat:
4333 case AC_I_trim:
4334 case AC_I_selected_int_kind:
4335 case AC_I_selected_real_kind:
4336 case AC_I_selected_char_kind:
4337 return mk_nonelem_init_intrinsic(intrin, ast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
4338 case AC_I_size:
4339 return mk_size_intrin(ast);
4340 case AC_I_transpose:
4341 return mk_transpose_intrin(ast);
4342 case AC_I_reshape:
4343 return mk_reshape_intrin(ast);
4344 case AC_I_shape:
4345 return mk_shape_intrin(ast);
4346 case AC_I_transfer:
4347 return mk_transfer_intrin(ast);
4348 default:
4349 error(155, ERR_Severe, gbl.lineno,
4350 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:",
4351 SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))));
4352 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
4353 return 0;
4354 }
4355}
4356
4357static int
4358get_ast_op(int op)
4359{
4360 int ast_op = 0;
4361
4362 switch (op) {
4363 case AC_NEG:
4364 ast_op = OP_NEG;
4365 break;
4366 case AC_ADD:
4367 ast_op = OP_ADD;
4368 break;
4369 case AC_SUB:
4370 ast_op = OP_SUB;
4371 break;
4372 case AC_MUL:
4373 ast_op = OP_MUL;
4374 break;
4375 case AC_DIV:
4376 ast_op = OP_DIV;
4377 break;
4378 case AC_CAT:
4379 ast_op = OP_CAT;
4380 break;
4381 case AC_LEQV:
4382 ast_op = OP_LEQV;
4383 break;
4384 case AC_LNEQV:
4385 ast_op = OP_LNEQV;
4386 break;
4387 case AC_LOR:
4388 ast_op = OP_LOR;
4389 break;
4390 case AC_LAND:
4391 ast_op = OP_LAND;
4392 break;
4393 case AC_EQ:
4394 ast_op = OP_EQ;
4395 break;
4396 case AC_GE:
4397 ast_op = OP_GE;
4398 break;
4399 case AC_GT:
4400 ast_op = OP_GT;
4401 break;
4402 case AC_LE:
4403 ast_op = OP_LE;
4404 break;
4405 case AC_LT:
4406 ast_op = OP_LT;
4407 break;
4408 case AC_NE:
4409 ast_op = OP_NE;
4410 break;
4411 case AC_LNOT:
4412 ast_op = OP_LNOT;
4413 break;
4414 case AC_EXP:
4415 case AC_EXPK:
4416 ast_op = OP_XTOI;
4417 break;
4418 case AC_EXPX:
4419 ast_op = OP_XTOX;
4420 break;
4421 default:
4422 interr("get_ast_op: unexpected operator in initialization expr", op, 3);
4423 }
4424 return ast_op;
4425}
4426
4427static int
4428get_ac_op(int ast)
4429{
4430 int ac_op = 0;
4431
4432 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
4433 case OP_NEG:
4434 ac_op = AC_NEG;
4435 break;
4436 case OP_ADD:
4437 ac_op = AC_ADD;
4438 break;
4439 case OP_SUB:
4440 ac_op = AC_SUB;
4441 break;
4442 case OP_MUL:
4443 ac_op = AC_MUL;
4444 break;
4445 case OP_DIV:
4446 ac_op = AC_DIV;
4447 break;
4448 case OP_CAT:
4449 ac_op = AC_CAT;
4450 break;
4451 case OP_LEQV:
4452 ac_op = AC_LEQV;
4453 break;
4454 case OP_LNEQV:
4455 ac_op = AC_LNEQV;
4456 break;
4457 case OP_LOR:
4458 ac_op = AC_LOR;
4459 break;
4460 case OP_LAND:
4461 ac_op = AC_LAND;
4462 break;
4463 case OP_EQ:
4464 ac_op = AC_EQ;
4465 break;
4466 case OP_GE:
4467 ac_op = AC_GE;
4468 break;
4469 case OP_GT:
4470 ac_op = AC_GT;
4471 break;
4472 case OP_LE:
4473 ac_op = AC_LE;
4474 break;
4475 case OP_LT:
4476 ac_op = AC_LT;
4477 break;
4478 case OP_NE:
4479 ac_op = AC_NE;
4480 break;
4481 case OP_LNOT:
4482 ac_op = AC_LNOT;
4483 break;
4484 case OP_XTOI:
4485 switch (DDTG(A_DTYPEG(A_ROPG(ast)))) {
4486 case DT_INT8:
4487 ac_op = AC_EXPK;
4488 break;
4489 case DT_REAL4:
4490 case DT_REAL8:
4491#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4492 case DT_QUAD:
4493 case DT_CMPLX8:
4494 case DT_CMPLX16:
4495 case DT_QCMPLX:
4496#endif
4497 ac_op = AC_EXPX;
4498 break;
4499 default:
4500 ac_op = AC_EXP;
4501 break;
4502 }
4503 break;
4504 default:
4505 interr("get_ac_op: unexpected operator in initialization expr",
4506 A_OPTYPEG(ast), 3);
4507 }
4508 return ac_op;
4509}
4510
4511static ACL *
4512eval_do_idx(int ast)
4513{
4514 ACL *aclp = NULL;
4515 DOSTACK *p;
4516 int sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
4517
4518 if (!sptr)
4519 return aclp;
4520
4521 for (p = sem.dostack; p < sem.top; p++) {
4522 if (p->sptr == sptr) {
4523 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4524 aclp->id = AC_CONST;
4525 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4526 aclp->is_const = 1;
4527 aclp->u1.ast = ast;
4528
4529 if (DT_ISWORD(A_DTYPEG(ast)))
4530 aclp->u1.ast = mk_cval1(p->currval, A_DTYPEG(ast));
4531 else
4532 aclp->u1.ast = mk_cnst(p->currval);
4533 return aclp;
4534 }
4535 }
4536 return aclp;
4537}
4538
4539ACL *
4540construct_acl_from_ast(int ast, DTYPE dtype, int parent_acltype)
4541{
4542 ACL *aclp = NULL, *subscr_aclp;
4543 ACL *u, *l, *s;
4544 ACL *prev;
4545 int lParent_acltype;
4546 int sptr;
4547 int asd;
4548 int sub_ast;
4549 int ndim;
4550 int i;
4551 int m_sptr;
4552 int p_dtype;
4553
4554 if (!ast) {
4555 errsev(457);
4556 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
4557 return 0;
4558 }
4559 if (!_can_fold(ast) &&
4560 (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID && !DOVARG(A_SPTRG(ast)) &&
4561 !(STYPEG(A_SPTRG(ast)) == ST_MEMBER) &&
4562 !(STYPEG(A_SPTRG(ast)) == ST_PARAM || PARAMG(A_SPTRG(ast)))) &&
4563 !(HCCSYMG(A_SPTRG(ast)) && DINITG(A_SPTRG(ast)))) {
4564 ACL *acl = eval_do_idx(ast);
4565 if (acl)
4566 return acl;
4567 errsev(87);
4568 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
4569 return 0;
4570 }
4571
4572 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
4573 case A_FUNC:
4574 if (sem.equal_initializer) {
4575 errsev(87);
4576 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
4577 return 0;
4578 }
4579 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4580 aclp->id = AC_IDENT;
4581 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4582 aclp->is_const = 1;
4583 aclp->u1.ast = A_LOPG(ast);
4584 break;
4585 case A_ID:
4586 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4587 aclp->id = AC_AST;
4588 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4589 aclp->is_const = 1;
4590 aclp->u1.ast = ast;
4591
4592 if (DTY(DDTG(dtype)) == TY_DERIVED &&
4593 (parent_acltype != AC_SCONST || DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast)) != DDTG(dtype)) &&
4594 !(DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast)) == TY_ARRAY)) {
4595 prev = aclp;
4596 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4597 aclp->id = AC_SCONST;
4598 aclp->dtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast));
4599 aclp->is_const = 1;
4600 aclp->subc = prev;
4601 }
4602 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast)) != TY_ARRAY &&
4603 parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4604 aclp->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(dtype);
4605 prev = aclp;
4606 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4607 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4608 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4609 aclp->is_const = 1;
4610 aclp->subc = prev;
4611 }
4612 break;
4613 case A_CNST:
4614 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4615 aclp->id = AC_AST;
4616 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4617 aclp->is_const = 1;
4618 aclp->u1.ast = ast;
4619 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast)) != TY_ARRAY &&
4620 parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4621 aclp->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(dtype);
4622 prev = aclp;
4623 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4624 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4625 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4626 aclp->is_const = 1;
4627 aclp->subc = prev;
4628 }
4629 break;
4630 case A_BINOP:
4631 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4632 aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4633 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4634 aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4635 aclp->u1.expr->op = get_ac_op(ast);
4636 /* this ACL may become the child of an AC_ACONST; set the last argument of
4637 * call to construct_acl_from_ast appropriately
4638 */
4639 lParent_acltype =
4640 (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) ? AC_ACONST : 0;
4641 aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(
4642 A_LOPG(ast), A_DTYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)), lParent_acltype);
4643 aclp->u1.expr->rop = construct_acl_from_ast(
4644 A_ROPG(ast), A_DTYPEG(A_ROPG(ast)), lParent_acltype);
4645
4646 if (!aclp->u1.expr->lop || !aclp->u1.expr->rop) {
4647 return 0;
4648 }
4649 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4650 prev = aclp;
4651 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4652 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4653 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4654 aclp->is_const = 1;
4655 aclp->subc = prev;
4656 }
4657 break;
4658 case A_UNOP:
4659 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4660 aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4661 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4662 aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4663 aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_NEG;
4664 if (get_ac_op(ast) == AC_LNOT)
4665 aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_LNOT;
4666 aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(A_LOPG(ast), A_DTYPEG(ast), 0);
4667 if (!aclp->u1.expr->lop) {
4668 return 0;
4669 }
4670 aclp->u1.expr->rop = NULL;
4671 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4672 prev = aclp;
4673 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4674 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4675 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4676 aclp->is_const = 1;
4677 aclp->subc = prev;
4678 }
4679 break;
4680 case A_CONV:
4681 if (DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast)) == DDTG(A_DTYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)))) {
4682 aclp = construct_acl_from_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0, 0);
4683 if (!aclp) {
4684 return 0;
4685 }
4686 } else {
4687 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4688 aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4689 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4690 aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4691 aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_CONV;
4692 aclp->u1.expr->lop =
4693 construct_acl_from_ast(A_LOPG(ast), DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast)), 0);
4694 if (!aclp->u1.expr->lop) {
4695 return 0;
4696 }
4697 aclp->u1.expr->rop = NULL;
4698 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4699 prev = aclp;
4700 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4701 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4702 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4703 aclp->is_const = 1;
4704 aclp->subc = prev;
4705 }
4706 }
4707 break;
4708 case A_SUBSCR:
4709 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4710 aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4711 aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4712 aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_ARRAYREF;
4713 aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0, 0);
4714 if (!aclp->u1.expr->lop) {
4715 return 0;
4716 }
4717 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4718 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
4719 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
4720 prev = NULL;
4721 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
4722 sub_ast = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
4723 subscr_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4724 subscr_aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4725 subscr_aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4726 subscr_aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_TRIPLE;
4727 subscr_aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(sub_ast);
4728 subscr_aclp->u1.expr->lop = NULL;
4729 if (prev == NULL) {
4730 aclp->u1.expr->rop = subscr_aclp;
4731 } else {
4732 prev->next = subscr_aclp;
4733 }
4734 prev = subscr_aclp;
4735
4736 l = GET_ACL(15);
4737 l->id = AC_AST;
4738 l->dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
4739 l->is_const = 1;
4740
4741 u = GET_ACL(15);
4742 u->id = AC_AST;
4743 u->dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
4744 u->is_const = 1;
4745
4746 s = GET_ACL(15);
4747 s->id = AC_AST;
4748 s->dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
4749 s->is_const = 1;
4750
4751 again:
4752 switch (A_TYPEG(sub_ast)) {
4753 case A_TRIPLE:
4754 l->u1.ast = A_LBDG(sub_ast);
4755 l->dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_LBDG(sub_ast));
4756 u->u1.ast = A_UPBDG(sub_ast);
4757 u->dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_UPBDG(sub_ast));
4758 if (A_STRIDEG(sub_ast) == 0) {
4759 s->u1.ast = astb.bnd.one;
4760 u->dtype = A_DTYPEG(astb.bnd.one);
4761 } else {
4762 s->u1.ast = A_STRIDEG(sub_ast);
4763 u->dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_STRIDEG(sub_ast));
4764 }
4765 break;
4766 case A_SUBSCR:
4767 /* This needs updated for sub_ast that is an array section
4768 * of multi-dimension array with rank one.
4769 */
4770 ast = sub_ast;
4771 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
4772 sub_ast = ASD_SUBS(asd, 0);
4773 subscr_aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0, 0);
4774 goto again;
4775 break;
4776 case A_CONV:
4777 ast = sub_ast;
4778 sub_ast = A_LOPG(sub_ast);
4779 goto again;
4780 break;
4781 case A_ID:
4782 if (DTY(A_DTYPEG(sub_ast)) == TY_ARRAY) {
4783 int shape;
4784 shape = A_SHAPEG(sub_ast);
4785 if (SHD_LWB(shape, 0)) {
4786 l->u1.ast = SHD_LWB(shape, 0);
4787 l->dtype = A_DTYPEG(SHD_LWB(shape, 0));
4788 } else {
4789 l->u1.ast = astb.bnd.one;
4790 l->dtype = A_DTYPEG(astb.bnd.one);
4791 }
4792 u->u1.ast = SHD_UPB(shape, 0);
4793 u->dtype = A_DTYPEG(SHD_UPB(shape, 0));
4794 s->u1.ast = astb.bnd.one;
4795 s->dtype = A_DTYPEG(astb.bnd.one);
4796 subscr_aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(sub_ast, 0, 0);
4797 break;
4798 }
4799 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
4800 default:
4801 l->u1.ast = sub_ast;
4802 l->dtype = A_DTYPEG(sub_ast);
4803 u->u1.ast = sub_ast;
4804 u->dtype = A_DTYPEG(sub_ast);
4805 s->u1.ast = astb.bnd.one;
4806 s->dtype = A_DTYPEG(astb.bnd.one);
4807 break;
4808 }
4809
4810 l->next = u;
4811 u->next = s;
4812 s->next = NULL;
4813 subscr_aclp->u1.expr->rop = l;
4814 }
4815 break;
4816 case A_MEM:
4817 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4818 aclp->id = AC_IEXPR;
4819 aclp->dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4820 aclp->u1.expr = (AEXPR *)getitem(15, sizeof(AEXPR));
4821 aclp->u1.expr->op = AC_MEMBR_SEL;
4822 aclp->u1.expr->lop = construct_acl_from_ast(A_PARENTG(ast), 0, 0);
4823 if (!aclp->u1.expr->lop) {
4824 return 0;
4825 }
4826
4827 /* find the field number */
4828 p_dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_PARENTG(ast));
4829 m_sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(ast));
4830 for (sptr = DTY(p_dtype + 1), i = 0; sptr > NOSYM && sptr != m_sptr;
4831 sptr = SYMLKG(sptr), i++)
4832 ;
4833 l = GET_ACL(15);
4834 l->id = AC_AST;
4835 l->dtype = DT_INT4;
4836 l->u1.ast = mk_cval(i, l->dtype);
4837
4838 aclp->u1.expr->rop = l;
4839 break;
4840 case A_INTR:
4841 aclp = construct_intrinsic_acl(ast, dtype, parent_acltype);
4842 if (aclp && DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast)) != TY_ARRAY &&
4843 parent_acltype != AC_ACONST &&
4844 !(STYPEG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))) == ST_PD &&
4845 PDNUMG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))) == PD_null)) {
4846 if (aclp->dtype == dtype) {
4847 if (aclp->subc && aclp->subc->repeatc == ADD_NUMELM(dtype))
4848 break;
4849 }
4850 aclp->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(dtype);
4851 prev = aclp;
4852 aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4853 aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4854 aclp->dtype = dtype;
4855 aclp->is_const = 1;
4856 aclp->subc = prev;
4857 }
4858
4859 break;
4860 default:
4861 interr("unexpected ast type in initialization expr", ast, 3);
4862 }
4863
4864 return aclp;
4865}
4866
4867static int
4868next_member(int member)
4869{
4870 int new_mbr = SYMLKG(member);
4871
4872 if (POINTERG(member) || ALLOCATTRG(member))
4873 while (new_mbr != NOSYM && HCCSYMG(new_mbr))
4874 new_mbr = SYMLKG(new_mbr);
4875
4876 return new_mbr == NOSYM ? 0 : new_mbr;
4877}
4878
4879ACL *
4880rewrite_acl(ACL *aclp, DTYPE dtype, int parent_acltype)
4881{
4882 SST *stkp;
4883 int ast;
4884 int sptr;
4885 int mbr_sptr;
4886 int wrk_dtype = dtype;
4887 DOINFO *doinfo;
4888 ACL *cur_aclp;
4889 ACL *wrk_aclp;
4890 ACL *prev_aclp = NULL;
4891 ACL *ret_aclp = aclp;
4892 ACL *sav_aclp = NULL;
4893 if (no_data_components(dtype) && !is_zero_size_typedef(dtype)) {
4894 return 0;
4895 }
4896 if (parent_acltype == AC_SCONST) {
4897 mbr_sptr = DTY(DDTG(dtype) + 1);
4898 wrk_dtype = DTYPEG(mbr_sptr);
4899 }
4900
4901 for (cur_aclp = aclp; cur_aclp != NULL; cur_aclp = cur_aclp->next) {
4902 wrk_aclp = cur_aclp;
4903 switch (cur_aclp->id) {
4904 case AC_EXPR:
4905 stkp = cur_aclp->u1.stkp;
4906 again:
4907 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
4908 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_ACONST) {
4909 /* attempt to avoid ICE by calling mkexpr() on
4910 * S_ACONST
4911 */
4912 mkexpr(stkp);
4913 if (SST_IDG(stkp) != S_ACONST)
4914 goto again;
4915 interr("rewrite_acl: unexpected S_ACONST", 0, 3);
4916 wrk_aclp->subc = SST_ACLG(stkp);
4917 wrk_aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4918 wrk_aclp->repeatc = 0;
4919 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
4920 sptr = SST_SYMG(stkp);
4921 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_PARAM || PARAMG(sptr)) {
4922 ast = mk_id(sptr);
4923 wrk_aclp = construct_acl_from_ast(ast, wrk_dtype, parent_acltype);
4924 wrk_aclp->u1.ast = ast;
4925 }
4926 /* MORE is this necessary */
4927 else if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_PD || STYPEG(sptr) == ST_INTRIN) {
4928 wrk_aclp = SST_ACLG(stkp);
4929 } else {
4930 errsev(87);
4931 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
4932 continue;
4933 }
4934 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_CONST) {
4935 wrk_aclp =
4936 construct_acl_from_ast(SST_ASTG(stkp), wrk_dtype, parent_acltype);
4937 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR &&
4938 (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CNST)) {
4939 wrk_aclp =
4940 construct_acl_from_ast(SST_ASTG(stkp), wrk_dtype, parent_acltype);
4941 } else
4942 wrk_aclp = construct_acl_from_ast(ast, wrk_dtype, parent_acltype);
4943 break;
4944 case AC_IDO:
4945 /* must make a copy of DOINFO because we don't know where
4946 * the current one was allocated or when it will be freed.
4947 */
4948 doinfo = get_doinfo(15);
4949 *doinfo = *cur_aclp->u1.doinfo;
4950 wrk_aclp->u1.doinfo = doinfo;
4951
4952 DOVARP(cur_aclp->u1.doinfo->index_var, 1);
4953 wrk_aclp->subc = rewrite_acl(cur_aclp->subc, DDTG(dtype), 0);
4954 if (!wrk_aclp->subc) {
4955 return 0;
4956 }
4957 DOVARP(cur_aclp->u1.doinfo->index_var, 0);
4958 wrk_aclp->repeatc = 0;
4959
4960 break;
4961 case AC_SCONST:
4962 case AC_TYPEINIT:
4963 wrk_aclp->subc =
4964 rewrite_acl(cur_aclp->subc, cur_aclp->dtype, cur_aclp->id);
4965 if (!wrk_aclp->subc && !is_zero_size_typedef(wrk_dtype)) {
4966 return 0;
4967 }
4968 if (DTY(wrk_dtype) == TY_ARRAY && parent_acltype != AC_ACONST) {
4969 wrk_aclp->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(wrk_dtype);
4970 sav_aclp = wrk_aclp;
4971 wrk_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
4972 wrk_aclp->id = AC_ACONST;
4973 wrk_aclp->dtype = wrk_dtype;
4974 wrk_aclp->is_const = 1;
4975 wrk_aclp->subc = sav_aclp;
4976 }
4977 break;
4978 case AC_ACONST:
4979 wrk_aclp->subc =
4980 rewrite_acl(cur_aclp->subc, cur_aclp->dtype, cur_aclp->id);
4981 if (!wrk_aclp->subc) {
4982 break;
4983 }
4984 wrk_aclp->repeatc = aclp->repeatc;
4985 break;
4986 case AC_AST:
4987 wrk_aclp = construct_acl_from_ast(cur_aclp->u1.ast, cur_aclp->dtype,
4988 parent_acltype);
4989 if (wrk_aclp) {
4990 wrk_aclp->repeatc = cur_aclp->repeatc;
4991 wrk_aclp->sptr = cur_aclp->sptr;
4992 }
4993 break;
4994 case AC_IEXPR:
4995 wrk_aclp = cur_aclp;
4996 break;
4997 case AC_REPEAT:
4998 default:
4999 interr("unexpected acl expresion type", cur_aclp->id, 3);
5000 break;
5001 }
5002
5003 if (wrk_aclp) {
5004 if (prev_aclp) {
5005 prev_aclp->next = wrk_aclp;
5006 } else {
5007 ret_aclp = wrk_aclp;
5008 }
5009 prev_aclp = wrk_aclp;
5010 }
5011
5012 if (parent_acltype == AC_SCONST) {
5013 mbr_sptr = next_member(mbr_sptr);
5014 wrk_dtype = DTYPEG(mbr_sptr);
5015 }
5016 }
5017
5018 if (sem.dinit_error) {
5019 ret_aclp = 0;
5020 }
5021
5022 return ret_aclp;
5023}
5024
5025static int
5026init_types_compatable(SST *istkp, DTYPE dtype, int sptr)
5027{
5028
5029 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_PD && PDNUMG(sptr) == PD_null &&
5030 SST_DTYPEG(istkp) == DT_WORD) {
5031 return TRUE;
5032 }
5033
5034 if ((DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY && DTY(dtype) != DTY(SST_DTYPEG(istkp))) ||
5035 (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(SST_DTYPEG(istkp)) == TY_ARRAY &&
5036 !cmpat_dtype_with_size(dtype, SST_DTYPEG(istkp))) ||
5037 (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && DTY(SST_DTYPEG(istkp)) != TY_ARRAY &&
5038 DDTG(dtype) != SST_DTYPEG(istkp))) {
5039 return FALSE;
5040 }
5041 return TRUE;
5042}
5043
5044void
5045construct_acl_for_sst(SST *istkp, DTYPE dtype)
5046{
5047 ACL *aclp = 0;
5048 int sptr = 0;
5049
5050 switch (SST_IDG(istkp)) {
5051 case S_IDENT:
5052 /* the ident must be a named constant or an alias for a named constant */
5053 aclp = SST_ACLG(istkp);
5054 if (aclp) {
5055 sptr = A_SPTRG(aclp->u1.ast);
5056 } else {
5057 sptr = SST_SYMG(istkp);
5058 }
5059 if ((!sptr || !(STYPEG(sptr) == ST_PARAM || PARAMG(sptr))) &&
5060 (!has_type_parameter(dtype) || !sem.param_struct_constr)) {
5061 if (!no_data_components(dtype)) {
5062 errsev(87);
5063 }
5064 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
5065 SST_ACLP(istkp, 0);
5066 return;
5067 }
5068 /* the types must be compatable */
5069 if (!init_types_compatable(istkp, dtype, sptr)) {
5070 errsev(91);
5071 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
5072 SST_ACLP(istkp, 0);
5073 return;
5074 }
5075 if (!aclp) {
5076 /* PARAMETER defined in a module, already processed */
5077 SST_ACLP(istkp, (ACL *)get_getitem_p(CONVAL2G(NMCNSTG(sptr))));
5078 } else if (DTY(DDTG(dtype)) == TY_DERIVED) {
5079 SST_ACLP(istkp, construct_acl_from_ast(aclp->u1.ast, dtype, 0));
5080 }
5081 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && (aclp = SST_ACLG(istkp)) &&
5082 DTY(aclp->dtype) != TY_ARRAY && aclp->id == AC_IEXPR &&
5083 aclp->u1.expr->op == AC_INTR_CALL) {
5084 aclp->repeatc = ADD_NUMELM(dtype);
5085 }
5086 break;
5087 case S_EXPR:
5088 case S_CONST:
5089 case S_LVALUE:
5090 SST_ACLP(istkp, construct_acl_from_ast(SST_ASTG(istkp), dtype, 0));
5091 break;
5092 case S_ACONST:
5093 SST_ACLP(istkp, rewrite_acl(SST_ACLG(istkp), dtype, 0));
5094 break;
5095 case S_SCONST:
5096 if (DDTG(dtype) != SST_DTYPEG(istkp)) {
5097 if (DTY(DDTG(dtype)) == TY_DERIVED &&
5098 DTY(SST_DTYPEG(istkp)) == TY_DERIVED) {
5099
5100 /* For parameterized derived types, the following from F2008 spec
5101 * applies (there's similar language in F2003 spec):
5102 * Section 5.2.3 ...
5103 * If initialization is = constant-expr, the variable is initially
5104 * defined with the value specified by the constant-expr; if
5105 * necessary, the value is converted according to the rules of
5106 * intrinsic assignment (7.2.1.3) to a value that agrees in type,
5107 * type parameters, and shape with the variable.
5108 *
5109 * Therefore, if the type on the LHS is a parameterized derived
5110 * type, check its "base type" with the type on the RHS. If they
5111 * are identical, then we have a legal initialization since the
5112 * value is to be "converted".
5113 */
5114
5115 int tag1, dty1, dty2;
5116 tag1 = DTY(DDTG(dtype) + 3);
5117 dty1 = (BASETYPEG(tag1)) ? BASETYPEG(tag1) : DDTG(dtype);
5118 dty2 = SST_DTYPEG(istkp);
5119 if (dty1 == dty2)
5120 goto sconst_ok;
5121 }
5122 errsev(91);
5123 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
5124 SST_ACLP(istkp, 0);
5125 return;
5126 }
5127 sconst_ok:
5128 SST_ACLP(istkp, rewrite_acl(SST_ACLG(istkp), dtype, 0));
5129 break;
5130 default:
5131 interr("unexpected sst type for initialization list", SST_IDG(istkp), 3);
5132 }
5133}
5134
5135ACL *
5136get_acl(int area)
5137{
5138 ACL *a;
5139 a = (ACL *)getitem(area, sizeof(ACL));
5140 BZERO(a, ACL, 1);
5141 return a;
5142}
5143
5144ACL *
5145save_acl(ACL *oldp)
5146{
5147 ACL *rootp, *newp;
5148 SST *stkp;
5149 DOINFO *doinfo;
5150
5151 if (oldp == NULL)
5152 return NULL;
5153
5154 rootp = newp = GET_ACL(15);
5155
5156 while (TRUE) {
5157 *newp = *oldp;
5158 switch (oldp->id) {
5159 case AC_EXPR:
5160 stkp = oldp->u1.stkp;
5161 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_ACONST) {
5162 newp->subc = SST_ACLG(stkp);
5163 newp->id = AC_ACONST;
5164 } else if (oldp->repeatc && oldp->size) {
5165 } else {
5166 newp->u1.ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
5167 newp->id = AC_AST;
5168 }
5169 break;
5170 case AC_IDO:
5171 newp->subc = save_acl(oldp->subc);
5172 doinfo = get_doinfo(ACL_SAVE_AREA);
5173 *doinfo = *oldp->u1.doinfo;
5174 newp->u1.doinfo = doinfo;
5175 break;
5176 case AC_REPEAT:
5177 case AC_SCONST:
5178 case AC_ACONST:
5179 newp->subc = save_acl(oldp->subc);
5180 break;
5181 case AC_AST:
5182 case AC_ICONST:
5183 case AC_CONST:
5184 break;
5185 case AC_IEXPR:
5186 if (newp->u1.expr->lop) {
5187 newp->u1.expr->lop = save_acl(oldp->u1.expr->lop);
5188 }
5189 if (newp->u1.expr->rop) {
5190 newp->u1.expr->rop = save_acl(oldp->u1.expr->rop);
5191 }
5192 break;
5193 default:
5194 interr("save_acl,ill.id", oldp->id, 3);
5195 break;
5196 }
5197 oldp = oldp->next;
5198 if (oldp == NULL)
5199 break;
5200 newp->next = GET_ACL(15);
5201 newp = newp->next;
5202 }
5203
5204 return rootp;
5205}
5206
5207static int dinit_array = 0;
5208static void
5209dinit_constructor(SPTR arr, ACL *aclp)
5210{
5211 if (DINITG(arr))
5212 return;
5213
5214 {
5215 VAR *ivl = (VAR *)getitem(15, sizeof(VAR));
5216 int ast = mk_id(arr);
5217 SCP(arr, SC_STATIC);
5218 STYPEP(arr, ST_ARRAY);
5219 ivl->id = Varref;
5220 ivl->u.varref.ptr = ast;
5221 ivl->u.varref.id = S_IDENT;
5222 ivl->u.varref.dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
5223 ivl->u.varref.shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
5224 ivl->u.varref.subt = NULL;
5225 ivl->next = NULL;
5226 DINITP(arr, 1);
5227 if (SCG(arr) != SC_NONE)
5228 sym_is_refd(arr);
5229
5230 dinit(ivl, aclp);
5231 }
5232 DINITP(arr, 1); /* will set for ST_DERIVED arrays, too - to indicate that
5233 components have been inited. */
5234}
5235
5236static void
5237put_a_init_tree(int ast, int dinit_array)
5238{
5239 ACL temp;
5240 for (; ast; ast = A_RIGHTG(ast)) {
5241 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_INIT) {
5242 interr("put_a_init_tree: unknown ast type", A_TYPEG(ast), 3);
5243 } else {
5244 DTYPE dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
5245 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
5246 case TY_ARRAY:
5247 put_a_init_tree(A_LEFTG(ast), dinit_array);
5248 break;
5249 case TY_DERIVED:
5250 dinit_put(DINIT_TYPEDEF, DTY(dtype + 3));
5251 put_a_init_tree(A_LEFTG(ast), dinit_array);
5252 dinit_put(DINIT_ENDTYPE, 0);
5253 break;
5254 default:
5255 temp.id = AC_AST;
5256 temp.u1.ast = A_LEFTG(ast);
5257 temp.next = NULL;
5258 temp.subc = NULL;
5259 temp.dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_LEFTG(ast));
5260 temp.u2.array_i = dinit_array;
5261 _dinit_acl(&temp, FALSE);
5262 break;
5263 }
5264 }
5265 }
5266} /* put_a_init_tree */
5267
5268static void
5269_dinit_acl(ACL *aclp, LOGICAL optimpldo)
5270{
5271 SST *stkp;
5272 DOINFO *doinfo;
5273 int ast, last, lastright;
5274 DTYPE dtype;
5275 int sptr;
5276 INT count, step;
5277 DOSTACK *tp;
5278
5279 for (; aclp != NULL; aclp = aclp->next) {
5280 switch (aclp->id) {
5281 case AC_EXPR:
5282 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
5283 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
5284 _dinit_acl(stkp->value.cnval.acl, FALSE);
5285 } else {
5286 /* the only AC_EXPR's left are those with A_INIT trees */
5287 ast = aclp->repeatc;
5288 last = aclp->size;
5289 /* break the list at 'last' */
5290 lastright = A_RIGHTG(last);
5291 A_RIGHTP(last, 0);
5292 put_a_init_tree(ast, dinit_array);
5293 /* restore the list at 'last' */
5294 A_RIGHTP(last, lastright);
5295 }
5296 break;
5297 case AC_AST:
5298 ast = aclp->u1.ast;
5299 sptr = 0;
5300 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
5301 if (ast && A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID) {
5302 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
5303 }
5304 if (sptr && (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_VAR || STYPEG(sptr) == ST_ARRAY) &&
5305 PARAMVALG(sptr)) {
5306 /* put out the initialization values */
5307 put_a_init_tree(PARAMVALG(sptr), dinit_array);
5308 } else if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
5309 /* constructor item is an array */
5310 interr("_dinit_acl,array", ast, 3);
5311 } else if (A_ALIASG(ast)) {
5312 /* constructor item is a scalar constant */
5313 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
5314 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
5315 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
5316 case TY_WORD:
5317 case TY_BINT:
5318 case TY_SINT:
5319 case TY_INT:
5320 case TY_BLOG:
5321 case TY_SLOG:
5322 case TY_LOG:
5323 case TY_REAL:
5324 dinit_put(dtype, CONVAL2G(sptr));
5325 break;
5326 case TY_CHAR:
5327 dinit_put(DINIT_STR, (INT)sptr);
5328 break;
5329 default:
5330 dinit_put(dtype, (INT)sptr);
5331 break;
5332 }
5333 } else if (DTY(astb.bnd.dtype) == TY_INT8) {
5334 /* constructor item is a scalar expression*/
5335 INT v[2];
5336
5337 /* NOTE: dinit_eval() returns a 4-byte int. this is
5338 wrong, but until it gets fixed, this will have to
5339 do. */
5340 v[1] = dinit_eval(ast);
5341 if (v[1] < 0)
5342 v[0] = -1;
5343 else
5344 v[0] = 0;
5345 dinit_put(astb.bnd.dtype, getcon(v, astb.bnd.dtype));
5346 } else
5347 /* constructor item is a scalar expression*/
5348 dinit_put(astb.bnd.dtype, dinit_eval(ast));
5349
5350 break;
5351 case AC_SCONST:
5352 dinit_put(DINIT_TYPEDEF, DTY(aclp->dtype + 3));
5353 _dinit_acl(aclp->subc, FALSE);
5354 dinit_put(DINIT_ENDTYPE, 0);
5355 break;
5356 case AC_ACONST:
5357 dinit_put(DINIT_STARTARY, 0);
5358 _dinit_acl(aclp->subc, FALSE);
5359 dinit_put(DINIT_ENDARY, 0);
5360 break;
5361 case AC_IDO:
5362 doinfo = aclp->u1.doinfo;
5363 if (sem.top == &sem.dostack[MAX_DOSTACK]) {
5364 /* nesting maximum exceeded. */
5365 errsev(34);
5366 return;
5367 }
5368 count = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(doinfo->count)));
5369 tp = sem.top;
5370 tp->sptr = doinfo->index_var;
5371 tp->currval = dinit_eval(doinfo->init_expr);
5372 step = dinit_eval(doinfo->step_expr);
5373 ++sem.top;
5374 /*
5375 * optimize the case where the initializer controlled by the
5376 * implied do is a single scalar constant
5377 */
5378 if (optimpldo && aclp->subc->id == AC_AST && aclp->subc->next == NULL &&
5379 DTY(A_DTYPEG(aclp->subc->u1.ast)) != TY_ARRAY &&
5380 A_ALIASG(aclp->subc->u1.ast)) {
5381 dinit_put(DINIT_REPEAT, count);
5382 _dinit_acl(aclp->subc, optimpldo);
5383 tp->currval += count * step;
5384 } else
5385 while (count-- > 0) {
5386 _dinit_acl(aclp->subc, optimpldo);
5387 tp->currval += step;
5388 }
5389 --sem.top;
5390 break;
5391 case AC_REPEAT:
5392 dinit_put(DINIT_REPEAT, aclp->u1.count);
5393 ast = aclp->subc->u1.ast;
5394 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
5395 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
5396 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
5397 if (DT_ISWORD(dtype))
5398 dinit_put(dtype, CONVAL2G(sptr));
5399 else
5400 dinit_put(dtype, (INT)sptr);
5401 break;
5402 default:
5403 interr("_dinit_acl,ill.id", aclp->id, 3);
5404 break;
5405 }
5406 }
5407}
5408
5409typedef struct struct_init {
5410 int default_count; /* is sptr+1, sptr is the last default init */
5411 int dt_count; /* number of members */
5412 ACL **default_acl; /* if sptr is inited, points to default acl*/
5413 ACL **dt_acl; /* points to all inited acl */
5414} struct_init;
5415
5416static struct_init dt_init = {0, 0, NULL, NULL};
5417
5418#define DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD dt_init.default_acl
5419#define DTC_ACL_HEAD dt_init.dt_acl
5420#define DTC_DEFAULT(i) dt_init.default_acl[i]
5421#define DTC_ACL(i) dt_init.dt_acl[i]
5422#define DTC_DEFAULT_CNT dt_init.default_count
5423#define DTC_DT_CNT dt_init.dt_count
5424
5425static char *
5426make_structkwd_str(DTYPE dtype, int *num_of_member, int *is_extend)
5427{
5428 int i;
5429 char *name;
5430 int optional = 1; /* all are optional */
5431 int len;
5432 int size;
5433 int avl;
5434 int member_sptr, ptr_sptr = 0, thissptr, myparent;
5435 char *kwd_str = NULL;
5436 char *first_str = NULL;
5437 int num, is_extend2, num_of_member2;
5438 int possible_ext = 1;
5439
5440 num = 0;
5441 avl = 0;
5442 i = 0;
5443 len = 0;
5444 size = 100;
5445 NEW(kwd_str, char, size);
5446 *kwd_str = '\0';
5447 member_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5448 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
5449 for (; member_sptr > NOSYM; member_sptr = SYMLKG(member_sptr)) {
5450 if (POINTERG(member_sptr))
5451 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
5452 if (is_tbp_or_final(member_sptr)) {
5453 possible_ext = 0;
5454 continue; /* skip tbp */
5455 }
5456 name = SYMNAME(member_sptr);
5457 len = strlen(name);
5458 if (ptr_sptr &&
5459 (member_sptr == MIDNUMG(ptr_sptr) || member_sptr == PTROFFG(ptr_sptr) ||
5460 member_sptr == SDSCG(ptr_sptr) ||
5461 (CLASSG(member_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)))) {
5462 /* skip pointer related members */
5463 possible_ext = 0;
5464 continue;
5465 }
5466 ptr_sptr =
5467 USELENG(member_sptr) || POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr)
5468 ? member_sptr
5469 : 0;
5470
5471 /* NOTE: should make kwd_str static */
5472 thissptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5473 myparent = PARENTG(thissptr);
5474 if (myparent && myparent == PARENTG(member_sptr) && possible_ext &&
5475 (DTY(DTYPEG(member_sptr)) == TY_DERIVED ||
5476 DTY(DTYPEG(member_sptr)) == TY_STRUCT)) {
5477 *is_extend = 1;
5478 first_str =
5479 make_structkwd_str(DTYPEG(member_sptr), &num_of_member2, &is_extend2);
5480 len = strlen(first_str);
5481 i = 0;
5482 num += num_of_member2;
5483 avl += len; /* len chars in name, 1 for ' ', 1 for null */
5484 if (avl > size) {
5485 NEED(avl, kwd_str, char, size, size + avl + 100);
5486 }
5487 strcpy(kwd_str, first_str);
5488 FREE(first_str);
5489 } else {
5490 if (member_sptr <= DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - 1 && DTC_DEFAULT(member_sptr))
5491 optional = 1;
5492 else
5493 optional = 0;
5494 i = avl;
5495 avl +=
5496 (optional + len + 2); /* len chars in name, 1 for ' ', 1 for null */
5497 NEED(avl, kwd_str, char, size, size + 100);
5498 if (optional)
5499 kwd_str[i++] = '*';
5500 strcpy(kwd_str + i, name);
5501 kwd_str[i + len] = ' ';
5502 kwd_str[i + len + 1] = '\0';
5503 ++num;
5504 avl--;
5505 }
5506 possible_ext = 0; /* only the first member is extended type member */
5507 }
5508
5509 *num_of_member = num;
5510
5511 /* Allocate ACL pointers to all members , reuse if possible*/
5512 if (DTC_DT_CNT < num) {
5513 NEED(num, DTC_ACL_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DT_CNT, num);
5514 }
5515 BZERO(DTC_ACL_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DT_CNT);
5516 return kwd_str;
5517}
5518
5519void
5520clean_struct_default_init(int sptr)
5521{
5522 int i;
5523 if (sptr == 0) {
5524 FREE(DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD);
5525 FREE(DTC_ACL_HEAD);
5526 DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD = NULL;
5527 DTC_ACL_HEAD = NULL;
5528 DTC_DEFAULT_CNT = 0;
5529 DTC_DT_CNT = 0;
5530 } else {
5531 /* only clean from the sptr, this is a case of contained routine */
5532 if (DTC_DEFAULT_CNT == 0)
5533 return;
5534 for (i = sptr; i < DTC_DEFAULT_CNT; ++i) {
5535 DTC_DEFAULT(i) = NULL;
5536 }
5537 DTC_DT_CNT = 0;
5538 FREE(DTC_ACL_HEAD);
5539 DTC_ACL_HEAD = NULL;
5540 }
5541}
5542
5543int
5544has_init_value(SPTR sptr)
5545{
5546 if (sptr < DTC_DEFAULT_CNT) {
5547 if (DTC_DEFAULT(sptr))
5548 return 1;
5549 }
5550 return 0;
5551}
5552
5553static ACL *
5554rewrite_typeinit_to_sconst(ACL *ict)
5555{
5556 ACL *newacl = ict;
5557 if (ict->id == AC_TYPEINIT) {
5558 newacl = GET_ACL(15);
5559 newacl->id = AC_SCONST;
5560 newacl->dtype = ict->dtype;
5561 newacl->next = ict->next;
5562 newacl->repeatc = ict->repeatc;
5563 newacl->subc = rewrite_typeinit_to_sconst(ict->subc);
5564 }
5565 return newacl;
5566}
5567
5568/** \brief Duplicate a derived type component's default initializations.
5569 *
5570 * \param new_sptr is the component that receives the initialization copy.
5571 * \param old_sptr has the default initialization that we want to duplicate.
5572 *
5573 * We need to duplicate the initialization of a derived type component when
5574 * we create new instances of the derived type with different kind/len
5575 * type parameters.
5576 */
5577void
5578dup_struct_init(int new_sptr, int old_sptr)
5579{
5580
5581 if (!has_init_value(old_sptr))
5582 return;
5583
5584 if (DTC_DEFAULT_CNT == 0) {
5585 NEED(new_sptr + 1, DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT, new_sptr + 10);
5586 BZERO(DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT);
5587 } else if (DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - 1 < new_sptr) {
5588 int oldcnt = DTC_DEFAULT_CNT;
5589 NEED(new_sptr + 1, DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT, new_sptr + 10);
5590 BZERO((DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD + oldcnt), ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - oldcnt);
5591 }
5592
5593 DTC_DEFAULT(new_sptr) = DTC_DEFAULT(old_sptr);
5594}
5595
5596void
5597save_struct_init(ACL *ict)
5598{
5599 ACL *newacl = ict;
5600
5601 if (DTC_DEFAULT_CNT == 0) {
5602 NEED(ict->sptr + 1, DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT,
5603 ict->sptr + 10);
5604 BZERO(DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT);
5605 } else if (DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - 1 < ict->sptr) {
5606 int oldcnt = DTC_DEFAULT_CNT;
5607 NEED(ict->sptr + 1, DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD, ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT,
5608 ict->sptr + 10);
5609 BZERO((DTC_DEFAULT_HEAD + oldcnt), ACL *, DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - oldcnt);
5610 }
5611#if DEBUG
5612#endif
5613
5614 if (ict->id == AC_TYPEINIT) {
5615 newacl = rewrite_typeinit_to_sconst(ict);
5616 }
5617
5618 /* in module, the ..$p is put in .mod file instead of member symbol */
5619 if (HCCSYMG(ict->sptr) && NEEDMODG(SCOPEG(ict->sptr))) {
5620 int sptr = VARIANTG(ict->sptr);
5621 if ((POINTERG(sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(sptr))) {
5622 if (MIDNUMG(sptr) == ict->sptr && SYMLKG(sptr) == ict->sptr) {
5623 DTC_DEFAULT(sptr) = newacl;
5624 return;
5625 }
5626 }
5627 }
5628 DTC_DEFAULT(ict->sptr) = newacl;
5629}
5630
5631static ACL *
5632get_struct_default_init(int sptr)
5633{
5634 if (sptr > 0 && sptr <= DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - 1) {
5635 ACL *init_acl = DTC_DEFAULT(sptr);
5636 if (init_acl) {
5637 return clone_init_const(init_acl, 0);
5638 }
5639 return init_acl;
5640 } else {
5641 return NULL;
5642 }
5643}
5644
5645/** \brief Check whether derived type has components with default
5646 * initializations.
5647 *
5648 * \param dtype is the derived type we want to check.
5649 *
5650 * \return pointer to first default initializer, else NULL.
5651 */
5652ACL *
5653all_default_init(DTYPE dtype)
5654{
5655 int mem, myparent, thissptr;
5656 ACL *rslt, *dflt;
5657 int possible_ext = 1;
5658
5659 rslt = dflt = NULL;
5660 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_DERIVED && DTY(dtype) != TY_STRUCT &&
5661 DTY(dtype) != TY_UNION) {
5662 return NULL;
5663 }
5664
5665 thissptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5666 for (mem = DTY(dtype + 1); mem > NOSYM; mem = SYMLKG(mem)) {
5667 if (POINTERG(mem))
5668 thissptr = mem;
5669 myparent = PARENTG(thissptr);
5670 if (myparent && myparent == PARENTG(mem) && possible_ext &&
5671 DTY(DTYPEG(mem)) == TY_DERIVED) {
5672 dflt = all_default_init(DTYPEG(mem));
5673 if (dflt)
5674 return dflt;
5675 } else {
5676 if (is_tbp_or_final(mem))
5677 continue; /* skip tbp */
5678 if (thissptr &&
5679 (mem == MIDNUMG(thissptr) || mem == PTROFFG(thissptr) ||
5680 mem == SDSCG(thissptr) || (CLASSG(mem) && DESCARRAYG(mem)))) {
5681 /* skip pointer related members */
5682 possible_ext = 0;
5683 continue;
5684 }
5685 if (mem > 0 && mem <= DTC_DEFAULT_CNT - 1) {
5686 rslt = DTC_DEFAULT(mem);
5687 if (rslt == NULL) {
5688 return NULL;
5689 } else if (!dflt) {
5690 dflt = clone_init_const(rslt, 0);
5691 }
5692 } else {
5693 return NULL;
5694 }
5695 }
5696 possible_ext = 0;
5697 }
5698 return dflt;
5699}
5700
5701static ACL *
5702get_exttype_list(int cnt)
5703{
5704 int i;
5705 ACL *first = NULL;
5706 ACL *prev = NULL;
5707 for (i = 0; i < cnt; ++i) {
5708 if (DTC_ACL(i)) {
5709 if (first == NULL) {
5710 first = DTC_ACL(i);
5711 prev = first;
5712 prev->next = NULL;
5713 } else {
5714 prev->next = DTC_ACL(i);
5715 prev = prev->next;
5716 prev->next = NULL;
5717 }
5718 }
5719 }
5720 return first;
5721}
5722
5723static int
5724set_exttype_list(ACL *aclp)
5725{
5726 int i;
5727 ACL *first = aclp;
5728 for (i = 0; first != NULL; ++i) {
5729 DTC_ACL(i) = first;
5730 first = first->next;
5731 }
5732 for (; i < DTC_DT_CNT; ++i) {
5733 DTC_ACL(i) = 0;
5734 }
5735 return i;
5736}
5737
5738static int
5739get_exttype_default(DTYPE dtype, int pos)
5740{
5741 int ptr_sptr = 0, thissptr, myparent;
5742 int member_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5743 int possible_ext = 1;
5744 if (pos >= DTC_DT_CNT)
5745 return pos;
5746
5747 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
5748 for (; member_sptr > NOSYM; member_sptr = SYMLKG(member_sptr)) {
5749 if (no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_sptr))) {
5750 possible_ext = 0;
5751 continue;
5752 }
5753 if (CLASSG(member_sptr) && VTABLEG(member_sptr) && BINDG(member_sptr)) {
5754 possible_ext = 0;
5755 continue;
5756 }
5757 if (POINTERG(member_sptr))
5758 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
5759 if (ptr_sptr &&
5760 (member_sptr == MIDNUMG(ptr_sptr) || member_sptr == PTROFFG(ptr_sptr) ||
5761 member_sptr == SDSCG(ptr_sptr) ||
5762 (CLASSG(member_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)))) {
5763 /* skip pointer related members */
5764 possible_ext = 0;
5765 continue;
5766 }
5767 ptr_sptr =
5768 USELENG(member_sptr) || POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr)
5769 ? member_sptr
5770 : 0;
5771
5772 thissptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5773 myparent = PARENTG(thissptr);
5774 if (myparent && myparent == PARENTG(member_sptr) && possible_ext &&
5775 DTY(DTYPEG(member_sptr)) == TY_DERIVED) {
5776 if (!no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_sptr)))
5777 pos = get_exttype_default(DTYPEG(member_sptr), pos);
5778 } else {
5779 if (DTC_ACL(pos) == NULL)
5780 DTC_ACL(pos) = get_struct_default_init(member_sptr);
5781 ++pos;
5782 }
5783
5784 possible_ext = 0; /* only the first member is extended type member */
5785 if (pos > DTC_DT_CNT)
5786 return pos;
5787 }
5788 return pos;
5789}
5790
5791/* Also create a new ACL of base type if the initialization list of
5792 * extended type is not in the form of base_type(..).
5793 * This is getting complicated.
5794 */
5795
5796static LOGICAL
5797get_keyword_components(ACL *in_aclp, int cnt, char *kwdarg, DTYPE dtype,
5798 int is_extend)
5799{
5800 SST *stkp;
5801 int pos;
5802 int i;
5803 char *kwd, *np;
5804 int kwd_len;
5805 char *actual_kwd; /* name of keyword used with the actual arg */
5806 int actual_kwd_len;
5807 LOGICAL kwd_present;
5808 ACL *t_aclp, *aclp = in_aclp->subc;
5809 int member_sptr;
5810
5811 /* convention for the keyword 'variable' arguments ---
5812 * the keyword specifier is of the form
5813 * #<pos>#<base>#<kwd>
5814 * where,
5815 * <pos> = digit indicating the zero-relative positional index where
5816 * the variable arguments begin in the argument list.
5817 * <base> = digit indicating value to be subtracted from the digit
5818 * string suffix of the keyword.
5819 * <kwd> = name of the keyword which varies (i.e., the prefix).
5820 */
5821
5822 if (*kwdarg == '\0' || *kwdarg == ' ')
5823 return TRUE;
5824 kwd_present = FALSE;
5825 for (i = 0; i < cnt; i++) {
5826 DTC_ACL(i) = NULL;
5827 }
5828
5829 for (pos = 0; aclp != NULL; pos++) {
5830 if (aclp->id == AC_EXPR) {
5831 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
5832 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_KEYWORD) {
5833 kwd_present = TRUE;
5834 actual_kwd = scn.id.name + SST_CVALG(stkp);
5835 actual_kwd_len = strlen(actual_kwd);
5836 kwd = kwdarg;
5837 for (i = 0; TRUE; i++) {
5838 if (*kwd == '*')
5839 kwd++;
5840 kwd_len = 0;
5841 for (np = kwd; TRUE; np++, kwd_len++)
5842 if (*np == ' ' || *np == '\0')
5843 break;
5844 if (kwd_len == actual_kwd_len &&
5845 strncmp(kwd, actual_kwd, actual_kwd_len) == 0)
5846 break;
5847 if (*np == '\0')
5848 goto ill_keyword;
5849 kwd = np + 1; /* skip over blank */
5850 }
5851 if (i > cnt)
5852 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
5853 "Too many elements in structure constructor", CNULL);
5854 if (DTC_ACL(i))
5855 goto ill_keyword;
5856 stkp = SST_E3G(stkp);
5857 aclp->u1.stkp = stkp; /* Should this be done?*/
5858 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_SCONST)
5859 DTC_ACL(i) = SST_ACLG(stkp);
5860 else
5861 DTC_ACL(i) = aclp; /* should SST_IDG change?*/
5862 } else {
5863 if (kwd_present) {
5864 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
5865 "Positional components must not follow keyword arguments",
5866 CNULL);
5867 return TRUE;
5868 }
5869 if (pos > cnt)
5870 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
5871 "Too many elements in structure constructor", CNULL);
5872 if (DTC_ACL(pos)) {
5873 char print[22];
5874 kwd = kwdarg;
5875 for (i = 0; TRUE; i++) {
5876 if (*kwd == '*' || *kwd == ' ')
5877 kwd++;
5878 if (*kwd == '\0') {
5879 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
5880 "Invalid element in structure constructor", CNULL);
5881 return TRUE;
5882 }
5883 kwd_len = 0;
5884 for (np = kwd; TRUE; np++) {
5885 if (*np == ' ' || *np == '\0')
5886 break;
5887 kwd_len++;
5888 }
5889 if (i == pos)
5890 break;
5891 kwd = np;
5892 }
5893 if (kwd_len > 21)
5894 kwd_len = 21;
5895 strncpy(print, kwd, kwd_len);
5896 print[kwd_len] = '\0';
5897 error(79, 3, gbl.lineno, print, CNULL);
5898 return TRUE;
5899 }
5900 DTC_ACL(pos) = aclp;
5901 }
5902 } else {
5903 if (kwd_present) {
5904 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
5905 "Positional components must not follow keyword components",
5906 CNULL);
5907 return TRUE;
5908 }
5909 DTC_ACL(pos) = aclp;
5910 }
5911 aclp = aclp->next;
5912 if (pos > cnt)
5913 errsev(67);
5914 }
5915
5916 if (is_extend) {
5917 /* for extended type, the first member is the base type. */
5918 /* if kwd_present, then it must list all members in base type(s). */
5919 aclp = in_aclp->subc;
5920 member_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
5921 if (!no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_sptr))) {
5922 if (kwd_present || pos < cnt) {
5923 /* get default value here if keyword is present */
5924 pos = get_exttype_default(dtype, 0);
5925 }
5926 aclp = get_exttype_list(cnt);
5927 if (!(aclp->id == AC_SCONST &&
5928 cmpat_dtype_with_size(aclp->dtype, DTYPEG(member_sptr)))) {
5929 aclp = get_exttype_struct_constructor(aclp, dtype, &t_aclp);
5930 }
5931 in_aclp->subc = aclp;
5932 return kwd_present;
5933 }
5934 }
5935
5936 /* determine if required component is not present. */
5937
5938 kwd = kwdarg;
5939 for (pos = 0; pos < cnt; pos++, kwd = np) {
5940 if (*kwd == ' ')
5941 kwd++;
5942 kwd_len = 0;
5943 for (np = kwd; TRUE; np++) {
5944 if (*np == ' ' || *np == '\0')
5945 break;
5946 kwd_len++;
5947 }
5948 if (DTC_ACL(pos) && sem.new_param_dt) {
5949 /* We have an initializer in a type parameter position...
5950 * skip over the type parameter since it is not defined in
5951 * the structure constructor portion of the syntax. Instead,
5952 * set the next component to this value and the type parameter
5953 * to its default value.
5954 */
5955 int i;
5956 char *buf = getitem(0, kwd_len + 1);
5957 strncpy(buf, kwd, kwd_len);
5958 buf[kwd_len] = '\0';
5959
5960 if (*buf == '*')
5961 ++buf;
5962
5963 put_default_kind_type_param(sem.new_param_dt, 0, 0);
5964 put_length_type_param(sem.new_param_dt, 0);
5965
5966 i = get_kind_parm_by_name(buf, sem.new_param_dt);
5967 if (i != 0) {
5968 SST *e1;
5969 int j;
5970
5971 for (j = (cnt - 1); j > pos; --j)
5972 DTC_ACL(j) = DTC_ACL(j - 1);
5973
5974 e1 = (SST *)getitem(ACL_SAVE_AREA, sizeof(SST));
5975 if (i < 0) {
5976 int val = 0;
5977 i = get_len_set_parm_by_name(buf, sem.new_param_dt, &val);
5978 if (val) {
5979 SST_IDP(e1, S_EXPR);
5980 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
5981 SST_ASTP(e1, val);
5982 } else {
5983 SST_IDP(e1, S_CONST);
5984 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
5985 SST_CVALP(e1, i);
5986 SST_ASTP(e1, mk_cval1(i, DT_INT));
5987 SST_SHAPEP(e1, 0);
5988 }
5989 } else {
5990
5991 SST_IDP(e1, S_CONST);
5992 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
5993 SST_CVALP(e1, i);
5994 SST_ASTP(e1, mk_cval1(i, DT_INT));
5995 SST_SHAPEP(e1, 0);
5996 }
5997
5998 t_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
5999 t_aclp->id = AC_EXPR;
6000 t_aclp->repeatc = t_aclp->size = 0;
6001 t_aclp->next = NULL;
6002 t_aclp->subc = NULL;
6003 t_aclp->u1.stkp = e1;
6004 DTC_ACL(pos) = t_aclp;
6005 continue;
6006 }
6007 } else if (DTC_ACL(pos) == NULL) {
6008 /* If missing value in structure constructor is a type parameter,
6009 * then fill in the value here.
6010 */
6011 int i;
6012 char *buf = getitem(0, kwd_len + 1);
6013 strncpy(buf, kwd, kwd_len);
6014 buf[kwd_len] = '\0';
6015 if (*buf == '*')
6016 ++buf;
6017 if (sem.new_param_dt) {
6018 /* Make sure the default values are initialized */
6019 put_default_kind_type_param(sem.new_param_dt, 0, 0);
6020 put_length_type_param(sem.new_param_dt, 0);
6021 }
6022 if ((sem.new_param_dt &&
6023 (i = get_kind_parm_by_name(buf, sem.new_param_dt)))) {
6024 SST *e1;
6025 e1 = (SST *)getitem(ACL_SAVE_AREA, sizeof(SST));
6026 if (i < 0) {
6027 int val = 0;
6028 i = get_len_set_parm_by_name(buf, sem.new_param_dt, &val);
6029 if (val) {
6030 SST_IDP(e1, S_EXPR);
6031 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
6032 SST_ASTP(e1, val);
6033 } else {
6034 SST_IDP(e1, S_CONST);
6035 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
6036 SST_CVALP(e1, i);
6037 SST_ASTP(e1, mk_cval1(i, DT_INT));
6038 SST_SHAPEP(e1, 0);
6039 }
6040 } else {
6041
6042 SST_IDP(e1, S_CONST);
6043 SST_DTYPEP(e1, DT_INT);
6044 SST_CVALP(e1, i);
6045 SST_ASTP(e1, mk_cval1(i, DT_INT));
6046 SST_SHAPEP(e1, 0);
6047 }
6048
6049 t_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
6050 t_aclp->id = AC_EXPR;
6051 t_aclp->repeatc = t_aclp->size = 0;
6052 t_aclp->next = NULL;
6053 t_aclp->subc = NULL;
6054 t_aclp->u1.stkp = e1;
6055
6056 DTC_ACL(pos) = t_aclp;
6057 continue;
6058 }
6059 }
6060 if (*kwd == '*') {
6061 continue;
6062 }
6063
6064 if (DTC_ACL(pos) == NULL) {
6065 char print[22];
6066 if (kwd_len > 21)
6067 kwd_len = 21;
6068 strncpy(print, kwd, kwd_len);
6069 print[kwd_len] = '\0';
6070 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
6071 "No default initialization in structure constructor- member",
6072 print);
6073
6074 return kwd_present;
6075 }
6076 }
6077
6078 return kwd_present;
6079
6080ill_keyword:
6081 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
6082 "Invalid component initialization in structure constructor", CNULL);
6083 return kwd_present;
6084}
6085
6086/* Put in_aclp in a form similar its datatype.
6087 * Also check the default init value here.
6088 */
6089static ACL *
6090get_exttype_struct_constructor(ACL *in_aclp, DTYPE dtype, ACL **prev_aclp)
6091{
6092 int member_dtype, field_dtype;
6093 int member_sptr;
6094 int ptr_sptr = 0, thissptr, myparent;
6095 ACL *aclp, *head_aclp, *curr_aclp;
6096 SST *stkp;
6097 int ast, possible_ext = 1;
6098
6099 aclp = in_aclp;
6100 head_aclp = in_aclp;
6101 curr_aclp = NULL;
6102
6103#if DEBUG
6104 if (DBGBIT(3, 64))
6105 printacl("get_exttype_struct_constructor", aclp, gbl.dbgfil);
6106#endif
6107
6108 member_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
6109 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
6110 if (member_sptr == 0) {
6111 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, "Use of derived type name before definition:",
6112 SYMNAME(DTY(dtype + 3)));
6113 return in_aclp;
6114 }
6115 for (; member_sptr != NOSYM && aclp != NULL;
6116 member_sptr = SYMLKG(member_sptr)) {
6117 if (no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_sptr))) {
6118 possible_ext = 0;
6119 continue;
6120 }
6121 if (is_tbp_or_final(member_sptr)) {
6122 possible_ext = 0;
6123 continue; /* skip tbp */
6124 }
6125
6126 if (POINTERG(member_sptr))
6127 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
6128 if (ptr_sptr &&
6129 (member_sptr == MIDNUMG(ptr_sptr) || member_sptr == PTROFFG(ptr_sptr) ||
6130 member_sptr == SDSCG(ptr_sptr) ||
6131 (CLASSG(member_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)))) {
6132 /* skip pointer related members */
6133 possible_ext = 0;
6134 continue;
6135 }
6136 ptr_sptr =
6137 USELENG(member_sptr) || POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr)
6138 ? member_sptr
6139 : 0;
6140 thissptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
6141 myparent = PARENTG(thissptr);
6142 member_dtype = DTYPEG(member_sptr);
6143 field_dtype = member_dtype;
6144 if (possible_ext) {
6145 switch (aclp->id) {
6146 case AC_AST:
6147 ast = aclp->u1.ast;
6148 field_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
6149 break;
6150 case AC_EXPR:
6151 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
6152 field_dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
6153 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(stkp) == S_LVALUE ||
6154 (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR && A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(stkp)) == A_ID)) {
6155 SPTR sptr;
6156 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
6157 sptr = SST_SYMG(stkp);
6158 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR &&
6159 A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(stkp)) == A_ID) {
6160 sptr = A_SPTRG(SST_ASTG(stkp));
6161 } else {
6162 sptr = SST_LSYMG(stkp);
6163 }
6164 if (DESCARRAYG(sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)) {
6165 field_dtype = DDTG(field_dtype);
6166 }
6167 if (SCG(member_sptr) == SC_BASED &&
6168 (SCG(sptr) == SC_BASED || TARGETG(sptr) ||
6169 (SCG(sptr) == SC_CMBLK && POINTERG(sptr) &&
6170 !F90POINTERG(sptr)))) {
6171 field_dtype = DDTG(field_dtype);
6172 }
6173 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR) {
6174 field_dtype = 0;
6175 }
6176 break;
6177 case AC_ACONST:
6178 case AC_SCONST:
6179 field_dtype = aclp->dtype;
6180 break;
6181 default:
6182 field_dtype = 0;
6183 break;
6184 }
6185 }
6186
6187 if (myparent && myparent == PARENTG(member_sptr) && possible_ext &&
6188 DTY(member_dtype) == TY_DERIVED &&
6189 !no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_dtype))) {
6190 if (!cmpat_dtype_with_size(field_dtype, member_dtype)) {
6191 head_aclp = GET_ACL(15);
6192 head_aclp->id = AC_SCONST;
6193 head_aclp->dtype = DDTG(member_dtype);
6194 head_aclp->next = NULL;
6195 *prev_aclp = aclp;
6196 head_aclp->subc = get_exttype_struct_constructor(
6197 aclp, DDTG(DTYPEG(member_sptr)), prev_aclp);
6198 if (*prev_aclp) {
6199 aclp = (*prev_aclp)->next;
6200 (*prev_aclp)->next = NULL;
6201 *prev_aclp = aclp;
6202 }
6203 curr_aclp = head_aclp;
6204 head_aclp->next = NULL;
6205 } else {
6206 *prev_aclp = aclp;
6207 if (curr_aclp)
6208 curr_aclp->next = aclp;
6209 curr_aclp = aclp;
6210 aclp = aclp->next;
6211 }
6212 } else {
6213 *prev_aclp = aclp;
6214 if (curr_aclp)
6215 curr_aclp->next = aclp;
6216 curr_aclp = aclp;
6217 aclp = aclp->next;
6218 }
6219
6220 possible_ext = 0;
6221 }
6222 return head_aclp;
6223}
6224
6225void
6226chk_struct_constructor(ACL *in_aclp)
6227{
6228 DTYPE dtype, member_dtype, field_dtype;
6229 int field_rank, member_rank;
6230 int member_sptr, memnum, cnt;
6231 int ptr_sptr = 0;
6232 ACL *aclp, *prev_aclp;
6233 SST *stkp;
6234 int ast, shape;
6235 int is_extend = 0;
6236 char *keyword;
6237
6238 aclp = in_aclp;
6239#if DEBUG
6240 if (DBGBIT(3, 64))
6241 printacl("chk_struct_constructor", aclp, gbl.dbgfil);
6242#endif
6243 assert(aclp->id == AC_SCONST, "bad id in chk_struct_constructor", aclp->id,
6244 3);
6245
6246 dtype = aclp->dtype;
6247 aclp = aclp->subc; /* go down to member list */
6248 member_sptr = DTY(dtype + 1);
6249 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
6250 if (member_sptr == 0) {
6251 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, "Use of derived type name before definition:",
6252 SYMNAME(DTY(dtype + 3)));
6253 return;
6254 }
6255 keyword = make_structkwd_str(dtype, &memnum, &is_extend);
6256 if (get_keyword_components(in_aclp, memnum, keyword, dtype, is_extend)) {
6257 ;
6258 }
6259 FREE(keyword);
6260 if (is_extend) {
6261 cnt = set_exttype_list(in_aclp->subc);
6262 }
6263
6264 cnt = 0;
6265 prev_aclp = NULL;
6266 for (; member_sptr != NOSYM; member_sptr = SYMLKG(member_sptr)) {
6267 if (POINTERG(member_sptr))
6268 ptr_sptr = member_sptr;
6269 if (no_data_components(DTYPEG(member_sptr)))
6270 continue;
6271 if (is_tbp_or_final(member_sptr))
6272 continue; /* skip tbp */
6273 if (ptr_sptr &&
6274 (member_sptr == MIDNUMG(ptr_sptr) || member_sptr == PTROFFG(ptr_sptr) ||
6275 member_sptr == SDSCG(ptr_sptr) ||
6276 (CLASSG(member_sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)))) {
6277 continue; /* skip pointer-related members */
6278 }
6279 ptr_sptr =
6280 USELENG(member_sptr) || POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr)
6281 ? member_sptr
6282 : 0;
6283
6284 aclp = DTC_ACL(cnt);
6285 if (aclp == NULL) {
6286 aclp = get_struct_default_init(member_sptr);
6287 }
6288 if (aclp)
6289 aclp->next = NULL;
6290 else
6291 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
6292 "No default initialization in structure constructor- member",
6293 SYMNAME(member_sptr));
6294
6295 if (prev_aclp == NULL) {
6296 prev_aclp = aclp;
6297 in_aclp->subc = aclp;
6298 } else {
6299 prev_aclp->next = aclp;
6300 prev_aclp = aclp;
6301 }
6302 member_dtype = DTYPEG(member_sptr);
6303 member_rank = rank_of(member_dtype);
6304
6305 ast = 0;
6306 switch (aclp->id) {
6307 case AC_AST:
6308 ast = aclp->u1.ast;
6309 field_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
6310 shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
6311 field_rank = (shape == 0) ? 0 : SHD_NDIM(shape);
6312 if ((POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr))) {
6313 if (aclp->dtype == DT_PTR) {
6314 int tdtype = aclp->ptrdtype;
6315 if (DTY(tdtype) == TY_PTR) {
6316 field_dtype = DTY(tdtype + 1);
6317 }
6318 }
6319 }
6320 break;
6321 case AC_EXPR:
6322 stkp = aclp->u1.stkp;
6323 field_dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stkp);
6324 if (field_dtype)
6325 field_rank = rank_of(field_dtype);
6326 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(stkp) == S_LVALUE ||
6327 (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR && A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(stkp)) == A_ID)) {
6328 int newast, sptr;
6329 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
6330 sptr = SST_SYMG(stkp);
6331 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR && A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(stkp)) == A_ID) {
6332 sptr = A_SPTRG(SST_ASTG(stkp));
6333 } else {
6334 sptr = SST_LSYMG(stkp);
6335 }
6336 if (DESCARRAYG(sptr) && DESCARRAYG(member_sptr)) {
6337 field_dtype = DDTG(field_dtype);
6338 member_dtype = DDTG(member_dtype);
6339 }
6340 if (SCG(member_sptr) == SC_BASED &&
6341 (SCG(sptr) == SC_BASED || TARGETG(sptr) ||
6342 (SCG(sptr) == SC_CMBLK && POINTERG(sptr) && !F90POINTERG(sptr)))) {
6343 /* add ACLs for pointer/offset/descriptor */
6344 ACL *naclp;
6345 SST *sp;
6346 int sdsc, ptroff, midnum;
6347 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
6348 if (ast) {
6349 shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
6350 field_rank = (shape == 0) ? 0 : SHD_NDIM(shape);
6351 }
6352 field_dtype = DDTG(field_dtype);
6353 member_dtype = DDTG(member_dtype);
6354 if ((TARGETG(sptr) || POINTERG(sptr)) && SDSCG(sptr) == 0 &&
6355 !F90POINTERG(sptr)) {
6356 get_static_descriptor(sptr);
6357 if (POINTERG(sptr) || (ALLOCATTRG(sptr) && TARGETG(sptr))) {
6358 get_all_descriptors(sptr);
6359 }
6360 }
6361 sdsc = SDSCG(sptr);
6362 if (sdsc && SDSCG(member_sptr) &&
6363 STYPEG(SDSCG(member_sptr)) == ST_MEMBER) {
6364
6365 sp = (SST *)getitem(ACL_AREA, sizeof(SST));
6366 if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
6367 SST_IDP(sp, S_IDENT);
6368 SST_SYMP(sp, sdsc);
6369 } else {
6370 SST_IDP(sp, S_LVALUE);
6371 SST_SYMP(sp, SST_SYMG(stkp));
6372 SST_LSYMP(sp, sdsc);
6373 newast = check_member(ast, mk_id(sdsc));
6374 SST_ASTP(sp, newast);
6375 SST_SHAPEP(sp, A_SHAPEG(newast));
6376 }
6377 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(sdsc));
6378 naclp = GET_ACL(ACL_AREA);
6379 naclp->id = AC_EXPR;
6380 naclp->repeatc = naclp->size = 0;
6381 naclp->next = prev_aclp->next;
6382 naclp->subc = NULL;
6383 naclp->u1.stkp = sp;
6384 prev_aclp->next = naclp;
6385 prev_aclp = naclp;
6386
6387 sp = (SST *)getitem(ACL_AREA, sizeof(SST));
6388 ptroff = PTROFFG(sptr);
6389 if (ptroff == 0) {
6390 SST_IDP(sp, S_CONST);
6391 SST_SYMP(sp, stb.i0);
6392 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(stb.i0));
6393 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
6394 SST_IDP(sp, S_IDENT);
6395 SST_SYMP(sp, ptroff);
6396 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(ptroff));
6397 } else {
6398 SST_IDP(sp, S_LVALUE);
6399 SST_SYMP(sp, SST_SYMG(stkp));
6400 SST_LSYMP(sp, ptroff);
6401 newast = check_member(ast, mk_id(ptroff));
6402 SST_ASTP(sp, newast);
6403 SST_SHAPEP(sp, A_SHAPEG(newast));
6404 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(ptroff));
6405 }
6406 naclp = GET_ACL(ACL_AREA);
6407 naclp->id = AC_EXPR;
6408 naclp->repeatc = naclp->size = 0;
6409 naclp->next = prev_aclp->next;
6410 naclp->subc = NULL;
6411 naclp->u1.stkp = sp;
6412 prev_aclp->next = naclp;
6413 prev_aclp = naclp;
6414
6415 sp = (SST *)getitem(ACL_AREA, sizeof(SST));
6416 midnum = MIDNUMG(sptr);
6417 if (midnum == 0) {
6418 SST_IDP(sp, S_CONST);
6419 SST_SYMP(sp, stb.i0);
6420 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(stb.i0));
6421 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_IDENT) {
6422 SST_IDP(sp, S_IDENT);
6423 SST_SYMP(sp, midnum);
6424 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(midnum));
6425 } else {
6426 SST_IDP(sp, S_LVALUE);
6427 SST_SYMP(sp, SST_SYMG(stkp));
6428 SST_LSYMP(sp, midnum);
6429 newast = check_member(ast, mk_id(midnum));
6430 SST_ASTP(sp, newast);
6431 SST_SHAPEP(sp, A_SHAPEG(ast));
6432 SST_DTYPEP(sp, DTYPEG(midnum));
6433 }
6434 naclp = GET_ACL(ACL_AREA);
6435 naclp->id = AC_EXPR;
6436 naclp->repeatc = naclp->size = 0;
6437 naclp->next = prev_aclp->next;
6438 naclp->subc = NULL;
6439 naclp->u1.stkp = sp;
6440 prev_aclp->next = naclp;
6441 prev_aclp = naclp;
6442 }
6443 }
6444 } else if (SST_IDG(stkp) == S_EXPR) {
6445 /* handle call to NULL() */
6446 ast = SST_ASTG(stkp);
6447 field_dtype = 0;
6448 field_rank = 0;
6449 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_NULL) {
6450 field_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
6451 if (POINTERG(member_sptr) || ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr)) {
6452 member_dtype = DT_PTR;
6453 }
6454 }
6455 }
6456 break;
6457 case AC_ACONST:
6458 case AC_SCONST:
6459 field_dtype = aclp->dtype;
6460 field_rank = rank_of(field_dtype);
6461 break;
6462 default:
6463 field_dtype = 0;
6464 field_rank = 0;
6465 break;
6466 }
6467 if ((field_rank && member_rank && field_rank != member_rank) ||
6468 (field_dtype && !cmpat_dtype_with_size(field_dtype, member_dtype))) {
6469 if (DTY(DTYPEG(member_sptr)) != TY_PTR &&
6470 DTY(DTY(DTYPEG(member_sptr) + 1)) != TY_PROC)
6471 error(155, 2, gbl.lineno, "Mismatched data type for member",
6472 SYMNAME(member_sptr));
6473 }
6474 if (is_illegal_expr_in_init(member_sptr, ast, aclp->dtype)) {
6475 error(457, 3, gbl.lineno, CNULL, CNULL);
6476 }
6477
6478 cnt++;
6479 }
6480 if (cnt > memnum)
6481 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
6482 "Too many elements in structure constructor- type",
6483 SYMNAME(DTY(dtype + 3)));
6484
6485 /* may want to set is_const flag in aclp if all members are constant */
6486}
6487
6488static bool
6489is_illegal_expr_in_init(SPTR member_sptr, int ast, DTYPE acl_dtype)
6490{
6491 if (!sem.dinit_data)
6492 return false;
6493 if (!POINTERG(member_sptr) && !ALLOCATTRG(member_sptr))
6494 return false;
6495 if (ast == 0)
6496 return true;
6497 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_NULL)
6498 return false;
6499 if (ast != astb.i0 || acl_dtype != DT_PTR ||
6500 DTY(ENCLDTYPEG(member_sptr)) != TY_DERIVED)
6501 return true;
6502 return false;
6503}
6504
6505int
6506init_derived_w_acl(int in_sptr, ACL *sconst)
6507{
6508 int sptr, dtype, tag;
6509
6510 if (in_sptr)
6511 sptr = in_sptr;
6512 else {
6513 dtype = sconst->dtype;
6514 tag = DTY(dtype + 3);
6515 sptr = get_next_sym(SYMNAME(tag), "d");
6516 STYPEP(sptr, ST_VAR);
6517 DCLDP(sptr, 1);
6518 SCP(sptr, sem.sc);
6519 DTYPEP(sptr, dtype);
6520 add_alloc_mem_initialize(sptr);
6521 }
6522
6523 constructf90(sptr, sconst);
6524
6525 return sptr;
6526}
6527
6528/*
6529 * keep track of an initialization ast tree.
6530 * this is a list of ast nodes linked by A_RIGHT fields;
6531 * the A_TYPE is A_INIT
6532 * the A_LEFT field points to the initialization value.
6533 * the A_SPTR field, if set, points to the variable or member symbol.
6534 */
6535
6536typedef struct {
6537 int head, tail;
6538} ASTLIST;
6539
6540static void
6541append_init_list(ASTLIST *target, ASTLIST *src)
6542{
6543 if (target->head == 0) {
6544 *target = *src;
6545 } else {
6546 A_RIGHTP(target->tail, src->head);
6547 target->tail = src->tail;
6548 }
6549}
6550
6551static void
6552add_init(ASTLIST *list, int left, DTYPE dtype, int sptr)
6553{
6554 int ast;
6555 ast = mk_init(left, dtype);
6556 A_SPTRP(ast, sptr);
6557 if (list->head == 0) {
6558 list->head = ast;
6559 } else {
6560 A_RIGHTP(list->tail, ast);
6561 }
6562 list->tail = ast;
6563} /* add_init */
6564
6565static LOGICAL out_of_elements_message;
6566
6567/*
6568 * Evaluate a constant expression. Code borrowed from dinit_eval() and
6569 * changed to allow expression types other than integer.
6570 * Part of the fix for FS2281.
6571 */
6572static INT
6573const_eval(int ast)
6574{
6575 DOSTACK *p;
6576 int sptr;
6577 INT val;
6578 int lop, rop;
6579 INT term;
6580 INT lv, rv;
6581 int count;
6582 int sign;
6583
6584 if (ast == 0)
6585 return 1L;
6586 if (A_ALIASG(ast)) {
6587 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
6588 goto eval_cnst;
6589 }
6590 switch (A_TYPEG(ast) /* opc */) {
6591 case A_ID:
6592 if (!DT_ISINT(A_DTYPEG(ast)))
6593 goto cnst_err;
6594 if (A_ALIASG(ast)) {
6595 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
6596 goto eval_cnst;
6597 }
6598 /* see if this ident is an active do index variable: */
6599 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
6600 for (p = sem.dostack; p < sem.top; p++)
6601 if (p->sptr == sptr)
6602 return p->currval;
6603 /* else - illegal use of variable: */
6604 error(64, 3, gbl.lineno, SYMNAME(sptr), CNULL);
6605 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
6606 return 1L;
6607
6608 case A_CNST:
6609 goto eval_cnst;
6610
6611 case A_UNOP:
6612 val = const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast));
6613 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == OP_SUB)
6614 val = negate_const(val, A_DTYPEG(ast));
6615 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == OP_LNOT)
6616 val = ~(val);
6617 return val;
6618
6619 case A_BINOP:
6620 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6621 case OP_ADD:
6622 case OP_SUB:
6623 case OP_MUL:
6624 case OP_DIV:
6625 return const_fold(A_OPTYPEG(ast), const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast)),
6626 const_eval((int)A_ROPG(ast)), A_DTYPEG(ast));
6627
6628 case OP_EQ:
6629 case OP_GE:
6630 case OP_GT:
6631 case OP_LE:
6632 case OP_LT:
6633 case OP_NE:
6634 val = const_fold(OP_CMP, const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast)),
6635 const_eval((int)A_ROPG(ast)), A_DTYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)));
6636 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6637 case OP_EQ:
6638 val = (val == 0);
6639 break;
6640 case OP_GE:
6641 val = (val >= 0);
6642 break;
6643 case OP_GT:
6644 val = (val > 0);
6645 break;
6646 case OP_LE:
6647 val = (val <= 0);
6648 break;
6649 case OP_LT:
6650 val = (val < 0);
6651 break;
6652 case OP_NE:
6653 val = (val != 0);
6654 break;
6655 }
6656 val = val ? SCFTN_TRUE : SCFTN_FALSE;
6657 return val;
6658
6659 case OP_LEQV:
6660 case OP_LNEQV:
6661 case OP_LOR:
6662 case OP_LAND:
6663 lv = const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast));
6664 rv = const_eval((int)A_ROPG(ast));
6665 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6666 case OP_LEQV:
6667 val = (lv == rv) ? SCFTN_TRUE : SCFTN_FALSE;
6668 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
6669 case OP_LNEQV:
6670 val = (lv == rv) ? SCFTN_FALSE : SCFTN_TRUE;
6671 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
6672 case OP_LOR:
6673 val = (lv == SCFTN_TRUE || rv == SCFTN_TRUE) ? SCFTN_TRUE : SCFTN_FALSE;
6674 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
6675 case OP_LAND:
6676 val = (lv == SCFTN_TRUE && rv == SCFTN_TRUE) ? SCFTN_TRUE : SCFTN_FALSE;
6677 }
6678 return val;
6679 case OP_XTOI:
6680 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
6681 rop = A_ROPG(ast);
6682 if (A_DTYPEG(rop) == DT_INT8) {
6683 term = stb.k1;
6684 if (A_DTYPEG(lop) != DT_INT8)
6685 term = cngcon(term, DT_INT8, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6686 val = term;
6687 lv = const_eval(lop);
6688 rv = const_eval(rop);
6689 count = get_int_cval(rv);
6690 count = (count < 0) ? -count : count;
6691 while (count--)
6692 val = const_fold(OP_MUL, val, lv, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6693 if (get_int_cval(rv) < 0) {
6694 /* exponentiation to a negative power */
6695 val = const_fold(OP_DIV, term, val, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6696 }
6697 } else if (DT_ISINT(A_DTYPEG(rop))) {
6698 term = 1;
6699 if (A_DTYPEG(lop) != DT_INT4)
6700 term = cngcon(term, DT_INT4, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6701 val = term;
6702 lv = const_eval(lop);
6703 rv = const_eval(rop);
6704 if (A_DTYPEG(rop) != DT_INT4)
6705 rv = cngcon(rv, A_DTYPEG(rop), DT_INT4);
6706 if (rv >= 0)
6707 sign = 0;
6708 else {
6709 rv = -rv;
6710 sign = 1;
6711 }
6712 while (rv--)
6713 val = const_fold(OP_MUL, val, lv, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6714 if (sign) {
6715 /* exponentiation to a negative power */
6716 val = const_fold(OP_DIV, term, val, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6717 }
6718 } else {
6719 lv = const_eval(lop);
6720 rv = const_eval(rop);
6721 val = const_fold(OP_XTOI, lv, rv, A_DTYPEG(lop));
6722 }
6723 return val;
6724 }
6725 break;
6726
6727 case A_CONV:
6728 val = const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast));
6729 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)), A_DTYPEG(ast));
6730
6731 case A_PAREN:
6732 return const_eval((int)A_LOPG(ast));
6733 case A_INTR:
6734 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6735 case I_NULL:
6736 return 0;
6737 case I_NCHAR:
6738
6739 /* kanji/international character sets */
6740
6741 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6742 val = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6743 if (A_TYPEG(val) == A_CNST) {
6744 int con1, con2, bytes;
6745 con1 = A_SPTRG(val);
6746 con2 = CONVAL1G(con1);
6747 count = size_of(DTYPEG(con2));
6748 val = kanji_char((unsigned char *)stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(con2), count,
6749 &bytes);
6750 return val;
6751 }
6752 break;
6753 case I_ICHAR:
6754 case I_IACHAR:
6755 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6756 val = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6757 if (A_TYPEG(val) == A_CNST) {
6758 val = A_SPTRG(val);
6759 count = size_of(DTYPEG(val));
6760 if (count == 1) {
6761 val = stb.n_base[CONVAL1G(val)] & 0xff;
6762 return val;
6763 }
6764 }
6765 break;
6766 case I_INT:
6767 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6768 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6769 val = const_eval(ast);
6770 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(ast), DT_INT);
6771 case I_INT8:
6772 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6773 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6774 val = const_eval(ast);
6775 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(ast), DT_INT8);
6776 case I_INT4:
6777 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6778 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6779 val = const_eval(ast);
6780 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(ast), DT_INT4);
6781 case I_INT2:
6782 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6783 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6784 val = const_eval(ast);
6785 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(ast), DT_SINT);
6786 case I_INT1:
6787 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6788 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6789 val = const_eval(ast);
6790 return cngcon(val, A_DTYPEG(ast), DT_BINT);
6791 case I_SIZE: {
6792 int sz;
6793 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6794 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6795 ast = ADD_NUMELM(A_DTYPEG(ast));
6796 sz = get_const_from_ast(ast);
6797 if (XBIT(68, 0x1) && A_ALIASG(ast) && !DT_ISWORD(A_DTYPEG(ast))) {
6798 sz = get_int_cval(sz);
6799 }
6800 return sz;
6801 }
6802 case I_LBOUND: {
6803 int lwb;
6804 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6805 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6806 ast = ADD_LWAST(A_DTYPEG(ast), val - 1);
6807 lwb = get_const_from_ast(ast);
6808 if (XBIT(68, 0x1) && A_ALIASG(ast) && !DT_ISWORD(A_DTYPEG(ast))) {
6809 lwb = get_int_cval(lwb);
6810 }
6811 return lwb;
6812 }
6813 case I_UBOUND: {
6814 int upb;
6815 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6816 ast = ARGT_ARG(val, 0);
6817 ast = ADD_UPAST(A_DTYPEG(ast), val - 1);
6818 upb = get_const_from_ast(ast);
6819 if (XBIT(68, 0x1) && A_ALIASG(ast) && !DT_ISWORD(A_DTYPEG(ast))) {
6820 upb = get_int_cval(upb);
6821 }
6822 return upb;
6823 }
6824 case I_MAX0: {
6825 int max, i, tmp;
6826 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6827 max = get_const_from_ast(ARGT_ARG(val, 0));
6828 for (i = 1; i < A_ARGCNTG(ast); ++i) {
6829 tmp = get_const_from_ast(ARGT_ARG(val, i));
6830 if (tmp > max) {
6831 max = tmp;
6832 }
6833 }
6834 return max;
6835 }
6836 case I_MIN0: {
6837 int min, i, tmp;
6838 val = A_ARGSG(ast);
6839 min = get_const_from_ast(ARGT_ARG(val, 0));
6840 for (i = 1; i < A_ARGCNTG(ast); ++i) {
6841 tmp = get_const_from_ast(ARGT_ARG(val, i));
6842 if (tmp < min) {
6843 min = tmp;
6844 }
6845 }
6846 return min;
6847 }
6848 }
6849 break;
6850 default:
6851 break;
6852 }
6853cnst_err:
6854 errsev(69);
6855 sem.dinit_error = TRUE;
6856 A_DTYPEP(ast, DT_INT);
6857 return 1L;
6858
6859eval_cnst:
6860 val = A_SPTRG(ast);
6861 if (DT_ISWORD(DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast))))
6862 val = CONVAL2G(val);
6863 return val;
6864}
6865
6866/*
6867 * make sure 'ast' is a constant of the proper datatype
6868 */
6869static int
6870dinit_getval(int ast, DTYPE dtype)
6871{
6872 DTYPE adtype;
6873 int aval, val;
