8784
8785#define GET_DBLE(x, y) \
8786 x[0] = CONVAL1G(y); \
8787 x[1] = CONVAL2G(y)
8788#define GET_QUAD(x, y) \
8789 x[0] = CONVAL1G(y); \
8790 x[1] = CONVAL2G(y); \
8791 x[2] = CONVAL3G(y); \
8792 x[3] = CONVAL4G(y);
8793#define GETVALI64(x, b) \
8794 x[0] = CONVAL1G(b); \
8795 x[1] = CONVAL2G(b);
8796
8797static ACL *
8798eval_abs(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
8799{
8800 ACL *rslt;
8801 ACL *wrkarg;
8802 INT con1, res[4], num1[4], num2[4];
8803 DTYPE rsltdtype = dtype;
8804 float f1, f2;
8805
8806 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
8807 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
8808 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
8809 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) {
8810 case TY_SINT:
8811 case TY_BINT:
8812 case TY_INT:
8813 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8814 con1 = con1 >= 0 ? con1 : -con1;
8815 break;
8816 case TY_INT8:
8817 con1 = wrkarg->conval; /* sptr */
8818 GETVALI64(num1, con1);
8819 GETVALI64(num2, stb.k0);
8820 if (cmp64(num1, num2) == -1) {
8821 neg64(num1, res);
8822 con1 = getcon(res, DT_INT8);
8823 }
8824 break;
8825 case TY_REAL:
8826 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8827 res[0] = 0;
8828 xfabsv(con1, &res[1]);
8829 con1 = res[1];
8830 break;
8831 case TY_DBLE:
8832 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8833 GET_DBLE(num1, con1);
8834 xdabsv(num1, res);
8835 con1 = getcon(res, dtype);
8836 break;
8837#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
8838 case TY_QUAD:
8839 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8840 GET_QUAD(num1, con1);
8841 xqabsv(num1, res);
8842 con1 = getcon(res, dtype);
8843 break;
8844#endif
8845 case TY_CMPLX:
8846 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8847 f1 = CONVAL1G(con1);
8848 f2 = CONVAL2G(con1);
8849 f1 = f1 * f1;
8850 f2 = f2 * f2;
8851 f2 = f1 + f2;
8852 xfsqrt(f2, &con1);
8853 dtype = rsltdtype = DT_REAL;
8854 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
8855 break;
8856 case TY_DCMPLX:
8857 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8858 rsltdtype = DT_REAL;
8859 break;
8860 default:
8861 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
8862 break;
8863 }
8864
8865 wrkarg->conval = cngcon(con1, wrkarg->dtype, rsltdtype);
8866 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
8867 }
8868 return rslt;
8869}
8870
8871/* scale(X, I) = X * 2 **I, X is real type, I is an integer */
8872static ACL *
8873eval_scale(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
8874{
8875 ACL *rslt;
8876 ACL *arg2;
8877 INT i, conval1, conval2, conval;
8878 DBLINT64 inum1, inum2;
8879 INT e;
8880#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
8881 INT qnum1[4], qnum2[4];
8882 QUAD qconval;
8883#endif
8884 DBLE dconval;
8885
8886 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
8887 conval1 = arg->conval;
8888 arg2 = arg->next;
8889
8890 if (arg2->dtype == DT_INT8)
8891 error(205, ERR_Warning, gbl.lineno, SYMNAME(arg2->conval),
8892 "- Illegal specification of scale factor");
8893
8894 i = arg2->dtype == DT_INT8 ? CONVAL2G(arg2->conval) : arg2->conval;
8895
8896 switch (size_of(arg->dtype)) {
8897 case 4:
8898 /* 8-bit exponent (127) to get an exponent value in the
8899 * range -126 .. +127 */
8900 e = 127 + i;
8901 if (e < 0)
8902 e = 0;
8903 else if (e > 255)
8904 e = 255;
8905
8906 /* calculate decimal value from it's IEEE 754 form*/
8907 conval2 = e << 23;
8908 xfmul(conval1, conval2, &conval);
8909 rslt->conval = conval;
8910 break;
8911
8912 case 8:
8913 e = 1023 + i;
8914 if (e < 0)
8915 e = 0;
8916 else if (e > 2047)
8917 e = 2047;
8918
8919 inum1[0] = CONVAL1G(conval1);
8920 inum1[1] = CONVAL2G(conval1);
8921
8922 inum2[0] = e << 20;
8923 inum2[1] = 0;
8924 xdmul(inum1, inum2, dconval);
8925 rslt->conval = getcon(dconval, DT_REAL8);
8926 break;
8927
8928#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
8929 case 16:
8930 e = 16383 + i;
8931 if (e < 0)
8932 e = 0;
8933 else if (e > 32767)
8934 e = 32767;
8935
8936 qnum1[0] = CONVAL1G(conval1);
8937 qnum1[1] = CONVAL2G(conval1);
8938 qnum1[2] = CONVAL3G(conval1);
8939 qnum1[3] = CONVAL4G(conval1);
8940
8941 qnum2[0] = e << 16;
8942 qnum2[1] = 0;
8943 qnum2[2] = 0;
8944 qnum2[3] = 0;
8945 xqmul(qnum1, qnum2, qconval);
8946 rslt->conval = getcon(qconval, DT_QUAD);
8947 break;
8948#endif
8949 }
8950
8951 return rslt;
8952}
8953
8954static ACL *
8955eval_merge(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
8956{
8957 ACL *tsource = eval_init_expr_item(arg);
8958 ACL *fsource = eval_init_expr_item(arg->next);
8959 ACL *mask = eval_init_expr_item(arg->next->next);
8960 ACL *result = clone_init_const(tsource, TRUE);
8961 ACL *r = result;
8962 if (tsource->id == AC_ACONST)
8963 tsource = tsource->subc;
8964 if (fsource->id == AC_ACONST)
8965 fsource = fsource->subc;
8966 if (mask->id == AC_ACONST)
8967 mask = mask->subc;
8968 if (r->id == AC_ACONST)
8969 r = r->subc;
8970 for (; r != 0; r = r->next) {
8971 int cond = DT_ISWORD(mask->dtype) ? mask->conval : CONVAL2G(mask->conval);
8972 r->conval = cond ? tsource->conval : fsource->conval;
8973 r->dtype = dtype;
8974 tsource = tsource->next;
8975 fsource = fsource->next;
8976 mask = mask->next;
8977 }
8978 return result;
8979}
8980
8981/* Compare two constant ACLs. Return x > y or x < y depending on want_max.
8982 */
8983static bool
8984cmp_acl(DTYPE dtype, ACL *x, ACL *y, bool want_max, bool back)
8985{
8986 int cmp;
8987 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
8988 case TY_CHAR:
8989 cmp = strcmp(stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(x->conval),
8990 stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(y->conval));
8991 break;
8992 case TY_BINT:
8993 case TY_SINT:
8994 case TY_INT:
8995 if (x->conval == y->conval) {
8996 cmp = 0;
8997 } else if (x->conval > y->conval) {
8998 cmp = 1;
8999 } else {
9000 cmp = -1;
9001 }
9002 break;
9003 case TY_REAL:
9004 cmp = xfcmp(x->conval, y->conval);
9005 break;
9006 case TY_INT8:
9007 case TY_DBLE:
9008#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9009 case TY_QUAD:
9010#endif
9011 cmp = const_fold(OP_CMP, x->conval, y->conval, dtype);
9012 break;
9013 default:
9014 interr("cmp_acl: bad dtype", dtype, ERR_Severe);
9015 return false;
9016 }
9017 if (back) {
9018 return want_max ? cmp >= 0 : cmp <= 0;
9019 } else {
9020 return want_max ? cmp > 0 : cmp < 0;
9021 }
9022}
9023
9024/* An index into a Fortran array. ndims is in [1,MAXDIMS], index[] is the
9025 * index itself, extent[] is the extent in each dimension.
9026 * index[i] is in [1,extent[i]] for i in 1..ndims
9027 */
9028typedef struct {
9029 unsigned ndims;
9030 unsigned index[MAXDIMS + 1];
9031 unsigned extent[MAXDIMS + 1];
9032} INDEX;
9033
9034/* Increment an array index starting at the left and carrying to the right. */
9035static bool
9036incr_index(INDEX *index)
9037{
9038 unsigned d;
9039 for (d = 1; d <= index->ndims; ++d) {
9040 if (index->index[d] < index->extent[d]) {
9041 index->index[d] += 1;
9042 return true; /* no carry needed */
9043 }
9044 index->index[d] = 1;
9045 }
9046 return false;
9047}
9048
9049static unsigned
9050get_offset_without_dim(INDEX *index, unsigned dim)
9051{
9052 if (dim == 0) {
9053 return 0;
9054 } else {
9055 unsigned result = 0;
9056 unsigned d;
9057 for (d = index->ndims; d > 0; --d) {
9058 if (d != dim) {
9059 result *= index->extent[d];
9060 result += index->index[d] - 1;
9061 }
9062 }
9063 return result;
9064 }
9065}
9066
9067/* Create an array dtype from the extents in index, omitting dimension dim. */
9068static DTYPE
9069mk_dtype_without_dim(INDEX *index, unsigned dim, DTYPE elem_dtype)
9070{
9071 DTYPE array_dtype;
9072 unsigned i, j;
9073 for (i = 1, j = 0; i <= index->ndims; ++i) {
9074 if (i != dim) {
9075 sem.bounds[j].lowtype = S_CONST;
9076 sem.bounds[j].lowb = 1;
9077 sem.bounds[j].lwast = 0;
9078 sem.bounds[j].uptype = S_CONST;
9079 sem.bounds[j].upb = index->extent[i];
9080 sem.bounds[j].upast = mk_cval(index->extent[i], stb.user.dt_int);
9081 ++j;
9082 }
9083 }
9084 sem.arrdim.ndim = index->ndims - 1;
9085 sem.arrdim.ndefer = 0;
9086 array_dtype = mk_arrdsc();
9087 DTY(array_dtype + 1) = elem_dtype;
9088 return array_dtype;
9089}
9090
9091/* Get an ACL representing the smallest/largest value of this type. */
9092static ACL *
9093get_minmax_val(DTYPE dtype, bool want_max)
9094{
9095 int ast = want_max ? mk_smallest_val(dtype) : mk_largest_val(dtype);
9096 return eval_init_expr_item(construct_acl_from_ast(ast, dtype, 0));
9097}
9098
9099static ACL *
9100convert_acl_dtype(ACL *head, int oldtype, int newtype)
9101{
9102 DTYPE dtype;
9103 ACL *cur_lop;
9104 if (DTY(oldtype) == TY_DERIVED || DTY(oldtype) == TY_STRUCT ||
9105 DTY(oldtype) == TY_CHAR || DTY(oldtype) == TY_NCHAR ||
9106 DTY(oldtype) == TY_UNION) {
9107 return head;
9108 }
9109 dtype = DDTG(newtype);
9110
9111 /* make sure all are AC_CONST */
9112 for (cur_lop = head; cur_lop; cur_lop = cur_lop->next) {
9113 if (cur_lop->id != AC_CONST)
9114 return head;
9115 }
9116
9117 for (cur_lop = head; cur_lop; cur_lop = cur_lop->next) {
9118 if (cur_lop->dtype != dtype) {
9119 cur_lop->dtype = dtype;
9120 cur_lop->conval = cngcon(cur_lop->conval, DDTG(oldtype), DDTG(newtype));
9121 }
9122 }
9123 return head;
9124}
9125
9126/* Evaluate {min,max}{val,loc}{elems, dim, mask, back).
9127 * index describes the shape of the array; elem_dt the type of elems.
9128 */
9129static ACL *
9130do_eval_minval_or_maxval(INDEX *index, DTYPE elem_dt, DTYPE loc_dt, ACL *elems,
9131 unsigned dim, ACL *mask, bool back,
9132 AC_INTRINSIC intrin)
9133{
9134 unsigned ndims = index->ndims;
9135 unsigned i;
9136 ACL **vals;
9137 unsigned *locs;
9138 unsigned vals_size = 1;
9139 unsigned locs_size;
9140 bool want_max = intrin == AC_I_maxloc || intrin == AC_I_maxval;
9141 bool want_val = intrin == AC_I_minval || intrin == AC_I_maxval;
9142
9143 /* vals[vals_size] contains the result for {min,max}val()
9144 * locs[locs_size] contains the result for {min,max}loc() */
9145 if (dim == 0) {
9146 locs_size = ndims;
9147 } else {
9148 unsigned d;
9149 for (d = 1; d <= ndims; ++d) {
9150 if (d != dim)
9151 vals_size *= index->extent[d];
9152 }
9153 locs_size = vals_size;
9154 }
9155 NEW(vals, ACL *, vals_size);
9156 for (i = 0; i < vals_size; ++i) {
9157 vals[i] = get_minmax_val(elem_dt, want_max);
9158 }
9159
9160 NEW(locs, unsigned, locs_size);
9161 BZERO(locs, unsigned, locs_size);
9162
9163 { /* iterate over elements computing min/max into vals[] and locs[] */
9164 ACL *elem;
9165 for (elem = elems; elem != 0; elem = elem->next) {
9166 if (elem->dtype != elem_dt) {
9167 elem = convert_acl_dtype(elem, elem->dtype, elem_dt);
9168 }
9169
9170 if (mask->conval) {
9171 ACL *val = eval_init_expr_item(elem);
9172 unsigned offset = get_offset_without_dim(index, dim);
9173 ACL *prev_val = vals[offset];
9174 if (cmp_acl(elem_dt, val, prev_val, want_max, back)) {
9175 vals[offset] = val;
9176 if (dim == 0) {
9177 BCOPY(locs, &index->index[1], int, ndims);
9178 } else {
9179 locs[offset] = index->index[dim];
9180 }
9181 }
9182 }
9183 if (mask->next)
9184 mask = mask->next;
9185 incr_index(index);
9186 }
9187 }
9188
9189 { /* build result from vals[] or locs[] */
9190 ACL *result;
9191 ACL *subc = NULL; /* elements of result array */
9192 if (!want_val) {
9193 for (i = 0; i < locs_size; i++) {
9194 ACL *elem = GET_ACL(15);
9195 BZERO(elem, ACL, 1);
9196 elem->id = AC_CONST;
9197 elem->dtype = loc_dt;
9198 elem->is_const = true;
9199 elem->conval = locs[i];
9200 elem->u1.ast = mk_cval(locs[i], loc_dt);
9201 add_to_list(elem, &subc);
9202 }
9203 } else if (dim > 0) {
9204 for (i = 0; i < vals_size; i++) {
9205 add_to_list(vals[i], &subc);
9206 }
9207 } else {
9208 return vals[0]; /* minval/maxval with no dim has scalar result */
9209 }
9210
9211 result = GET_ACL(15);
9212 BZERO(result, ACL, 1);
9213 result->id = AC_ACONST;
9214 result->dtype =
9215 mk_dtype_without_dim(index, dim, want_val ? elem_dt : loc_dt);
9216 result->is_const = 1;
9217 result->subc = subc;
9218 return result;
9219 }
9220}
9221
9222static ACL *
9223eval_minval_or_maxval(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype, AC_INTRINSIC intrin)
9224{
9225 DTYPE elem_dt = array_element_dtype(dtype);
9226 DTYPE loc_dtype = DT_INT;
9227 ACL *array = eval_init_expr_item(arg);
9228 unsigned dim = 0; /* 0 means no DIM specified, otherwise in 1..ndims */
9229 ACL *mask = 0;
9230 INDEX index;
9231 unsigned d;
9232 ACL *arg2;
9233 bool back = FALSE;
9234
9235 while ((arg = arg->next)) {
9236 if (DT_ISLOG(arg->dtype)) { /* back */
9237 arg2 = eval_init_expr_item(arg);
9238 back = arg2->conval;
9239 } else if (DT_ISINT(arg->dtype)) { /* dim */
9240 arg2 = eval_init_expr_item(arg);
9241 dim = arg2->conval;
9242 assert(dim == arg2->conval, "DIM value must be an integer!", 0,
9243 ERR_Fatal);
9244 } else { //(DT_ISLOG_ARR(arg->dtype))
9245 mask = eval_init_expr_item(arg);
9246 if (mask != 0 && mask->id == AC_ACONST)
9247 mask = mask->subc;
9248 }
9249 }
9250
9251 if (mask == 0) {
9252 /* mask defaults to .true. */
9253 mask = GET_ACL(15);
9254 BZERO(mask, ACL, 1);
9255 mask->id = AC_CONST;
9256 mask->dtype = DT_LOG;
9257 mask->is_const = 1;
9258 mask->conval = 1;
9259 mask->u1.ast = mk_cval(gbl.ftn_true, DT_LOG);
9260 }
9261 /* index contains the rank and extents of the array dtype */
9262 BZERO(&index, INDEX, 1);
9263 index.ndims = ADD_NUMDIM(dtype);
9264 for (d = 1; d <= index.ndims; ++d) {
9265 int lwbd = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(ADD_LWAST(dtype, d - 1)));
9266 int upbd = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(ADD_UPAST(dtype, d - 1)));
9267 int extent = upbd - lwbd + 1;
9268 index.extent[d] = extent;
9269 index.index[d] = 1;
9270 }
9271 return do_eval_minval_or_maxval(&index, elem_dt, loc_dtype, array->subc, dim,
9272 mask, back, intrin);
9273}
9274
9275/* evaluate min or max, depending on want_max flag */
9276static ACL *
9277eval_min_or_max(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype, LOGICAL want_max)
9278{
9279 ACL *rslt;
9280 ACL *wrkarg1, *head, *c;
9281 ACL **arglist;
9282 int nargs;
9283 int nelems = 0;
9284 int i, j, repeatc1, repeatc2;
9285 ADSC *adsc;
9286 ACL *root = NULL;
9287
9288 /* at this point we only know argument types but we don't know the
9289 * lhs of min(...) type
9290 * Therefore, create a result based on the result of args.
9291 */
9292
9293 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9294 BZERO(rslt, ACL, 1);
9295 rslt->dtype = arg->dtype;
9296
9297 for (wrkarg1 = arg, nargs = 0; wrkarg1; wrkarg1 = wrkarg1->next, nargs++)
9298 ;
9299
9300 NEW(arglist, ACL *, nargs);
9301 for (i = 0, wrkarg1 = arg; i < nargs; i++, wrkarg1 = wrkarg1->next) {
9302 head = arglist[i] = eval_init_expr(wrkarg1);
9303 if (DTY(head->dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
9304 int num;
9305 adsc = AD_DPTR(head->dtype);
9306 num = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(AD_NUMELM(adsc)));
9307 if (nelems == 0) {
9308 nelems = num;
9309 } else if (nelems != num) {
9310 /* error */
9311 }
9312 rslt->id = AC_ACONST;
9313 rslt->dtype = head->dtype;
9314 }
9315 }
9316 if (nelems == 0) {
9317 nelems = 1; /* scalar only */
9318 c = rslt;
9319 c->id = AC_CONST;
9320 c->repeatc = astb.bnd.one;
9321 c->next = NULL;
9322 add_to_list(c, &root);
9323 } else {
9324 for (j = 0; j < nelems; j++) {
9325 c = GET_ACL(15);
9326 c->id = AC_CONST;
9327 c->repeatc = astb.bnd.one;
9328 c->next = NULL;
9329 add_to_list(c, &root);
9330 }
9331 rslt->subc = root;
9332 rslt->repeatc = 0;
9333 }
9334
9335 wrkarg1 = arglist[0];
9336 for (i = 1; i < nargs; i++) {
9337 ACL *wrkarg2 = arglist[i];
9338 if (wrkarg2->id == AC_ACONST) {
9339 wrkarg2 = wrkarg2->subc;
9340 if (wrkarg2->repeatc)
9341 repeatc2 = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(wrkarg2->repeatc));
9342 else
9343 repeatc2 = 1;
9344 } else {
9345 repeatc2 = nelems;
9346 }
9347 if (wrkarg1->id == AC_ACONST) {
9348 wrkarg1 = wrkarg1->subc;
9349 if (wrkarg1->repeatc)
9350 repeatc1 = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(wrkarg1->repeatc));
9351 else
9352 repeatc1 = 1;
9353 } else {
9354 repeatc1 = nelems;
9355 }
9356
9357 c = root;
9358 for (j = 0; j < nelems; j++) {
9359 if (cmp_acl(dtype, wrkarg2, wrkarg1, want_max, FALSE)) {
9360 c->u1 = wrkarg2->u1;
9361 c->conval = wrkarg2->conval;
9362 c->dtype = wrkarg2->dtype;
9363 } else if (root != wrkarg1) {
9364 c->u1 = wrkarg1->u1;
9365 c->conval = wrkarg1->conval;
9366 c->dtype = wrkarg1->dtype;
9367 }
9368 if (--repeatc2 <= 0) {
9369 wrkarg2 = wrkarg2->next;
9370 if (wrkarg2 && wrkarg2->repeatc)
9371 repeatc2 = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(wrkarg2->repeatc));
9372 else
9373 repeatc2 = 1;
9374 }
9375 c = c->next;
9376 if (wrkarg1 == root) { /* result becomes argument on next
9377 * iteration of outer loop
9378 */
9379 wrkarg1 = c;
9380 repeatc1 = 1;
9381 } else if (--repeatc1 <= 0) {
9382 wrkarg1 = wrkarg1->next;
9383 if (wrkarg2 && wrkarg2->repeatc)
9384 repeatc2 = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(wrkarg2->repeatc));
9385 else
9386 repeatc2 = 1;
9387 }
9388 }
9389 wrkarg1 = c = root;
9390 }
9391 return rslt;
9392}
9393
9394static ACL *
9395eval_nint(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9396{
9397 ACL *rslt;
9398 ACL *wrkarg;
9399 int conval;
9400
9401 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9402 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
9403 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
9404 INT num1[4];
9405 INT res[4];
9406 INT con1;
9407 DTYPE dtype1 = wrkarg->dtype;
9408
9409 switch (DTY(dtype1)) {
9410 case TY_REAL:
9411 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
9412 num1[0] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
9413 if (xfcmp(con1, num1[0]) >= 0) {
9414 INT fv2_23;
9415 xffloat(1 << 23, &fv2_23);
9416 if (xfcmp(con1, fv2_23) >= 0)
9417 xfadd(con1, CONVAL2G(stb.flt0), &res[0]);
9418 else
9419 xfadd(con1, CONVAL2G(stb.flthalf), &res[0]);
9420 } else {
9421 INT fvm2_23;
9422 xffloat(-(1 << 23), &fvm2_23);
9423 if (xfcmp(con1, fvm2_23) <= 0)
9424 xfsub(con1, CONVAL2G(stb.flt0), &res[0]);
9425 else
9426 xfsub(con1, CONVAL2G(stb.flthalf), &res[0]);
9427 }
9428 break;
9429 case TY_DBLE:
9430 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
9431 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.dbl0, DT_REAL8) >= 0) {
9432 INT dv2_52[2] = {0x43300000, 0x00000000};
9433 INT d2_52;
9434 d2_52 = getcon(dv2_52, DT_DBLE);
9435 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, d2_52, DT_REAL8) >= 0)
9436 res[0] = const_fold(OP_ADD, con1, stb.dbl0, DT_REAL8);
9437 else
9438 res[0] = const_fold(OP_ADD, con1, stb.dblhalf, DT_REAL8);
9439 } else {
9440 INT dvm2_52[2] = {0xc3300000, 0x00000000};
9441 INT dm2_52;
9442 dm2_52 = getcon(dvm2_52, DT_DBLE);
9443 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, dm2_52, DT_REAL8) <= 0)
9444 res[0] = const_fold(OP_SUB, con1, stb.dblhalf, DT_REAL8);
9445 else
9446 res[0] = const_fold(OP_SUB, con1, stb.dbl0, DT_REAL8);
9447 }
9448 break;
9449#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9450 case TY_QUAD:
9451 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
9452 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.quad0, DT_QUAD) >= 0) {
9453 INT qv2_112[4] = {MAX_MANTI_BIT0_31, MAX_MANTI_BIT32_63, MAX_MANTI_BIT64_95, MAX_MANTI_BIT96_127};
9454 INT q2_112;
9455 q2_112 = getcon(qv2_112, DT_QUAD);
9456 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, q2_112, DT_QUAD) >= 0)
9457 res[0] = const_fold(OP_ADD, con1, stb.quad0, DT_QUAD);
9458 else
9459 res[0] = const_fold(OP_ADD, con1, stb.quadhalf, DT_QUAD);
9460 } else {
9461 INT qvm2_112[4] = {MMAX_MANTI_BIT0_31, MMAX_MANTI_BIT32_63, MMAX_MANTI_BIT64_95, MMAX_MANTI_BIT96_127};
9462 INT qm2_112;
9463 qm2_112 = getcon(qvm2_112, DT_QUAD);
9464 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, qm2_112, DT_QUAD) <= 0)
9465 res[0] = const_fold(OP_SUB, con1, stb.quadhalf, DT_QUAD);
9466 else
9467 res[0] = const_fold(OP_SUB, con1, stb.quad0, DT_QUAD);
9468 }
9469 break;
9470#endif
9471 }
9472 conval = cngcon(res[0], dtype1, dtype);
9473 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
9474 wrkarg->conval = conval;
9475 }
9476 return rslt;
9477}
9478
9479static ACL *
9480eval_floor(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9481{
9482 ACL *rslt;
9483 ACL *wrkarg;
9484 int conval;
9485
9486 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9487 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
9488 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
9489 INT num1[4];
9490 INT con1;
9491 int adjust;
9492
9493 adjust = 0;
9494 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
9495 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) {
9496 case TY_REAL:
9497 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_REAL4, dtype);
9498 num1[0] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
9499 if (xfcmp(con1, num1[0]) < 0) {
9500 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_REAL4);
9501 if (xfcmp(con1, wrkarg->conval) != 0)
9502 adjust = 1;
9503 }
9504 break;
9505 case TY_DBLE:
9506 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_REAL8, dtype);
9507 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.dbl0, DT_REAL8) < 0) {
9508 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_REAL8);
9509 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, wrkarg->conval, DT_REAL8) != 0)
9510 adjust = 1;
9511 }
9512 break;
9513#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9514 case TY_QUAD:
9515 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_QUAD, dtype);
9516 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.quad0, DT_QUAD) < 0) {
9517 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_QUAD);
9518 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, wrkarg->conval, DT_QUAD) != 0)
9519 adjust = 1;
9520 }
9521 break;
9522#endif
9523 }
9524 if (adjust) {
9525 if (DT_ISWORD(dtype))
9526 conval--;
9527 else {
9528 num1[0] = 0;
9529 num1[1] = 1;
9530 con1 = getcon(num1, dtype);
9531 conval = const_fold(OP_SUB, conval, con1, dtype);
9532 }
9533 }
9534 wrkarg->conval = conval;
9535 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
9536 }
9537 return rslt;
9538}
9539
9540static ACL *
9541eval_ceiling(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9542{
9543 ACL *rslt;
9544 ACL *wrkarg;
9545 int conval;
9546
9547 rslt = eval_init_expr(arg);
9548 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
9549 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
9550 INT num1[4];
9551 INT con1;
9552 int adjust;
9553
9554 adjust = 0;
9555 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
9556 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) {
9557 case TY_REAL:
9558 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_REAL4, dtype);
9559 num1[0] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
9560 if (xfcmp(con1, num1[0]) > 0) {
9561 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_REAL4);
9562 if (xfcmp(con1, wrkarg->conval) != 0)
9563 adjust = 1;
9564 }
9565 break;
9566 case TY_DBLE:
9567 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_REAL8, dtype);
9568 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.dbl0, DT_REAL8) > 0) {
9569 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_REAL8);
9570 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, wrkarg->conval, DT_REAL8) != 0)
9571 adjust = 1;
9572 }
9573 break;
9574#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9575 case TY_QUAD:
9576 conval = cngcon(con1, DT_QUAD, dtype);
9577 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, stb.quad0, DT_QUAD) > 0) {
9578 con1 = cngcon(conval, dtype, DT_QUAD);
9579 if (const_fold(OP_CMP, con1, wrkarg->conval, DT_QUAD) != 0)
9580 adjust = 1;
9581 }
9582 break;
9583#endif
9584 }
9585 if (adjust) {
9586 if (DT_ISWORD(dtype))
9587 conval++;
9588 else {
9589 num1[0] = 0;
9590 num1[1] = 1;
9591 con1 = getcon(num1, dtype);
9592 conval = const_fold(OP_ADD, conval, con1, dtype);
9593 }
9594 }
9595 wrkarg->conval = conval;
9596 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
9597 }
9598 return rslt;
9599}
9600
9601static ACL *
9602eval_mod(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9603{
9604 ACL *rslt, *arg1, *arg2;
9605 int conval1, conval2, conval3;
9606
9607 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9608 arg1 = arg->id == AC_ACONST ? arg->subc : arg;
9609 arg2 = arg->next->id == AC_ACONST ? arg->next->subc : arg->next;
9610 arg->next = 0;
9611 dtype = DDTG(dtype);
9612 for (; arg1; arg1 = arg1->next) {
9613 /* mod(a,p) == a-int(a/p)*p */
9614 conval1 = cngcon(arg1->conval, arg1->dtype, dtype);
9615 conval2 = cngcon(arg2->conval, arg2->dtype, dtype);
9616 conval3 = const_fold(OP_DIV, conval1, conval2, dtype);
9617 conval3 = cngcon(conval3, dtype, DT_INT8);
9618 conval3 = cngcon(conval3, DT_INT8, dtype);
9619 conval3 = const_fold(OP_MUL, conval3, conval2, dtype);
9620 conval3 = const_fold(OP_SUB, conval1, conval3, dtype);
9621 arg1->conval = conval3;
9622 arg1->dtype = dtype;
9623 if (arg2->next)
9624 arg2 = arg2->next;
9625 }
9626 return rslt;
9627}
9628
9629static ACL *
9630eval_repeat(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9631{
9632 ACL *rslt = NULL;
9633 ACL *arg1;
9634 ACL *arg2;
9635 int i, j, cvlen, newlen;
9636 INT ncopies;
9637 char *p, *cp, *str;
9638
9639 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9640 arg1 = arg;
9641 arg2 = arg->next;
9642 ncopies = get_int_from_init_conval(arg2);
9643 newlen = size_of(dtype);
9644 cvlen = size_of(arg1->dtype);
9645
9646 NEW(str, char, newlen);
9647 cp = str;
9648 j = ncopies;
9649 while (j-- > 0) {
9650 i = cvlen;
9651 p = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(arg1->conval);
9652 while (i-- > 0)
9653 *cp++ = *p++;
9654 }
9655
9656 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9657 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9658 rslt->dtype = dtype;
9659 rslt->repeatc = astb.i1;
9660 rslt->conval = getstring(str, newlen);
9661
9662 FREE(str);
9663 return rslt;
9664}
9665
9666/* Store the value 'conval' of type 'dtype' into 'destination'. */
9667static void
9668transfer_store(INT conval, DTYPE dtype, char *destination)
9669{
9670 int *dest = (int *)destination;
9671 INT real, imag;
9672
9673 if (DT_ISWORD(dtype)) {
9674 dest[0] = conval;
9675 return;
9676 }
9677
9678 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
9679 case TY_DWORD:
9680 case TY_INT8:
9681 case TY_LOG8:
9682 case TY_DBLE:
9683 dest[0] = CONVAL2G(conval);
9684 dest[1] = CONVAL1G(conval);
9685 break;
9686
9687#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9688 case TY_QUAD:
9689 dest[0] = CONVAL4G(conval);
9690 dest[1] = CONVAL3G(conval);
9691 dest[2] = CONVAL2G(conval);
9692 dest[3] = CONVAL1G(conval);
9693 break;
9694#endif
9695
9696 case TY_CMPLX:
9697 dest[0] = CONVAL1G(conval);
9698 dest[1] = CONVAL2G(conval);
9699 break;
9700
9701 case TY_DCMPLX:
9702 real = CONVAL1G(conval);
9703 imag = CONVAL2G(conval);
9704 dest[0] = CONVAL2G(real);
9705 dest[1] = CONVAL1G(real);
9706 dest[2] = CONVAL2G(imag);
9707 dest[3] = CONVAL1G(imag);
9708 break;
9709
9710 case TY_CHAR:
9711 memcpy(dest, stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(conval), size_of(dtype));
9712 break;
9713
9714 default:
9715 interr("transfer_store: unexpected dtype", dtype, 3);
9716 }
9717}
9718
9719/* Get a value of type 'dtype' from buffer 'source'. */
9720static INT
9721transfer_load(DTYPE dtype, char *source)
9722{
9723 int *src = (int *)source;
9724 INT num[4], real[2], imag[2];
9725
9726 if (DT_ISWORD(dtype))
9727 return src[0];
9728
9729 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
9730 case TY_DWORD:
9731 case TY_INT8:
9732 case TY_LOG8:
9733 case TY_DBLE:
9734 num[1] = src[0];
9735 num[0] = src[1];
9736 break;
9737
9738#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9739 case TY_QUAD:
9740 num[3] = src[0];
9741 num[2] = src[1];
9742 num[1] = src[2];
9743 num[0] = src[3];
9744 break;
9745#endif
9746
9747 case TY_CMPLX:
9748 num[0] = src[0];
9749 num[1] = src[1];
9750 break;
9751
9752 case TY_DCMPLX:
9753 real[1] = src[0];
9754 real[0] = src[1];
9755 imag[1] = src[2];
9756 imag[0] = src[3];
9757 num[0] = getcon(real, DT_REAL8);
9758 num[1] = getcon(imag, DT_REAL8);
9759 break;
9760
9761 case TY_CHAR:
9762 return getstring(source, size_of(dtype));
9763
9764 default:
9765 interr("transfer_load: unexpected dtype", dtype, 3);
9766 }
9767
9768 return getcon(num, dtype);
9769}
9770
9771static ACL *
9772eval_transfer(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
9773{
9774 ACL *src;
9775 ACL *rslt;
9776 int ssize, sdtype, rsize, rdtype;
9777 int need, avail;
9778 char value[256];
9779 char *buffer = value;
9780 char *bp;
9781 INT pad;
9782
9783 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9784 src = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
9785 /* Find the type and size of the source and result. */
9786 sdtype = DDTG(arg->dtype);
9787 ssize = size_of(sdtype);
9788 rdtype = DDTG(dtype);
9789 rsize = size_of(rdtype);
9790
9791 /* Be sure we have enough space. */
9792 need = (rsize > ssize ? rsize : ssize) * 2;
9793 if (sizeof(value) < need) {
9794 NEW(buffer, char, need);
9795 return 0;
9796 }
9797
9798 /* Get a pad value in case we have to fill. */
9799 if (DTY(sdtype) == TY_CHAR)
9800 memset(buffer, ' ', ssize);
9801 else
9802 BZERO(buffer, char, ssize);
9803 pad = transfer_load(sdtype, buffer);
9804
9805 src->next = 0;
9806 if (DTY(src->dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
9807 src = src->subc;
9808 bp = buffer;
9809 avail = 0;
9810 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY) {
9811 /* Result is scalar. */
9812 while (avail < rsize) {
9813 if (src) {
9814 transfer_store(src->conval, sdtype, bp);
9815 src = src->next;
9816 } else
9817 transfer_store(pad, sdtype, bp);
9818 bp += ssize;
9819 avail += ssize;
9820 }
9821 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9822 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9823 rslt->dtype = rdtype;
9824 rslt->conval = transfer_load(rdtype, buffer);
9825 } else {
9826 /* Result is array. */
9827 ACL *root, **current;
9828 ISZ_T i, nelem;
9829 int j;
9830
9831 nelem = get_const_from_ast(ADD_NUMELM(dtype));
9832 root = NULL;
9833 current = &root;
9834 for (i = 0; i < nelem; i++) {
9835 while (avail < rsize) {
9836 if (src) {
9837 transfer_store(src->conval, sdtype, bp);
9838 src = src->next;
9839 } else
9840 transfer_store(pad, sdtype, bp);
9841 bp += ssize;
9842 avail += ssize;
9843 }
9844 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9845 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9846 rslt->dtype = rdtype;
9847 rslt->conval = transfer_load(rdtype, buffer);
9848 *current = rslt;
9849 current = &(rslt->next);
9850 bp -= rsize;
9851 avail -= rsize;
9852 for (j = 0; j < avail; j++)
9853 buffer[j] = buffer[rsize + j];
9854 }
9855 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9856 rslt->id = AC_ACONST;
9857 rslt->dtype = dtype;
9858 rslt->subc = root;
9859 }
9860
9861 if (buffer != value)
9862 FREE(buffer);
9863 return rslt;
9864}
9865
9866static ACL *
9867eval_len_trim(ACL *arg)
9868{
9869 ACL *rslt;
9870 ACL *wrkarg;
9871 char *p;
9872 int cvlen, result;
9873
9874 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9875 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
9876 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
9877 p = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->conval);
9878 result = cvlen = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
9879 p += cvlen - 1;
9880 /* skip trailing blanks */
9881 while (cvlen-- > 0) {
9882 if (*p-- != ' ')
9883 break;
9884 result--;
9885 }
9886 wrkarg->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
9887 rslt->conval = get_default_int_val(result);
9888 }
9889 return rslt;
9890}
9891
9892static ACL *
9893eval_selected_real_kind(ACL *arg)
9894{
9895 ACL *rslt;
9896 ACL *wrkarg;
9897 int r;
9898 INT con;
9899
9900 r = 4;
9901
9902 wrkarg = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
9903 con = get_int_from_init_conval(wrkarg);
9904 if (con <= 6)
9905 r = 4;
9906 else if (con <= 15)
9907 r = 8;
9908#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9909 else if (con <= MAX_EXP_OF_QMANTISSA)
9910 r = REAL_16;
9911#endif
9912 else
9913 r = -1;
9914
9915 if (arg->next) {
9916 wrkarg = arg = arg->next;
9917 con = get_int_from_init_conval(wrkarg);
9918 if (con <= 37) {
9919 if (r > 0 && r < 4)
9920 r = 4;
9921 } else if (con <= 307) {
9922 if (r > 0 && r < 8)
9923 r = 8;
9924#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
9925 } else if (con <= MAX_EXP_QVALUE) {
9926 if (r > REAL_0 && r < REAL_16)
9927 r = REAL_16;
9928#endif
9929 } else {
9930 if (r > 0)
9931 r = 0;
9932 r -= 2;
9933 }
9934 }
9935
9936 if (arg->next) {
9937 wrkarg = arg->next;
9938 con = get_int_from_init_conval(wrkarg);
9939 if (con != RADIX2) {
9940 if (con == NOT_GET_VAL && !ARG_STK(KEYWD_ARGS2)) {
9941 } else {
9942 r = NO_REAL;
9943 }
9944 }
9945 }
9946
9947 rslt = GET_ACL(15);
9948 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9949 rslt->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
9950 rslt->repeatc = astb.i1;
9951 rslt->conval = get_default_int_val(r);
9952
9953 return rslt;
9954}
9955
9956static ACL *
9957eval_selected_int_kind(ACL *arg)
9958{
9959 ACL *rslt;
9960 int r;
9961 INT con;
9962
9963 rslt = eval_init_expr(arg);
9964 con = get_int_from_init_conval(rslt);
9965 if (con > 18 || (con > 9 && XBIT(57, 2)))
9966 r = -1;
9967 else if (con > 9)
9968 r = 8;
9969 else if (con > 4)
9970 r = 4;
9971 else if (con > 2)
9972 r = 2;
9973 else
9974 r = 1;
9975 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9976 rslt->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
9977 rslt->repeatc = astb.i1;
9978 rslt->conval = get_default_int_val(r);
9979
9980 return rslt;
9981}
9982
9983static ACL *
9984eval_selected_char_kind(ACL *arg)
9985{
9986 ACL *rslt;
9987 int r;
9988
9989 rslt = eval_init_expr(arg);
9990 r = _selected_char_kind(rslt->conval);
9991 rslt->id = AC_CONVAL;
9992 rslt->dtype = stb.user.dt_int;
9993 rslt->repeatc = astb.i1;
9994 rslt->conval = get_default_int_val(r);
9995
9996 return rslt;
9997}
9998
9999static ACL *
10000eval_scan(ACL *arg)
10001{
10002 ACL *rslt = NULL;
10003 ACL *c;
10004 ACL *wrkarg;
10005 int i, j;
10006 int l_string, l_set;
10007 char *p_string, *p_set;
10008 INT back = 0;
10009
10010 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10011 p_set = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(arg->next->conval);
10012 l_set = size_of(arg->next->dtype);
10013
10014 if (arg->next->next) {
10015 back = get_int_from_init_conval(arg->next->next);
10016 }
10017
10018 wrkarg = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10019 wrkarg = (wrkarg->id == AC_ACONST ? wrkarg->subc : wrkarg);
10020 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10021 p_string = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->conval);
10022 l_string = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
10023
10024 c = GET_ACL(15);
10025 c->id = AC_CONVAL;
10026 c->dtype = stb.dt_int;
10027 c->repeatc = wrkarg->repeatc;
10028
10029 if (back == 0) {
10030 for (i = 0; i < l_string; ++i)
10031 for (j = 0; j < l_set; ++j)
10032 if (p_set[j] == p_string[i]) {
10033 c->conval = i + 1;
10034 goto addtolist;
10035 }
10036 } else {
10037 for (i = l_string - 1; i >= 0; --i)
10038 for (j = 0; j < l_set; ++j)
10039 if (p_set[j] == p_string[i]) {
10040 c->conval = i + 1;
10041 goto addtolist;
10042 }
10043 }
10044 c->conval = 0;
10045
10046 addtolist:
10047 add_to_list(c, &rslt);
10048 }
10049 rslt->repeatc = arg->repeatc;
10050 return rslt;
10051}
10052
10053static ACL *
10054eval_verify(ACL *arg)
10055{
10056 ACL *rslt = NULL;
10057 ACL *c;
10058 ACL *wrkarg;
10059 int i, j;
10060 int l_string, l_set;
10061 char *p_string, *p_set;
10062 INT back = 0;
10063
10064 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10065 p_set = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(arg->next->conval);
10066 l_set = size_of(arg->next->dtype);
10067
10068 if (arg->next->next) {
10069 back = get_int_from_init_conval(arg->next->next);
10070 }
10071
10072 wrkarg = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10073 wrkarg = (wrkarg->id == AC_ACONST ? wrkarg->subc : wrkarg);
10074 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10075 p_string = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->u1.ast);
10076 l_string = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
10077
10078 c = GET_ACL(15);
10079 c->id = AC_CONVAL;
10080 c->dtype = stb.dt_int;
10081 c->conval = 0;
10082 c->repeatc = wrkarg->repeatc;
10083
10084 if (back == 0) {
10085 for (i = 0; i < l_string; ++i) {
10086 for (j = 0; j < l_set; ++j) {
10087 if (p_set[j] == p_string[i])
10088 goto contf;
10089 }
10090 c->conval = i + 1;
10091 break;
10092 contf:;
10093 }
10094 } else {
10095 for (i = l_string - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
10096 for (j = 0; j < l_set; ++j) {
10097 if (p_set[j] == p_string[i])
10098 goto contb;
10099 }
10100 c->conval = i + 1;
10101 break;
10102 contb:;
10103 }
10104 }
10105
10106 add_to_list(c, &rslt);
10107 }
10108 rslt->repeatc = arg->repeatc;
10109 return rslt;
10110}
10111
10112static ACL *
10113eval_index(ACL *arg)
10114{
10115 ACL *rslt = NULL;
10116 ACL *c;
10117 ACL *wrkarg;
10118 int i, n;
10119 int l_string, l_substring;
10120 char *p_string, *p_substring;
10121 INT back = 0;
10122
10123 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10124 p_substring = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(arg->next->conval);
10125 l_substring = size_of(arg->next->dtype);
10126
10127 if (arg->next->next) {
10128 back = get_int_from_init_conval(arg->next->next);
10129 }
10130
10131 wrkarg = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10132 wrkarg = (wrkarg->id == AC_ACONST ? wrkarg->subc : wrkarg);
10133 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10134 p_string = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->conval);
10135 l_string = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
10136
10137 c = GET_ACL(15);
10138 c->id = AC_CONST;
10139 c->dtype = stb.dt_int;
10140 c->repeatc = wrkarg->repeatc;
10141
10142 n = l_string - l_substring;
10143 if (n < 0)
10144 c->conval = 0;
10145 if (back == 0) {
10146 if (l_substring == 0)
10147 c->conval = 0;
10148 for (i = 0; i <= n; ++i) {
10149 if (p_string[i] == p_substring[0] &&
10150 strncmp(p_string + i, p_substring, l_substring) == 0)
10151 c->conval = i + 1;
10152 }
10153 } else {
10154 if (l_substring == 0)
10155 c->conval = l_string + 1;
10156 for (i = n; i >= 0; --i) {
10157 if (p_string[i] == p_substring[0] &&
10158 strncmp(p_string + i, p_substring, l_substring) == 0)
10159 c->conval = i + 1;
10160 }
10161 }
10162 add_to_list(c, &rslt);
10163 }
10164 rslt->repeatc = arg->repeatc;
10165 return rslt;
10166}
10167
10168static ACL *
10169eval_trim(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
10170{
10171 ACL *rslt;
10172 char *p, *cp;
10173 const char *str;
10174 int i, cvlen, newlen;
10175
10176 rslt = eval_init_expr(arg);
10177 p = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(rslt->conval);
10178 cvlen = newlen = size_of(rslt->dtype);
10179
10180 i = 0;
10181 p += cvlen - 1;
10182 /* skip trailing blanks */
10183 while (cvlen-- > 0) {
10184 if (*p-- != ' ')
10185 break;
10186 newlen--;
10187 }
10188
10189 if (newlen == 0) {
10190 str = " ";
10191 rslt->conval = getstring(str, strlen(str));
10192 } else {
10193 str = cp = getitem(0, newlen);
10194 i = newlen;
10195 cp += newlen - 1;
10196 p++;
10197 while (i-- > 0) {
10198 *cp-- = *p--;
10199 }
10200
10201 rslt->conval = getstring(str, newlen);
10202 }
10203
10204 rslt->dtype = get_type(2, DTY(dtype), newlen);
10205 return rslt;
10206}
10207
10208static ACL *
10209eval_adjustl(ACL *arg)
10210{
10211 ACL *rslt;
10212 ACL *wrkarg;
10213 char *p, *cp, *str;
10214 char ch;
10215 int i, cvlen, origlen;
10216
10217 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10218 rslt = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10219 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
10220 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10221 p = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->conval);
10222 cvlen = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
10223 origlen = cvlen;
10224 str = cp = getitem(0, cvlen + 1); /* +1 just in case cvlen is 0 */
10225 i = 0;
10226 /* left justify string - skip leading blanks */
10227 while (cvlen-- > 0) {
10228 ch = *p++;
10229 if (ch != ' ') {
10230 *cp++ = ch;
10231 break;
10232 }
10233 i++;
10234 }
10235 while (cvlen-- > 0)
10236 *cp++ = *p++;
10237 /* append blanks */
10238 while (i-- > 0)
10239 *cp++ = ' ';
10240 wrkarg->conval = getstring(str, origlen);
10241 }
10242
10243 return rslt;
10244}
10245
10246static ACL *
10247eval_adjustr(ACL *arg)
10248{
10249 ACL *rslt;
10250 ACL *wrkarg;
10251 char *p, *cp, *str;
10252 char ch;
10253 int i, cvlen, origlen;
10254
10255 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10256 rslt = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10257 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
10258 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10259 p = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(wrkarg->conval);
10260 origlen = cvlen = size_of(wrkarg->dtype);
10261 str = cp = getitem(0, cvlen + 1); /* +1 just in case cvlen is 0 */
10262 i = 0;
10263 p += cvlen - 1;
10264 cp += cvlen - 1;
10265 /* right justify string - skip trailing blanks */
10266 while (cvlen-- > 0) {
10267 ch = *p--;
10268 if (ch != ' ') {
10269 *cp-- = ch;
10270 break;
10271 }
10272 i++;
10273 }
10274 while (cvlen-- > 0)
10275 *cp-- = *p--;
10276 /* insert blanks */
10277 while (i-- > 0)
10278 *cp-- = ' ';
10279 wrkarg->id = AC_CONVAL;
10280 wrkarg->conval = getstring(str, origlen);
10281 }
10282
10283 return rslt;
10284}

10290

10292 rslt->dtype = dtype;
10293 return rslt;

10296static ACL *
10297eval_size(ACL *arg)
10298{
10299 ACL *arg1;
10300 ACL *arg2;
10301 ACL *arg3;
10302 ACL *rslt;
10303 int dim;
10304 int i;
10305
10306 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10307 arg1 = arg;
10308 arg2 = arg->next;
10309 if ((arg3 = arg->next->next)) {
10310 arg3 = eval_init_expr_item(arg3);
10311 if (!arg3) {
10312 return 0;
10313 }
10314 dim = arg3->conval;
10315
10316 for (i = 1, arg2 = arg2->subc; i < dim && arg2; i++, arg2 = arg2->next)
10317 ;
10318 rslt = clone_init_const(arg2, TRUE);
10319 } else {
10320 rslt = clone_init_const(arg1, TRUE);
10321 }
10322
10323 return rslt;
10324}
10325
10326static ACL *
10327eval_ul_bound(ACL *arg)
10328{
10329 ACL *arg1;
10330 ACL *arg2;
10331 INT arg2const;
10332 ACL *rslt;
10333 ADSC *adsc;
10334 int rank;
10335 int i;
10336
10337 arg = arg1 = eval_init_expr(arg);
10338 adsc = AD_DPTR(arg1->dtype);
10339 rank = AD_UPBD(adsc, 0);
10340 if (arg->next) {
10341 arg2 = arg->next;
10342 arg2const = get_int_from_init_conval(arg2);
10343
10344 if (arg2const > rank) {
10345 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, "DIM argument greater than the array rank",
10346 CNULL);
10347 return 0;
10348 }
10349 rslt = arg1->subc;
10350 for (i = 1; rslt && i < arg2const; i++) {
10351 rslt = rslt->next;
10352 }
10353 rslt = clone_init_const(rslt, TRUE);
10354 } else {
10355 rslt = clone_init_const(arg1, TRUE);
10356 }
10357 return rslt;
10358}
10359
10360static int
10361copy_initconst_to_array(ACL **arr, ACL *c, int count)
10362{
10363 int i;
10364 int acnt;
10365 ACL *acl;
10366
10367 for (i = 0; i < count;) {
10368 if (c == NULL)
10369 break;
10370 switch (c->id) {
10371 case AC_ACONST:
10372 acnt = copy_initconst_to_array(arr, c->subc,
10373 count - i); /* MORE: count - i??? */
10374 i += acnt;
10375 arr += acnt;
10376 break;
10377 case AC_CONST:
10378 case AC_AST:
10379 acl = *arr = clone_init_const(c, TRUE);
10380 /* if there is a repeat */
10381 if (acl->repeatc > 0) {
10382 acnt = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(acl->repeatc));
10383 arr += acnt;
10384 i += acnt;
10385 } else {
10386 arr++;
10387 i++;
10388 }
10389 break;
10390 default:
10391 interr("copy_initconst_to_array: unexpected const type", c->id, 3);
10392 return count;
10393 }
10394 c = c->next;
10395 }
10396 return i;
10397}
10398
10399static ACL *
10400eval_reshape(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype, LOGICAL transpose)
10401{
10402 ACL *srclist;
10403 ACL *tacl;
10404 ACL *pad = NULL;
10405 ACL *wrklist = NULL;
10406 ACL *orderarg = NULL;
10407 ACL **old_val = NULL;
10408 ACL **new_val = NULL;
10409 ACL *c = NULL;
10410 ADSC *adsc = AD_DPTR(dtype);
10411 int *new_index;
10412 int src_sz, dest_sz;
10413 int rank;
10414 INT order[MAXDIMS];
10415 int lwb[MAXDIMS];
10416 int upb[MAXDIMS];
10417 int mult[MAXDIMS];
10418 int i;
10419 int count;
10420
10421 arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10422 srclist = clone_init_const(arg, TRUE);
10423 if (arg->next && arg->next->next) {
10424 pad = arg->next->next;
10425 if (pad->id == AC_ACONST) {
10426 pad = eval_init_expr_item(pad);
10427 }
10428 if (arg->next->next->next && arg->next->next->next->id == AC_ACONST) {
10429 orderarg = eval_init_expr_item(arg->next->next->next);
10430 }
10431 }
10432
10433 src_sz = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(ADD_NUMELM(arg->dtype)));
10434 dest_sz = 1;
10435
10436 rank = AD_NUMDIM(adsc);
10437 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
10438 lwb[i] = 0;
10439 upb[i] = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(AD_UPBD(adsc, i)));
10440 mult[i] = dest_sz;
10441 dest_sz *= upb[i];
10442 }
10443
10444 if (orderarg == NULL) {
10445 if (transpose) {
10446 order[0] = 1;
10447 order[1] = 0;
10448 } else {
10449 if (src_sz == dest_sz) {
10450 return srclist;
10451 }
10452 for (i = 0; i < rank; i++) {
10453 order[i] = i;
10454 }
10455 }
10456 } else {
10457 LOGICAL out_of_order;
10458
10459 out_of_order = FALSE;
10460 c = (orderarg->id == AC_ACONST ? orderarg->subc : orderarg);
10461 for (i = 0; c && i < rank; c = c->next, i++) {
10462 order[i] =
10463 DT_ISWORD(c->dtype) ? c->conval - 1 : get_int_cval(c->conval) - 1;
10464 if (order[i] != i)
10465 out_of_order = TRUE;
10466 }
10467 if (!out_of_order && src_sz == dest_sz) {
10468 return srclist;
10469 }
10470 }
10471
10472 NEW(old_val, ACL *, dest_sz);
10473 if (old_val == NULL)
10474 return 0;
10475 BZERO(old_val, ACL *, dest_sz);
10476 /* MORE use GET_ACL for new_value */
10477 NEW(new_val, ACL *, dest_sz);
10478 NEW(new_index, int, dest_sz);
10479 if (new_val == NULL || new_index == NULL) {
10480 return 0;
10481 }
10482 BZERO(old_val, ACL *, dest_sz);
10483 BZERO(new_index, int, dest_sz);
10484
10485 count = dest_sz > src_sz ? src_sz : dest_sz;
10486 wrklist = srclist->id == AC_ACONST ? srclist->subc : srclist;
10487 (void)copy_initconst_to_array(old_val, wrklist, count);
10488
10489 if (dest_sz > src_sz) {
10490 count = dest_sz - src_sz;
10491 wrklist = pad->id == AC_ACONST ? pad->subc : pad;
10492 while (count > 0) {
10493 i = copy_initconst_to_array(old_val + src_sz, wrklist, count);
10494 count -= i;
10495 src_sz += i;
10496 }
10497 }
10498
10499 /* index to access source in linear order */
10500 i = 0;
10501 while (TRUE) {
10502 int index; /* index where to store each element of new val */
10503 int j;
10504
10505 index = 0;
10506 for (j = 0; j < rank; j++)
10507 index += lwb[j] * mult[j];
10508
10509 /* new_index contains old_val index */
10510 new_index[index] = i;
10511
10512 /* update loop indices */
10513 for (j = 0; j < rank; j++) {
10514 int loop;
10515 loop = order[j];
10516 lwb[loop]++;
10517 if (lwb[loop] < upb[loop])
10518 break;
10519 lwb[loop] = 0; /* reset and go on to the next loop */
10520 }
10521 if (j >= rank)
10522 break;
10523 i++;
10524 }
10525
10526 for (i = 0; i < dest_sz; i++) {
10527 ACL *tacl, *tail;
10528 int idx, start, end;
10529 int index = new_index[i];
10530 int repeatc;
10531 if (old_val[index]) {
10532 if (old_val[index]->repeatc)
10533 repeatc = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(old_val[index]->repeatc));
10534 else
10535 repeatc = 1;
10536 if (repeatc <= 1) {
10537 new_val[i] = old_val[index];
10538 new_val[i]->id = AC_CONVAL;
10539 } else {
10540 idx = index + 1;
10541 start = i;
10542 end = repeatc - 1;
10543 while (new_index[++start] == idx) {
10544 ++idx;
10545 if (end <= 0 || start > dest_sz - 1)
10546 break;
10547 }
10548 old_val[index]->next = NULL;
10549 tacl = clone_init_const(old_val[index], TRUE);
10550 tacl->repeatc = mk_cval(idx - index, DT_INT);
10551 tacl->id = AC_CONVAL;
10552 old_val[index]->repeatc = mk_cval(index - (idx - index), DT_INT);
10553 new_val[i] = tacl;
10554 }
10555 } else {
10556 tail = old_val[index];
10557 idx = index;
10558 while (tail == NULL && idx >= 0) {
10559 tail = old_val[idx--];
10560 }
10561 tail->next = NULL;
10562 tacl = clone_init_const(tail, TRUE);
10563 start = i;
10564 end = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(tail->repeatc)) - 1;
10565 idx = index + 1;
10566 while (new_index[++start] == idx) {
10567 ++idx;
10568 --end;
10569 if (end <= 0 || start > dest_sz - 1)
10570 break;
10571 }
10572 tail->repeatc = mk_cval(index - (idx - index), DT_INT);
10573 tacl->repeatc = mk_cval(idx - index, DT_INT);
10574 tacl->id = AC_CONVAL;
10575 new_val[i] = tacl;
10576 }
10577 }
10578 tacl = new_val[0];
10579 for (i = 0; i < dest_sz - 1; ++i) {
10580 if (new_val[i + 1] == NULL) {
10581 continue;
10582 } else {
10583 tacl->next = new_val[i + 1];
10584 tacl = new_val[i + 1];
10585 }
10586 }
10587 if (new_val[dest_sz - 1])
10588 (new_val[dest_sz - 1])->next = NULL;
10589 srclist = *new_val;
10590
10591 FREE(old_val);
10592 FREE(new_index);
10593
10594 return srclist;
10595}
10596
10597static ACL *
10598eval_null(int sptr)
10599{
10600 ACL *root = NULL;
10601 ACL *c;
10602
10603 /* for <ptr>$p */
10604 c = GET_ACL(15);
10605 c->id = AC_CONVAL;
10606 c->dtype = DT_PTR;
10607 c->u1.ast = astb.bnd.zero;
10608 c->conval = 0;
10609 add_to_list(c, &root);
10610 if (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)) == TY_ARRAY) {
10611 /* for <ptr>$o */
10612 c = GET_ACL(15);
10613 c->id = AC_CONVAL;
10614 c->dtype = DT_PTR;
10615 c->sptr = PTROFFG(sptr);
10616 c->u1.ast = astb.bnd.zero;
10617 c->conval = 0;
10618 add_to_list(c, &root);
10619 /* for <ptr>$sd[1] */
10620 c = GET_ACL(15);
10621 c->id = AC_CONVAL;
10622 c->dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
10623 c->sptr = SDSCG(sptr);
10624 c->u1.ast = astb.bnd.zero;
10625 c->conval = 0;
10626 add_to_list(c, &root);
10627 }
10628
10629 return root;
10630}
10631
10632static ACL *
10633eval_sqrt(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype)
10634{
10635 ACL *rslt;
10636 ACL *wrkarg;
10637 INT conval;
10638
10639 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg);
10640 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt);
10641 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) {
10642 INT num1[4];
10643 INT res[4];
10644 INT con1;
10645
10646 con1 = wrkarg->conval;
10647 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) {
10648 case TY_REAL:
10649 xfsqrt(con1, &res[0]);
10650 conval = res[0];
10651 break;
10652 case TY_DBLE:
10653 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1);
10654 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1);
10655 xdsqrt(num1, res);
10656 conval = getcon(res, DT_DBLE);
10657 break;
10658#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
10659 case TY_QUAD:
10660 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1);
10661 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1);
10662 num1[2] = CONVAL3G(con1);
10663 num1[3] = CONVAL4G(con1);
10664 xqsqrt(num1, res);
10665 conval = getcon(res, DT_QUAD);
10666 break;
10667#endif
10668 case TY_CMPLX:
10669 case TY_DCMPLX:
10670 /*
10671 a = sqrt(real**2 + imag**2); "hypot(real,imag)
10672 if (a == 0) {
10673 x = 0;
10674 y = 0;
10675 }
10676 else if (real > 0) {
10677 x = sqrt(0.5 * (a + real));
10678 y = 0.5 * (imag / x);
10679 }
10680 else {
10681 y = sqrt(0.5 * (a - real));
10682 if (imag < 0)
10683 y = -y;
10684 x = 0.5 * (imag / y);
10685 }
10686 res.real = x;
10687 res.imag = y;
10688 */
10689
10690 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
10691 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", "sqrt");
10692 break;
10693 default:
10694 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
10695 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", "sqrt");
10696 break;
10697 }
10698 conval = cngcon(conval, wrkarg->dtype, dtype);
10699 wrkarg->conval = conval;
10700 wrkarg->dtype = dtype;
10701 }
10702 return rslt;
10703}

10705/*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
10706
10707#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
10708#define FPINTRIN1(iname, ent, fscutil, dscutil, qscutil) \
10709 static ACL *ent(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype) \
10710 { \
10711 ACL *rslt; \
10712 ACL *wrkarg; \
10713 INT conval; \
10714 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg); \
10715 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt); \
10716 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) { \
10717 INT num1[4]; \
10718 INT res[4]; \
10719 INT con1; \
10720 con1 = wrkarg->conval; \
10721 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) { \
10722 case TY_REAL: \
10723 fscutil(con1, &res[0]); \
10724 conval = res[0]; \
10725 break; \
10726 case TY_DBLE: \
10727 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10728 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10729 dscutil(num1, res); \
10730 conval = getcon(res, DT_DBLE); \
10731 break; \
10732 case TY_QUAD: \
10733 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10734 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10735 num1[2] = CONVAL3G(con1); \
10736 num1[3] = CONVAL4G(con1); \
10737 qscutil(num1, res); \
10738 conval = getcon(res, DT_QUAD); \
10739 break; \
10740 case TY_CMPLX: \
10741 case TY_DCMPLX: \
10742 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10743 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10744 break; \
10745 case TY_HALF: \
10746 /* fallthrough to error */ \
10747 default: \
10748 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10749 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10750 break; \
10751 } \
10752 conval = cngcon(conval, wrkarg->dtype, dtype); \
10753 wrkarg->conval = conval; \
10754 wrkarg->dtype = dtype; \
10755 } \
10756 return rslt; \
10757 }
10758#else
10759#define FPINTRIN1(iname, ent, fscutil, dscutil, qscutil) \
10760 static ACL *ent(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype) \
10761 { \
10762 ACL *rslt; \
10763 ACL *wrkarg; \
10764 INT conval; \
10765 rslt = arg = eval_init_expr(arg); \
10766 wrkarg = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt); \
10767 for (; wrkarg; wrkarg = wrkarg->next) { \
10768 INT num1[4]; \
10769 INT res[4]; \
10770 INT con1; \
10771 con1 = wrkarg->conval; \
10772 switch (DTY(wrkarg->dtype)) { \
10773 case TY_REAL: \
10774 fscutil(con1, &res[0]); \
10775 conval = res[0]; \
10776 break; \
10777 case TY_DBLE: \
10778 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10779 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10780 dscutil(num1, res); \
10781 conval = getcon(res, DT_DBLE); \
10782 break; \
10783 case TY_CMPLX: \
10784 case TY_DCMPLX: \
10785 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10786 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10787 break; \
10788 case TY_HALF: \
10789 /* fallthrough to error */ \
10790 default: \
10791 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10792 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10793 break; \
10794 } \
10795 conval = cngcon(conval, wrkarg->dtype, dtype); \
10796 wrkarg->conval = conval; \
10797 wrkarg->dtype = dtype; \
10798 } \
10799 return rslt; \
10800 }
10801#endif

10821#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
10822#define FPINTRIN2(iname, ent, fscutil, dscutil, qscutil) \
10823 static ACL *ent(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype) \
10824 { \
10825 ACL *rslt = arg; \
10826 ACL *arg1, *arg2; \
10827 INT conval; \
10828 arg1 = eval_init_expr_item(arg); \
10829 arg2 = eval_init_expr_item(arg->next); \
10830 rslt = clone_init_const(arg1, TRUE); \
10831 arg1 = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt); \
10832 arg2 = (arg2->id == AC_ACONST ? arg2->subc : arg2); \
10833 for (; arg1; arg1 = arg1->next, arg2 = arg2->next) { \
10834 INT num1[4], num2[4]; \
10835 INT res[4]; \
10836 INT con1, con2; \
10837 con1 = arg1->conval; \
10838 con2 = arg2->conval; \
10839 switch (DTY(arg1->dtype)) { \
10840 case TY_REAL: \
10841 fscutil(con1, con2, &res[0]); \
10842 conval = res[0]; \
10843 break; \
10844 case TY_DBLE: \
10845 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10846 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10847 num2[0] = CONVAL1G(con2); \
10848 num2[1] = CONVAL2G(con2); \
10849 dscutil(num1, num2, res); \
10850 conval = getcon(res, DT_DBLE); \
10851 break; \
10852 case TY_QUAD: \
10853 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10854 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10855 num1[2] = CONVAL3G(con1); \
10856 num1[3] = CONVAL4G(con1); \
10857 num2[0] = CONVAL1G(con2); \
10858 num2[1] = CONVAL2G(con2); \
10859 num2[2] = CONVAL3G(con2); \
10860 num2[3] = CONVAL4G(con2); \
10861 qscutil(num1, num2, res); \
10862 conval = getcon(res, DT_QUAD); \
10863 break; \
10864 case TY_CMPLX: \
10865 case TY_DCMPLX: \
10866 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10867 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10868 break; \
10869 case TY_HALF: \
10870 /* fallthrough to error */ \
10871 default: \
10872 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10873 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10874 break; \
10875 } \
10876 conval = cngcon(conval, arg1->dtype, dtype); \
10877 arg1->conval = conval; \
10878 arg1->dtype = dtype; \
10879 } \
10880 return rslt; \
10881 }
10882#else
10883#define FPINTRIN2(iname, ent, fscutil, dscutil, qscutil) \
10884 static ACL *ent(ACL *arg, DTYPE dtype) \
10885 { \
10886 ACL *rslt = arg; \
10887 ACL *arg1, *arg2; \
10888 INT conval; \
10889 arg1 = eval_init_expr_item(arg); \
10890 arg2 = eval_init_expr_item(arg->next); \

10892 arg1 = (rslt->id == AC_ACONST ? rslt->subc : rslt); \
10893 arg2 = (arg2->id == AC_ACONST ? arg2->subc : arg2); \
10894 for (; arg1; arg1 = arg1->next, arg2 = arg2->next) { \

10898 con1 = arg1->conval; \

10900 switch (DTY(arg1->dtype)) { \
10901 case TY_REAL: \
10902 fscutil(con1, con2, &res[0]); \
10903 conval = res[0]; \
10904 break; \
10905 case TY_DBLE: \
10906 num1[0] = CONVAL1G(con1); \
10907 num1[1] = CONVAL2G(con1); \
10908 num2[0] = CONVAL1G(con2); \
10909 num2[1] = CONVAL2G(con2); \
10910 dscutil(num1, num2, res); \
10911 conval = getcon(res, DT_DBLE); \
10912 break; \
10913 case TY_CMPLX: \
10914 case TY_DCMPLX: \
10915 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10916 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10917 break; \
10918 case TY_HALF: \
10919 /* fallthrough to error */ \
10920 default: \
10921 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno, \
10922 "Intrinsic not supported in initialization:", iname); \
10923 break; \
10924 } \
10925 conval = cngcon(conval, arg1->dtype, dtype); \
10926 arg1->conval = conval; \
10927 arg1->dtype = dtype; \
10928 } \
